INSERT INTO `Activity` VALUES (1,'Royal Golf Course','高尔夫','Nuwara Eliya Golf Club, Nuwara Eliya','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','The Nuwara Eliya golf course has a interesting history. Built in 1889 this is located very centrally & just off the town center. It stretches across about 100 acres of land & was originally built amidst the tea plantations of this central highland region. This is a hill station town & the course is located at an altitude of 6000 feet.So the ball does travel faster – atleast 6 % approximately. The course is a 18 hole, 6070 yard, Par 70 layout – the scorecard is in meters, the distance from the ya','努瓦勒埃利耶高尔夫球场位于维多利亚花园对面，占地约40公顷，是努瓦勒埃利耶城中心最大的一片绿地。这个高尔夫球场建于1889年，是一个全长5520米，拥有18洞71标准杆的球场，是亚洲最古老的球场，号称亚洲第一。球场被群山环绕，周围树林密不透光，在这里打球如同打猎一般。目前，高尔夫俱乐部有很多的外籍会员，据说英国王子每年都来此打球，甚至有些外籍会员从他们的祖父起就已经是这里的会员。',0,4226,63,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Activities/Royal%20Golf%20Course/Thumb%20Royal%20Golf%20Course.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Activities/Royal%20Golf%20Course/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Activities/Royal%20Golf%20Course/Royal%20Golf%20Course.mp3',99),(2,'Train from Kandy to Nuwara Eliya (Nanu Oya Station)','高山小火车','nanu oya, Sri Lanka','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','The train from Kandy to NuwaraWliya, is rated as stunning rail way of the world. You will pass through the tea garden, the forest, and the mountain.','从斯里兰卡岛中部康提KANDY古城前往高山产茶区努沃勒埃利耶NuwaraEliya，这段被誉为“世上最美的高山火车线”。斯里兰卡火车和印度的火车一样，全程不报站，火车大门也是全程敞开的，火车缓缓穿梭于蜿蜒的热带丛林，旖旎风光在窗外慢慢流走。',0,3472,130,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Activities/Train%20from%20Kandy%20to%20Nuwara%20Eliya%20(Nanu%20Oya%20Station)/Thumb%20Train%20from%20Kandy%20to%20Nuwara%20Eliya%20(Nanu%20Oya%20Station).jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Activities/Train%20from%20Kandy%20to%20Nuwara%20Eliya%20(Nanu%20Oya%20Station)/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Activities/Train%20from%20Kandy%20to%20Nuwara%20Eliya%20(Nanu%20Oya%20Station)/Train%20from%20Kandy%20to%20Nuwara%20Eliya%20(Nanu%20Oya%20Station).mp3',99),(3,'Beach Activities','水上项目','update later...','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','','',0,8686,108,6,1,'','','','',99),(4,'Rekawa Turtle Nesting','海龟保育','update later...','','','','','1000LKR/500LKR','1000卢比/500卢比','',0,0,'','','The Turtle Conservation Project (TCP) developed a unique approach to turtle conservation in Rekawa – and continued this up until this day. Firstly, it provides in situ protection for turtle nests. This means that eggs remain where they were laid, with nest protectors providing protection across the entire beach. This maximizes the yield of the nests and ensures as many hatchlings as possible survive into the sea.','为了保护生活在印度洋的海龟而建。印度洋中生活的革龟、绿海龟、玳瑁、蠵龟、橄榄绿鳞龟都可以在这里看到。在斯里兰卡西南海岸，每天晚上海龟都会爬上海滩产卵，但是由于近些年来人类活动的破坏，小海龟非常不容易成活，所以志愿者每晚都会寻找龟卵，并帮助其孵化，然后等海龟长大再放归大海。在海龟孵化基地可以欣赏到海龟的孵化过程，听取环保知识，并可以参加放生小海龟活动。',0,9014,102,6,1,'','','','',99),(5,'Jeep Safari to Minneriya Elephant Park','米内瑞亚Safari','Habarana-Polonnaruwa Road, Habarana','','','#ERROR!','','','','',0,0,'','','Minneriya National Park is a national park in North Central Province of Sri Lanka. The area was designated as a national park on 12 August 1997. The tank is of historical importance, having been built by King Mahasen in third century AD. The park is a dry season feeding ground for the elephant population dwelling in forests of Matale, Polonnaruwa, and Trincomalee districts.','斯里兰卡全国拥有多达九个国家公园，其中米内日亚国家公园虽属面积较细小的一个，但占地也有九十平方公里，而园内那个玛哈辛国王在三世纪修建的巨大蓄水湖，面积更是该国数一数二的。蓄水湖区在旱季时露出青草，吸引附近生物到来栖息，包括来自马塔拉、波隆纳鲁瓦和亭可马里等地区的象群，也会在这时来到绿草茵茵的湖畔寻找水源和嫩草，有时会多达2-300头。所以米内日亚国家公园是该国其中一个最重要的大象栖息地。',0,9012,136,7,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Activities/Jeep%20Safari%20to%20Minneriya%20Elephant%20Park/Thumb%20Jeep%20Safari%20to%20Minneriya%20Elephant%20Park.jpg','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Activities/Jeep%20Safari%20to%20Minneriya%20Elephant%20Park/Jeep%20Safari%20to%20Minneriya%20Elephant%20Park.html','',99),(6,'Water Sports','水上活动','Narigama, Sri Lanka','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','Hikkaduwa is the most famours place of surfing at Sri Lanka, there is so many surfing store along the beach, especially Wewala and Narigama.','黑卡杜瓦是斯里兰卡西海岸最著名的冲浪地，这里开设了斯里兰卡最早的冲浪店，是冲浪爱好者的天堂。黑卡杜瓦南部的Wewala海滩和有“冲浪麦加”称号的Narigama海滩之间，沙滩宽阔、海水澎湃汹涌，非常适合初级冲浪者和中级冲浪爱好者。每年11月至次年4月是希卡杜瓦最好的冲浪季节，每年12月这里还会举办世界职业冲浪比赛。',0,8021,125,8,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Activities/Water%20Sports/Thumb%20Water%20Sports.jpg','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Activities/Water%20Sports/Water%20Sports.html','',99),(7,'Moonstone Mining Visit','月光石','update later...','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','','在Meetiyagoda的月光石开采工厂，你可以看到月光石从开采，原始到打磨成型的全过程。喜爱宝石的你千万不要错过。',0,3069,69,8,1,'','','','',99),(8,'River Safari Boat Ride on Madu River','Madu河游船','update later...','','','','','4500LKR','4500卢比','',0,0,'','','A little more than an hour boat ride takes you through the mangroves, and past islands where locals eat by fishing..Cinnamon island an elderly gentleman will show you the way he harvests the leaves and processes it to produce oils and other products by hand.','独具斯里兰卡风格的肉桂树木，配上殖民风格，这就是madu河上的游船了。小船带你穿梭在茂密的红树林中，同时你还可以看到生活在湿地环境中丰富多样的动植物物种。这里有上百种鸟类栖息，还有蜥蜴、鳄鱼在此出没，鱼和虾也很丰富，是观鸟探险的圣地。',0,9280,119,8,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Activities/River%20Safari%20Boat%20Ride%20on%20Madu%20River/Thumb%20River%20Safari%20Boat%20Ride%20on%20Madu%20River.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Activities/River%20Safari%20Boat%20Ride%20on%20Madu%20River/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Activities/River%20Safari%20Boat%20Ride%20on%20Madu%20River/River%20Safari%20Boat%20Ride%20on%20Madu%20River.mp3',99),(9,'Bicycle Tour of Anuradhapura','阿努拉德普勒古城骑自行车','Anuradhapura,Sri Lanka','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','','',0,6195,140,10,1,'','','','',99),(10,'Kinniya Hot Springs','坎尼亚温泉','Kanniya Hot Water Well, Trincomalee','','','','','','50卢比','',0,0,'','','Kanniya Hot Springs is famous hot well in Sri Lanka from the past. There are seven wells in a square shape. Wells are only 3–4 feet deep and you can clearly see the bottom. The temperature is considerably high but vary from one spring to another. Wells run out of water, when 10-15 buckets of water are taken out.\nIn the ancient time, there was a Buddhist temple complex in this site and the entrance is a part of a Buddhist monastery.','坎尼亚温泉（Kanniya Hot Water Wells）又名“七口井”，位于亭可马里城西5公里的坎尼亚（Kanniya），传说这是印度教魔王拉瓦纳用剑挖出的温泉。坎尼亚温泉共有七个井口，每一个井口的水温各不相同。当地的泰米尔人将其视为神水，据说可以治疗多种疾病，每年都有来自斯里兰卡各地的印度教徒前来沐浴。',0,7135,91,11,1,'','','','',99),(11,'White Water Rafting','漂流','update later...','','','#ERROR!','','','','',0,0,'','','White Water Rafting is a challenging recreational activity and an exhilarating water sport. Yet contrary to the public belief, White Water Rafting is not a sport that demands great physical strength.','斯里兰卡的漂流胜地位于斯里兰卡的腹地——基图加勒（Kitulgala），高山茶园附近。对于一个初级的漂流爱好者，湍急的河流带给你颤栗的同时，也伴随着壮观的景色可供欣赏，途中会路过斯里兰卡乡村，顺道就能欣赏乡村生活的景象。对于专业的漂流爱好者，在老天爷赏脸的情况下，可以去一些极具挑战性的河流小试身手。',0,7093,85,9,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Activities/White%20Water%20Rafting/Thumb%20White%20Water%20Rafting.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Activities/White%20Water%20Rafting/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Activities/White%20Water%20Rafting/White%20Water%20Rafting.html','',99),(12,'Water Activities','人体漂流 & 跳潭','update later...','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','','',0,4054,105,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Activities/Water%20Activities/Thumb%20Water%20Activities.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Activities/Water%20Activities/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Activities/Water%20Activities/Water%20Activities.html','',99),(13,'Udawatta Kele Sanctuary','乌达瓦塔凯勒保护区','Buwelikada Kandy, Sri Lanka','','','','','644LKR','644卢比','',0,0,'','','Udawatta Kele Sanctuary, often spelled as Udawattakele, is a historic forest reserve on a hill-ridge in the city of Kandy. It is 104 hectares (257 acres) large. During the days of the Kandyan kingdom, Udawatta Kele was known as \"Uda Wasala Watta\" in Sinhalese meaning \"the garden above the royal palace\". The sanctuary is famous for its extensive avifauna. The reserve also contains a great variety of plant species, especially lianas, shrubs and small trees. There are several giant lianas. Many of ','乌达瓦塔凯勒保护区又称作Udawattakele，僧伽罗语“皇宫上面的花园”的意思，是康堤北部山上一座历史悠久的森林保护区。传说历史上曾有一位僧伽罗语皇帝逃难到此地。乌达瓦塔凯勒保护区以丰富的鸟类(80多种)而闻名，活跃着豪猪、鹿、金喉拟啄木鸟、斯里兰卡短尾鹦鹉和灰白地鸫等特殊鸟类。该保护区的植被种类繁多，大量哺乳动物在此繁衍生息，是斯里兰卡儿童的科普教育基地。同时，乌达瓦塔凯勒保护区还是重要的佛教隐身冥想修行地，因为这里有一个婆罗门修行的洞穴。到访此处的中国游客非常少，不过近两年有所上升。',0,9994,119,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Activities/Udawatta%20Kele%20Sanctuary/Thumb%20Udawatta%20Kele%20Sanctuary.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Activities/Udawatta%20Kele%20Sanctuary/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Activities/Udawatta%20Kele%20Sanctuary/Udawatta%20Kele%20Sanctuary.mp3',99),(14,'Tea Garden Glenloch','格伦洛奇茶厂','The Glen Loch Tea Estate is one of the oldest estates in the area and boasts to be more than 100 yea','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','The Glen Loch Tea Estate is one of the oldest estates in the area and boasts to be more than 100 years old.\nThe staff is nice and courteous. They have very intricate knowledge of the picking and processing of tea.\nTea tasting session was interesting and we tasted 4 kinds of tea.\nShopping area is a bit premium but you can buy some exclusive stuff if you are a chai fan.','这里群山延绵起伏，云遮雾绕，茶园众多，满山都是成片的茶树，空气清新，景色优美。茶山在云雾中若隐若现，恍若仙境。 茶园内还会有身穿民族服装的接待员带领参观并讲解锡兰茶的制作流程和工艺。',0,6810,131,2,1,'','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Activities/Tea%20Garden%20Glenloch/vtour/tour.html','','',99),(15,'Gamini Gems','Gamini Gems','update later...','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','It\'s such a nice place to know about gems and jewellery. You will watch movie about this ancient industry. You can take a look in this museum as it have wide variety of gems of different type, colour and size.','',0,8068,149,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Activities/Gamini%20Gems/Thumb%20Gamini%20Gems.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Activities/Gamini%20Gems/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Activities/Gamini%20Gems/Gamini%20Gems.mp3',99),(16,'Kapparathota Anchorage','Kapparathota Anchorage','update later...','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','','',0,9910,103,3,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Activities/Kapparathota%20Anchorage/Thumb%20Kapparathota%20Anchorage.jpg','','','',99),(17,'Unuwatuna Beach','Unuwatuna Beach','update later...','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','','',0,8345,117,3,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Activities/Unuwatuna%20Beach/Thumb%20Unuwatuna%20Beach.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Activities/Unuwatuna%20Beach/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Activities/Unuwatuna%20Beach/Unuwatuna%20Beach.html','',99),(18,'Safari - Yala','Safari - Yala','Yala National Park','','','#ERROR!','','3000LKR','3000卢比','',0,0,'','','Situated in Sri Lanka’s south-east hugging the panoramic Indian Ocean, Yala was designated a wildlife sanctuary in 1900 and was designated a national park in 1938. Ironically, the park was initially used as a hunting ground for the elite under British rule. Yala is home to 44 varieties of mammal and 215 bird species. Among its more famous residents are the world’s biggest concentration of leopards, majestic elephants, sloth bears, sambars, jackals, spotted dear, peacocks, and crocodiles. The bes','',0,8997,126,6,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Activities/Safari%20-%20Yala/Thumb%20Safari%20-%20Yala.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Activities/Safari%20-%20Yala/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Activities/Safari%20-%20Yala/Safari%20-%20Yala.mp3',99),(19,'Elephant Ride','Elephant Ride','update later...','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','','',0,9952,131,7,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Activities/Elephant%20Ride/Thumb%20Elephant%20Ride.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Activities/Elephant%20Ride/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Activities/Elephant%20Ride/Elephant%20Ride.html','',99),(21,'Bali Safari and Marine Park','巴厘岛野生动物园','Jl. Prof Ida Bagus Mantra Km, 19.8, 80551, Indonesia','周一-周日 ','9:00 - 21:00',' +62 361 95000','http://www.balisafarimarinepark.com/home','','Jungle Hopper套餐为成人49美元，儿童39美元。','',0,0,'','','Bali Safari & Marine Park, home for more than 60 different species of animals, continues to develop its facilities for the pleasure of its visitors. After 2 years of successful operations, the Night Safari has become a signature at the park along with the Safari Journey, Bali Agung Show, Elephant Safari, Tsavo Lion Restaurant, Mara River Safari Lodge, Funzone and Waterpark.','巴厘岛野生动物园位于吉安雅，占地40公顷，2007年10月开幕。园区中设有儿童游乐园、玻璃景观餐厅、传统舞蹈表演等，还可搭乘园区专车与动物近距离接触。在这里你会看到包括科莫多巨蜥在内的超过百种动物和数十种野生动物的自然栖息地，从亚洲的热带雨林一直到非洲大草原。',0,5769,91,21,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/South/Activities/Bali%20Safari%20and%20Marine%20Park/Thumb%20Bali%20Safari%20and%20Marine%20Park.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Activities/Bali%20Safari%20and%20Marine%20Park/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Activities/Bali%20Safari%20and%20Marine%20Park/Bali%20Safari%20and%20Marine%20Park.mp3',99),(22,'Dolphin Play','海豚互动公园','Jl. Tangkuban Perahu, Sanur, Denpasar, Indonesia','周一-周日 ','9:00-15:00','+62 361 4730218','http://www.balidolphins.com/','','','',0,0,'','','Experience the thrill and joy of interaction with friendly dolphins Bali, it\'s fun, educational and memorable, an unforgettable encounter of a lifetime! pat, interact and perform various trick and activities with our friendly and intelligent dolphins.','这是一个多么难得的经历，当你来巴厘岛时，一定要做的，在这里你将获得一次与海豚亲密接触的美好体验。这里的服务很出色,他们很显然都特别爱海豚，真是一个充满爱的好地方。',0,9987,148,21,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/South/Activities/Dolphin%20Play/Thumb%20Dolphin%20Play.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Activities/Dolphin%20Play/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Activities/Dolphin%20Play/Dolphin%20Play.mp3',99),(23,'Kintamani Volcano','京打马尼火山','Kintamani is in the centre of Bangli District, within an approximate 2.5-hour transfer from Denpasar','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','Bali volcano, also referred to as Kintamani volcano or Mount Batur as a whole, is a popular sightseeing destination in Bali\'s central highlands. The magnificent views of the 13sqkm Batur caldera lake serves as the main attraction, surrounded by the captivating Mount Batur range.','京打马尼火山位于巴厘北部山区。3万年前京打马尼形成了一处巨大的火山口，宽约3公里。京打马尼火山是一个地区，包括著名的巴图尔火山和巴图尔湖。巴图尔山是一座活火山，而巴图尔湖就在火山口里。从火山口边缘看上去,整个地方尽收眼底,包括湖泊,景色无比壮观。在火山西边,还能看见黑色的熔岩流。',0,8630,117,25,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/Middle&North/Activities/Kintamani%20Volcano/Thumb%20Kintamani%20Volcano.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Middle&North/Activities/Kintamani%20Volcano/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Middle&North/Activities/Kintamani%20Volcano/Kintamani%20Volcano.mp3',99),(24,'Boat Cruising to Brijuni National Park','布里俄尼群岛国家公园轮渡','Brijuni National Park, Croatia','','','385 (0) 52 525 888','http://www.np-brijuni.hr/en/','','','',0,0,'','','The Maker intended to shape a part of the Earth to the image of Heaven. That is how Istria came into being, like a garden covered with magnificent trees and vast meadows, washed by the deep blue sea, appealing people to a happier life. But the jealous devil destroyed his work by tearing the bag in which the angel was carrying the unused stones. Thousands of rocks scattered around the Istrian land making it a land of contrasts, gentle and rough, fertile and barren, sunny and cloudy. The desolated','布里俄尼群岛国家公园坐落于克罗地亚的伊斯特拉县，由位于克罗地亚北部亚得里亚海的14个岛屿组成，面积约8平方千米，其中最大岛屿的面积为5.6平方千米，公园因天然的美景而备受亲睐。\n这个旖旎多姿的国家公园由美丽的小岛、狭长的海岸线、绵延的海滩、茂密的树林、稀奇的动物组成，是大自然馈赠给人类最宝贵的自然资源。正是由于公园的静谧、优雅和神秘才吸引了世界游客的造访，已经成为克罗地亚最知名的度假胜地。公园所在地还是克罗地亚最知名的历史遗址，为远近闻名的考古胜地，如罗马时代的罗斯卡别墅和鱼塘、罗马兵营遗迹、威尼斯时代的遗迹、威力布均上的泰吉索夫军事要塞以及奥匈时期的一个大碉堡等。',0,3189,76,29,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Activities/Boat%20Cruising%20to%20Brijuni%20National%20Park/Thumb%20Boat%20Cruising%20to%20Brijuni%20National%20Park.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Activities/Boat%20Cruising%20to%20Brijuni%20National%20Park/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Activities/Boat%20Cruising%20to%20Brijuni%20National%20Park/Boat%20Cruising%20to%20Brijuni%20National%20Park.mp3',99),(25,'Boat in Plitvice Lakes National Park','十六湖国家公园游船','Plitvicka jezera, Plitvice Lakes National Park 53231, Croatia','周一 - 周日','07:00-21：00','385 53 751 015','','adult/child 180','55/180库纳','',0,0,'','','National park Plitvice Lakes is considered one of the most beautiful national parks in the world.\nPlitvice Lakes make wonderful blend of oak forests, meadows, rocks and lakes. You can explore them by walking along the lakes, by electric train or electric boat.','普利特维采湖群国家公园，也作布里特威斯湖国家公园，位于克罗地亚中部的喀斯特山区，创立于1949年，为东南欧历史最悠久的国家公园，现在也是克罗地亚最大的国家公园。公园内有许多有石灰岩沉积形成的天然堤坝，这些堤坝又形成了一个个湖泊、洞穴和瀑布。由于主要有16个湖泊，故公园又叫十六湖国家公园。',0,8050,130,28,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Activities/Boat%20in%20Plitvice%20Lakes%20National%20Park/Thumb%20Boat%20in%20Plitvice%20Lakes%20National%20Park.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Activities/Boat%20in%20Plitvice%20Lakes%20National%20Park/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Activities/Boat%20in%20Plitvice%20Lakes%20National%20Park/Boat%20in%20Plitvice%20Lakes%20National%20Park.mp3',99),(26,'Boat to Rab','拉布轮渡','Rab, Croatia','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','The boat to Rab town','前往拉布的轮渡',0,6686,72,30,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Istria/Activities/Boat%20to%20Rab/Thumb%20Boat%20to%20Rab.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Activities/Boat%20to%20Rab/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Activities/Boat%20to%20Rab/Boat%20to%20Rab.mp3',99),(27,'Flying Squirrels','丛林飞鼠','Flying Squirrels Chiang Mai, Thailand','','','66-53-278989-90','http://www.treetopflight.com/','2699THB','2699泰铢','中文',0,0,'','','Flying Squirrels Zip Line Chiang Mai is a truly incredible treetop adventure experience created by a select group of fun-loving experts who have engineered a one-of-a-kind attraction. Come FLY through our action-packed, 32 station course featuring jungle paths, zip lines, sky bridges, climbing nets, repelling lines, a crazy zipwire skateboard, Tarzan mega jump, gigantic exit slide, and Northern Thailand’s only treetop high-wire bicycle ride through lush rainforest canopy.','丛林飞跃Flying Squirrels，是清迈四大家丛林飞跃中最新的一家，因其优越的环境设备和服务受到很多顾客的好评，除此之外它还将之前各家丛林飞跃项目的长处综合在了一起，推出了许多新鲜刺激的飞行项目，如：空中自行车、空中滑板、高空网强等项目受到了众多游客的青睐。Flying Squirrel使用的器械都是专业的Petzl品牌，而且工作人员的操做都很专业。十分值得一提的是这家的教练全都是来自于之前澳大利亚公司Flight of Gibbon 的专业人士。',0,6284,116,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Activities/Flying%20Squirrels/Thumb%20Flying%20Squirrels.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(28,'School Visiting','参观学校','Sigiria','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','','百见独家亲子活动，带你深入兰卡，参观当地学校，体验最纯正的锡兰文化。',0,8359,95,7,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Activities/School%20Visiting/Thumb%20School%20Visiting.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(29,'Exciting','Exciting','','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','','',0,5946,132,48,13,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1500864534/Thumb%20point%20Saipan/Managaha/Activities/Exciting/Thumb%20Exciting.jpg',NULL,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1500864534/video_utovr/video/Saipan/Managaha/Activities/Exciting/Exciting.html',NULL,99),(30,'Skydiving','Skydiving','','','','','','','','',0,0,'','','','',0,8654,144,48,13,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1500864534/Thumb%20point%20Saipan/Managaha/Activities/Skydiving/Thumb%20Skydiving.jpg',NULL,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1500864534/video_utovr/video/Saipan/Managaha/Activities/Skydiving/Skydiving.html',NULL,99);
