INSERT INTO `City` VALUES (1,'Colombo','科伦坡','The garden city of the East, Colombo has emerged as a must-see stop in Sri Lanka.','科伦坡是斯里兰卡首都和最大的城市，素有“东方十字路口”之称。科伦坡是一座典型的东南亚海滨城市，这里有旖旎的滨海风光，也有喧闹的夜市赌场。',257,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Thumb%20Colombo.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Colombo/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Colombo/Colombo.mp3'),(2,'Kandy','康提','Kandy is a tempting taste of the tropicsis the Temple of the Tooth','康提是斯里兰卡旧都，经历了僧伽罗王朝和殖民统治。背山面水的康提还有佛牙寺，那里供奉着佛祖释迦牟尼的牙齿。',483,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Thumb%20Kandy.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Kandy/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Kandy/Kandy.mp3'),(3,'Galle & Merissa','加勒&美瑞莎','Galle is the timeless song of the sea','加勒位于斯里兰卡西南，处于印度洋的海滨上。加勒老城的存在充分展现了17世纪与19世纪期间欧洲建筑与南亚传统建筑之间的相互影响。',245,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Thumb%20Galle%20&%20Merissa.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Galle%20&%20Merissa/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Galle%20&%20Merissa.mp3'),(4,'Negombo','尼甘布','Negombo is sand, sails and the sea','尼甘布是一个海边小镇，这里的风情比起都市更为原始，这里盛产龙虾、螃蟹、对虾等，鱼市上有本地渔民从海里打捞上来的新鲜海产。',177,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Thumb%20Negombo.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Negombo/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Negombo/Negombo.mp3'),(5,'Nuwara Eliya','努瓦勒埃利耶','Nuwara Eliya is mist swirling through the hillsis splashes of colour amongst the tea pla','努瓦勒埃利耶意为“旷野之城”或者“城市之光”,是斯里兰卡中部核心城市,被称为亚洲的花园城市,以其小山、峡谷和瀑布闻名。',100,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Thumb%20Nuwara%20Eliya.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Nuwara%20Eliya/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Nuwara%20Eliya/Nuwara%20Eliya.mp3'),(6,'Tissamaharama & Yala','提瑟默哈拉默&雅拉国家公园','In Tissamaharama, eyes are automatically drawn upwards and outwards.','雅拉国家公园位于斯里兰卡东南部,距科伦坡300公里,占地1250平方公里,是斯里兰卡游客到访最多的国家公园。',370,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Thumb%20Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala.mp3'),(7,'Sigiriya & Dambulla','锡吉里耶&丹布拉','Sigiriya is carved from the bedrock','锡吉里耶，位于高约200米的“狮子岩”上，锡吉里耶壁画是斯里兰卡历史上唯一流传下来的非宗教题材壁画',149,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Thumb%20Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla.mp3'),(8,'Bentota & Hikkaduwa','本托塔&黑卡杜瓦','The ribbon of golden sand that makes up Bentota beach is a glorious holiday sun-and-fun playground.','本托塔因拥有斯里兰卡著名的黄金海滩,现已是著名的海滨旅游胜地。被誉为“斯里兰卡的天堂”。',487,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Thumb%20Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa.mp3'),(9,'Ella & Hatton','埃勒&哈顿','Ella is everyone’s favourite hill-country village','锡兰美丽的茶园小火车，罗摩衍那神秘的传说和背包客向往的户外，组成了多彩的埃勒。',139,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Thumb%20Ella%20&%20Hatton.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Ella%20&%20Hatton/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Ella%20&%20Hatton.mp3'),(10,'Anuradhapura','阿努拉德普勒','Anuradhapura is a garden of dagobas','阿努拉德普勒拥有2500年历史，在公元前380年成为斯里兰卡首都，并且在之后的一千年，都是斯里兰卡王权所在地。',85,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Thumb%20Anuradhapura.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Anuradhapura/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Anuradhapura/Anuradhapura.mp3'),(11,'Trincomalee','亭可马里','This historic city is old almost beyond reckoning: it’s possibly the site of historic Gokana in the Mahavamsa (Great Chronicle)','亭可马里历史极为悠久，有许多宗教和人文遗迹，同时还拥有印度洋无敌海景。',410,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Thumb%20Trincomalee.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Trincomalee/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Trincomalee/Trincomalee.mp3'),(12,'Bangkok','曼谷','One of the busiest cities of the world, Bangkok is a vibrate mix of East and West.','曼谷是中南半岛最大城市，东南亚第二大城市，它是融合东西方文化、包罗万象的\"天使之城\"，同时也是贵金属和宝石的交易中心。',393,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Bangkok/Thumb%20Bangkok.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Bangkok/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Bangkok/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Bangkok/Bangkok.mp3'),(13,'Sukhothai','素可泰','Sukhothai was the capital of the Sukhothai Kingdom. Sukhothai is 12 km west of the modern city of Sukhothai Thani.','素可泰位居曼谷以北440公里的地区，不但是泰国国的第一个首都，也是泰文化的摇篮，泰国的文字、艺术、文化与法规，很多都是由素可泰时代开始创立的',235,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Sukhothai/Thumb%20Sukhothai.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Sukhothai/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Sukhothai/Sukhothai/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Sukhothai/Sukhothai/Sukhothai.mp3'),(14,'Chiang Mai','清迈','Chiang Mai is the largest city in northern Thailand. It is the capital of Chiang Mai Province and was a former capital of the Kingdom of Lan Na.','泰国第二大城市，是清迈府的首府，也是泰国北部政治、经济、文化的中心，其发达程度仅次于首都曼谷。市内风景秀丽，遍植花草，尤以玫瑰花最为著名。',396,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Chiang%20Mai/Thumb%20Chiang%20Mai.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Chiang%20Mai/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Chiang%20Mai/Chiang%20Mai/vtour/tour.html','',''),(15,'Krabi','甲米','Krabi is the main town in the province of Krabi on the west coast of southern Thailand at the mouth of the Krabi River where it empties in Phang Nga B','泰国南部的甲米是一个有如天堂的热带半岛，这里到处诗情画意，美不胜收。甲米拥有风光旖旎的岛屿和浓厚的本土文化，丰富的植被和动物种群也闻名遐迩。',325,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Krabi/Thumb%20Krabi.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Krabi/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Krabi/Krabi/vtour/tour.html','',''),(16,'Pattaya','芭提雅','Sand,sunand fun make Pattaya one of the most popular destinations for visitors toThailand.','芭提雅是泰国一处著名海景度假胜地，素以阳光、沙滩、海鲜名扬世界，美丽的海景、最负盛名的人妖表演，还有缤纷无休的夜文化，吸引着全世界的游客。',386,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Pattaya/Thumb%20Pattaya.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Pattaya/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Pattaya/Pattaya/vtour/tour.html','',''),(17,'Phuket','普吉岛','Phuket is one of the southern provinces of Thailand. It consists of the island of Phuket, the country\'s largest island, and another 32 smaller islands','普吉岛以其迷人的热带风光和丰富的旅游资源被称为\"安达曼海上的一颗明珠\"，而且自然资源十分丰富，有\"珍宝岛\"、\"金银岛\"的美称。',459,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Phuket/Thumb%20Phuket.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Phuket/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Phuket/Phuket/vtour/tour.html','',''),(18,'Ko Samui','苏梅岛','Ko Samui is an island off the east coast of the Kra Isthmus,Thailand. Geographically in the Chumphon Archipelago, it is part of Surat Thani Province, ','苏梅岛位于泰国湾，是全国第三大岛，面积247㎞2，距大陆约80公里，周围有80个大小岛屿，但多无人居住，它距苏叻府仅84公里，属于真正的岛屿',187,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Ko%20Samui/Thumb%20Ko%20Samui.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20Thailand/Ko%20Samui/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Ko%20Samui/Ko%20Samui/vtour/tour.html','',''),(19,'Ko Phi-Phi','皮皮岛','The Phi Phi Islands are an island group in Thailand, between the large island of Phuket and the west Strait of Malacca coast of the mainland. The isla','皮皮岛位于泰国普吉岛东南约20公里处，是由两个主要岛屿组成的姐妹岛，1983年被定为泰国国家公园。这里海水清澈湛蓝，可潜游海底世界。',406,3,'','','','',''),(20,'Ayuthaya','大城','Ayutthaya is the former capital of Phra Nakhon Si Ayutthaya province in Thailand, it was sometimes known as the \"Venice of the East\".','大城为泰国故都，公元1350年以来曾有33代君主在此建都。大城原名为梵文阿耸陀，或译作“阿犹