INSERT INTO `Hotel` VALUES (1,'The Hill Club','希尔俱乐部酒店','The Hill Club, 29 Grand Hotel Road,Nuwara Eliya, 22200, Sri Lanka','#ERROR!','http://www.hillclubsrilanka.lk/',3,39,'',8,0,'The “Little England of Sri Lanka – Nuwara Eliya” is a fabulous gateway located amidst the addictive scenic beauty of the misty Blue Mountains, which is just the right spot to curl up in comforts, away from the work-o-holic routine of our lives.','The Hill Club俱乐部酒店被努沃勒埃利耶郁郁葱葱的绿树环绕，拥有典型的英伦风格。酒店设有3个餐饮场所，包括所有仅供男性使用的酒廊酒吧。酒店的部分区域有着装要求',0,8361,91,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/The%20Hill%20Club/Thumb%20The%20Hill%20Club.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/The%20Hill%20Club/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/The%20Hill%20Club/The%20Hill%20Club.mp3',99),(2,'Jetwing St Andrews Hotel','圣安德鲁杰特威酒店','Jetwing St. Andrews, Nuwara Eliya, 22200, Sri Lanka','','http://www.jetwinghotels.com/jetwingstandrews/',4,51,'',8,0,'Amidst mountains swathed in mist and dotted with tea plantations, stands the quaint old mansion of Jetwing St. Andrews. A former country house converted into a Jetwing Hotel, life at Jetwing St. Andrews is reminiscent of the days of the British Rulers.','Jetwing St. Andrew\'s酒店的海拔是1884米，坐落在斯里兰卡的Nuwara Eliya山城，为客人提供豪华的5星级住宿。这家迷人的都铎风格的酒店提供免费无线网络连接、免费停车场和骑马。',0,4255,117,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/Jetwing%20St%20Andrews%20Hotel/Thumb%20Jetwing%20St%20Andrews%20Hotel.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/Jetwing%20St%20Andrews%20Hotel/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/Jetwing%20St%20Andrews%20Hotel/Jetwing%20St%20Andrews%20Hotel.mp3',99),(3,'The Grand Hotel','橘子集团酒店','Grand Hotel Rd, Nuwara Eliya City Center, Nuwara Eliya, 22200, Sri Lanka','','http://www.grand-hotel-nuwara-eliya-sri-lanka.en.w',4,161,'',7.4,0,'Grand Hotel is an excellent architectural structure of the Elizabethan era and is also the former mansion of Sir Edward Barnes who was the Governor of Sri Lanka during 1830-1850. With luxury settings and an ambience of ancient times where royalty roamed, this hotel offers a range of facilities to make your holiday in the hill country a perfect one. From exotic buffets and a la carte dishes, the hotel caters for various occasions and events.','Grand Hotel酒店位于Nuwara Eliya Hill山，毗邻Nuwar Eliya高尔夫球场。酒店被热带植物所包围，并享受凉爽的气候，设有2间餐厅、一个购物商场和一间健身房。该酒店是伊丽莎白时代的优秀建筑，在1830-1850年期间也是巴恩斯爱德华爵士的豪宅',0,7189,62,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/The%20Grand%20Hotel/Thumb%20The%20Grand%20Hotel.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/The%20Grand%20Hotel/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/The%20Grand%20Hotel/The%20Grand%20Hotel.mp3',99),(4,'Langdale by Amaya Boutique Resort','阿马亚朗戴尔精品度假酒店','Radalla, Nuwara eliya, Nuwara Eliya, 22200, Sri Lanka','#ERROR!','https://www.amayaresorts.com/amayalangdale/en/',5,13,'',6.9,0,'In the hill country in the centre of Sri Lanka, nestles ‘the city of light’, Nuwara Eliya. Amidst majestic mountains, lush gardens and the finest tea, Amaya Langdale, a stately century-old manor, takes you back to a simpler time','Amaya Langdale酒店的客房享有茶树种植园（Tea Estate）时代的特色，设有深色木质地板和古典家具。客房设有卫星电视、1张沙发和沏茶设施。入住宁静的Langdale酒店的客人可以在风景秀丽的地带远足。客人可以在桑拿浴室或蒸汽浴室放松，?也可以在Ayurvedic水疗区享受按摩服务。',0,6192,109,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/Langdale%20by%20Amaya%20Boutique%20Resort/Thumb%20Langdale%20by%20Amaya%20Boutique%20Resort.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/Langdale%20by%20Amaya%20Boutique%20Resort/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/Langdale%20by%20Amaya%20Boutique%20Resort/Langdale%20by%20Amaya%20Boutique%20Resort.mp3',99),(5,'Heritance Tea Factory','茶厂遗产酒店','Kandapola, Nuwara Eliya, Sri Lanka','#ERROR!','http://www.heritancehotels.com/teafactory/',5,54,'',8.6,0,'Heavy mist rolls in, a chill breeze swirls across the valley, dew glistens and glimmers on fresh green leaves – acres of them, over into the distance. Indoors, a cloak of warmth embraces, centuries of tea hangs infused in the air. Have you returned to 19th century Ceylon?','Heritance Tea Factory酒店是以前旧茶厂改造而成的，外表是灰白长方体，正是艾丽亚地区所有红茶工厂的一致外观。现在里面还保留了很多以前茶厂的印记，酒店在山上，时而大雾弥漫，时而阳光灿烂。在里面可以参观古老的制茶工具跟工艺，还有复古的电梯等设备可以感受英伦风情。',0,6375,108,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/Heritance%20Tea%20Factory/Thumb%20Heritance%20Tea%20Factory.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/Heritance%20Tea%20Factory/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Hotels/Heritance%20Tea%20Factory/Heritance%20Tea%20Factory.mp3',99),(6,'Shangri-La\'s Resort and Spa - Hambantota','香格里拉汉班托塔度假酒店','Sittrakala Estate, Chithragala, Ambalantota, Sri Lanka','#ERROR!','http://www.shangri-la.com/cn/hambantota/shangrila/',5,300,'',8.7,0,'Shangri-La\'s Hambantota Resort & Spa is located along the ancient Spice Route in a city steeped in rich history. Hambantota is known for its natural beauty and wildlife, and allows visitors to explore Asia’s most fascinating nature sanctuaries, including the Yala, Udawalawe, Lunugamvehera and Bundala National Parks.','斯里兰卡香格里拉汉班托塔度假酒店以城市的厚重历史底蕴为依托，坐落于古老的香料之路上，俯瞰质朴迷人的斯里兰卡南海岸。汉班托塔自然环境优美，拥有众多野生动物园，包括雅拉（Yala）国家公园、乌达瓦拉维（Udawalawe）国家公园、鲁努岗维赫罗（Lunugamvehera）国家公园以及本达拉（Bundala）国家公园，是游客探索亚洲最迷人自然保护区的首选之地。',0,3272,66,6,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Hotels/Shangri-La\'s%20Resort%20and%20Spa%20-%20Hambantota/Thumb%20Shangri-La\'s%20Resort%20and%20Spa%20-%20Hambantota.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Tissamah