eatments at the Ayurveda Spa. The hotel can help guests arrange for windsurfing or water skiing activities by the beach. Laundry and dry cleaning services are offered.','位于Negombo市的Goldi Sands Hotel酒店四周环绕着荷兰殖民建筑，距离Bandaranaike国际机场15分钟车程，设有滨海住宿、免费停车场和淡水室外泳池。\r\n\r\n空调客房设有可俯瞰美丽的印度洋的私人阳台。每间客房均设有迷你吧、沏茶/咖啡设施和平面电视。\r\n',0,5477,149,4,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Hotels/Goldi%20Sands%20Hotel/Thumb%20Goldi%20Sands%20Hotel.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(75,'Elephas Resort','埃勒法斯酒店',' Audangawa, Sigiriya 50150, Sri Lanka','','http://www.elephassigiriya.com/',4,32,'',8,0,'\r\nRenovated in 2013, the Elephas Hotel guarantees guests a pleasant stay whether in Sigiriya for business or pleasure. The excitement of the city center is only 9.4 km away. Visitors to the hotel can take pleasure in touring the city\'s top attractions: Habarana Hospital, Archaeological Museum, Citadel of Sigiriya - Lion Rock.','埃勒法斯酒店位于锡吉里耶的哈巴拉纳，是十分受旅客欢迎的订房选择。 在这里，住客们可轻松前往市区内各大旅游、购物、餐饮地点。 这家酒店气氛闲适安逸，而且与Habarana Hospital, 考古博物馆, Citadel of Sigiriya - Lion Rock等景点相距不远。',0,6571,64,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498705713/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dumbulla/Hotels/Elephas%20Resort/Thumb%20Elephas%20Resort.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(76,'Pigeon Island Resort','鸽子岛度假村','11th Milepost, Nilaveli, Trincomalee','','http://www.pigeonislandresort.com/',3,0,'',8.3,0,'Pigeon Island is located North from Tincomalee out of Nilaveli on the most beautiful among all sandy beaches in Sri Lanka.\r\n\r\nThe place is really idyllic and delighting, you will find here peace and serenity.','',0,6423,123,11,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Hotels/Pigeon%20Island%20Resort/Thumb%20Pigeon%20Island%20Resort.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(77,'Little Eden Hotel','小伊甸园酒店','update later...','','',0,0,'',0,0,'','',0,9401,73,40,9,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1500859969/Thumb%20point%20Laos/Don%20Det/Hotels/Little%20Eden%20Hotel/Thumb%20Little%20Eden%20Hotel.