rants/Midnight%20Kai%20Don/Thumb%20Midnight%20Kai%20Don.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Midnight%20Kai%20Don/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Midnight%20Kai%20Don/Midnight%20Kai%20Don.mp3',99),(17,'Mango Tango','Mango Tango','Siam Squares Soi 3 | RamaOne Road, Pathumwan,Bangkok','','','','We serve the best mango in Thailand.','泰国的“许留山”','serve the best mango in Thailand. Meet us at MangoTango Siam Square, Asiatique, Nimmanhaemin soi 13 Chiangmai.','全泰国连锁的知名甜品店，是泰国的“许留山”.出镜率极高的一家甜品店，几乎所有来到清迈的游客都会到此，品尝芒果糯米饭和冰淇淋，如今已经被国人占领了。','','http://www.mymangotango.com/','',0,0,0,3401,58,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Mango%20Tango/Thumb%20Mango%20Tango.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Mango%20Tango/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Mango%20Tango/Mango%20Tango.mp3',99),(18,'Thanon Maha Rat','推车橙汁','update later...','','','','','','','曼谷街头有很多这种果汁摊的，果汁做好装瓶后放在冰渣上面冷藏，喝的时候就是凉凉的很解暑。橙汁是基本款，一般也就二三十铢的样子，还有其他水果的，芒果百香果火龙果之类的，不同水果价格有时不太一样。','','','',0,0,0,6247,128,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Thanon%20Maha%20Rat/Thumb%20Thanon%20Maha%20Rat.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Thanon%20Maha%20Rat/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Thanon%20Maha%20Rat/Thanon%20Maha%20Rat.mp3',99),(19,'MK Restaurants Central World','MK餐厅','Central World Zen, 4, 4 / 1-2, Central World, 7th Floor, Rajdamri Road, Pathumwan, Khet Pathumwan, B','周一-周日','10:00-22:00','','','','','泰国最有名的火锅店，味道可口价格公道','66-2-2556578','','',0,0,0,4034,125,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/MK%20Restaurants%20Central%20World/Thumb%20MK%20Restaurants%20Central%20World.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/MK%20Restaurants%20Central%20World/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/MK%20Restaurants%20Central%20World/MK%20Restaurants%20Central%20World.mp3',99),(20,'China town','唐人街','update later...','','09:00 - 16:00','','','小香港既视感','Bangkok’s Chinatown is a popular tourist attraction and a food haven for new generation gourmands who flock here after sunset to explore the vibrant street-side cuisine. At day time, it’s no less busy, as hordes of shoppers descend upon this 1-km strip and adjacent Charoenkrung Road to get a day’s worth of staple, trade gold, or pay a visit to one of the Chinese temples.','曼谷唐人街位于曼谷中心西南部，是城区最繁华的商业区之一，由三聘街、耀华力路、石龙军路三条大街以及许多街巷连接而成，以耀花力路为中轴。曼谷唐人街有很多餐馆，经营的燕窝、鱼翅很便宜，不妨去尝一下。这里夜间会变成海鲜夜排档，价廉物美。','','','',0,0,0,5427,86,12,3,'','','','',99),(21,'Khao San Road','考山路','Khao San Road in Bangkok, Thailand','','','','backpacker ghetto','背包客聚集地','Khaosan Road or Khao San Road is a short street in central Bangkok, Thailand constructed in 1892 during the reign of Rama V. It is in the Banglamphu area of about 1 kilometre north of the Grand Palace and Wat Phra Kaew.\"Khaosan\" translates as \"milled rice\", a reminder that in former times the street was a major Bangkok rice market. In the last 20 years, however, Khaosan Road has developed into a world-famous \"backpacker ghetto\". It offers cheap accommodation, ranging from \"mattress in a box\" sty','考山路夜市是曼谷最大、最受喜爱的夜市。 ·所有泰国小吃在这都能吃到，米粉汤、炒面、炸春卷、芒果饭、烤串等各种美食，好吃又实惠。街边随处可见各类纪念品小店、SPA和酒吧，即使到了深夜，依然灯火通明。这里住宿便宜又便利，是背包客聚集的地方。','-2596204','','',0,8,0,5036,108,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Khao%20San%20Road/Thumb%20Khao%20San%20Road.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Khao%20San%20Road/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Khao%20San%20Road/Khao%20San%20Road.mp3',99),(22,'Siam Paragon','暹罗百丽宫','Siam Paragon, 991/1 1st Floor, Rama I Road, Bangkok 10330','','','','','','','堪称东南亚最大的购物中心——Siam Paragon，斥资150亿泰铢建立的豪华顶级大卖场，占地50万平方公尺，共有250间商店，要整个逛完得要花上数天时间；除了卖场主体以外、可停4,000部车的大型停车场，和宽广的户外广场，入夜后可观赏水舞。 这家姿态高调、城镇规模的商场把自己比作一颗多面体宝石，它位于一个六层楼的中庭大厅背后，大厅里面装饰着垂直花园和流水瀑布。这里甚至不像一个购物中心，倒像一座城市花园。 商场有十层楼，包括各种商店及餐馆共270多间，以及一家有15间放映室的电影院，亦拥有一个号称东南亚最大的名叫曼谷海洋世界的水族馆及一个展览厅和泰国艺术画廊和歌剧院。还拥有大型保龄球场，卡拉OK。五层是泰国最大的英文书店Kinokuniya。','','www.siamparagon.co.th','',0,0,0,5894,133,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Siam%20Paragon/Thumb%20Siam%20Paragon.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Siam%20Paragon/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Siam%20Paragon/Siam%20Paragon.mp3',99),(23,'Anapuri Villas','Anapuri Villa 晚餐餐厅','Banjar Pabean, Ketewel, Sukawati, Gianyar 80582. Bali, Indonesia.','','','','Stay there, and every guest will be taken by the views of the spectacular Indian Ocean, Nusa Penida Island, and the monumental silhouettes of the sacred mountain in Bali, Mount Agung.','来这里举行一场浪漫的婚礼，感受美味的佳肴','Situated on Bali’s south east coast, Pabean Beach, which only 45 Minutes from Ngurah Rai International airport. Anapuri Villas exclusively offer a luxury private holiday with stunning Badung strait as its view. Centrally located between famous tourist destination in Bali.Anapuri Villas presents the finest standard of hospitality and service in Indonesia to the black volcanic sand of Pabean Beach, Saba Bay. The architect, Guy Morgan, created a complex of boutique Villa which consists of 4 unique ','这是一家非常浪漫的酒店，如果你想要举行一场难忘的婚礼，Anapuri Villas一定是一个理想场所。这家巴厘岛海滨酒店的规模和位置以及灵活的别墅布局，为您和客人提供了众多打造理想空间的选择。可举行4至125位客人的小型或大型婚礼。','62 361 894 6388','http://www.anapurivillas.com/zh/','',5,9,0,4367,90,21,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/South/Restaurants/Anapuri%20Villas/Thumb%20Anapuri%20Villas.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Restaurants/Anapuri%20Villas/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Restaurants/Anapuri%20Villas/Anapuri%20Villas.mp3',99),(24,'Soori Bali','Soori Bali海边烛光晚餐','Kpg. Dukuh | Kerambitan, Tabanan 82111, Indonesia ','','','','uniquely combined with Indonesian hospitality and traditional cultures','该住宿被评为库塔地理位置最佳的下榻之处','With its charming ambience and breathtaking ocean views, The ANVAYA Beach Resort Bali is a tropical hideaway featuring 495 modern and spacious Guestrooms, Suites and Villa with the highest standard of facilities, amenities and professional service, uniquely combined with Indonesian hospitality and traditional cultures.','The Anvaya Beach Resorts Bali度假酒店坐落在库塔（Kuta）的卡迪卡广场（Kartika Plaza）区，距离Waterbom Bali水上乐园500米，提供spa中心、桑拿浴室、室外游泳池、私人海滩区和餐厅。\n每间客房均提供平板卫星电视、水壶、私人浴室、便利的拖鞋和免费洗浴用品。The Anvaya Beach Resorts Bali度假酒店距离Discovery Shopping Mall购物商场500米，距离图班海滩（Tuban Beach）500米，距离最近的机场——伍拉·赖国际机场（Ngurah Rai International Airport）1公里。该住宿也被评为库塔地理位置最佳的下榻之处！和当地其他住宿相比，客人对这家住宿的满意度更高。','(62-21) 2700027','http://www.santika.com/indonesia/kuta/anvaya-beach-resorts-bali/','',0,0,0,8151,101,21,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/South/Hotels/Soori%20Bali/Thumb%20Soori%20Bali.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Hotels/Soori%20Bali/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Hotels/Soori%20Bali/Soori%20Bali.mp3',99),(25,'Dirty Duck','脏鸭餐','Jl Hanoman, Padang Tegal, Ubud','周一-周日','11:00-22:30','','serving delicious food and providing good service in a friendly','脏鸭餐厅是乌布特色饭店之一。','Bebek Bengil (Dirty Duck Diner) was opened in 1990. Since then, we have been serving delicious food and providing good service in a friendly, comfortable and relaxed atmosphere. Many People have asked us how we got the name \'Bebek Bengil\'; well here\'s the story ','脏鸭餐厅是乌布特色饭店之一。饭店坐落在一片稻田之间，田园风光。典型的巴厘岛建筑。鸭子做法也很多有特色。是个吃饭聊天的好地方。脏鸭餐(Dirty duck)应该算是巴厘岛最有名的特色菜了，鸭子烤成棕色，酥脆的鸭肉用手即可撕下，放进嘴里没有油腻的感觉，更难得的是，丝毫没有鸭腥味。餐厅位于乌布，餐厅的连廊下就是整片的稻田，环境十分优美。','-977974','http://www.bebekbengil.co.id/','',0,8,0,3656,87,21,