INSERT INTO `Sight` VALUES (0,'Hassan II Mosque','哈桑二世清真寺','','Hassan II Mosque, Casablanca, Grand Casablanca, Morocco','从市区可乘坐出租或步行抵达景点。','周五及平时礼拜时间不可参观，其','9:00-11:00、15:00-16:','The mosque is commonly thought to be the world\'s third-largest mosque ','世界第三大清真寺，规模仅次于麦加与麦地那清真寺','120DH/30DH','120迪拉姆/人，4-12岁儿童30迪拉姆/人，外国学生60迪拉姆/人，本国学生30迪拉姆/人','212 5224-72620','http://www.mosquee-hassan2.com/en/',0,0,'The mosque was built in 1989. The minaret measuring 200m in height, but the muezzin who comes to make the call to prayer has an elevator to go up. It is the second largest mosque in the world after Mecca! It was built by the French architect Pinseau and Bouygues.C\'est an advanced sea that did not exist before, half the course is actually on the ocean atlantique.On visit the prayer room and then ablution places where we wash before d\'aller pray 5 times a day. This place also has modern touches, chandeliers descending from the ceiling all alone, the sunroof or the protection against earthquakes.','哈桑二世清真寺是世界第三大清真寺，规模仅次于麦加与麦地那清真寺，同时也是世界上现代化程度最高的清真寺。清真寺大殿中大理石地面常年供暖，夏季屋顶可以自动打开散热，寺内有电梯可直达宣礼塔顶，堪称奢华。寺庙有三分之一的部分建于海上，据说是为了纪念那些从海上来到摩洛哥繁衍生息的阿拉伯祖辈。该清真寺是摩洛哥唯一对外国游客开放的寺庙，入寺时需脱鞋脱帽，非穆斯林不可进入主殿参观。',0,5832,136,46,11,'http://africa.beejeen.com/1500862395/Thumb%20point%20Morocco/Casablanca/Sights/Hassan%20II%20Mosque/Thumb%20Hassan%20II%20Mosque.jpg','','http://africa.beejeen.com/1500862395/video_utovr/video/Morocco/Casablanca/Sights/Hassan%20II%20Mosque/Hassan%20II%20Mosque.html','',99),(1,'St Mary\'s Church','圣玛丽教堂','','Main Street, Negombo','步行或者骑自行车即可抵达','','','Thunderous religious ceiling paintings covering the nave','殖民风格建筑，精美壁画','','','#ERROR!','',0,8,'The fading pink chamber of St Mary’s Church, in the town centre, has some thunderous religious ceiling paintings covering the nave.','1874年开始修建，精雕细刻，总共修了50年。教堂装饰庄严典雅，十分讲究。走进这座巨大的教堂内，立即感受到西方天主教的气势宏大和内涵丰富。巨大的壁画，缤纷的雕塑，高大的空间，肃静的氛围，华丽的装饰，虔诚的信徒。所见所闻感受到的是一种宗教信仰的力量和气场。眼前这座气势恢宏内部华丽的教堂很能说明真的是名副其实。',0,6861,54,4,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/St%20Mary\'s%20Church/Thumb%20St%20Mary\'s%20Church.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/St%20Mary\'s%20Church/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/St%20Mary\'s%20Church/St%20Mary\'s%20Church.mp3',99),(2,'Negombo Beach','尼甘布海滩','','update later...','','','','Stunning sunrise','日落和晚霞不可错过','0','0','#ERROR!','',0,7.8,'Even though it could never compete in a beauty contest against many Sri Lankan beaches, Negombo\'s beach, which stretches north from the town right along the hotel strip before fading into a palm tree distance, has been recently tidied up and, in front of the big hotels, is now quite pleasant. Sadly, the water does have a distinct brown colour thanks to estuary run-off and pollution, but it\'s no longer bad enough to stop people swimming.','尼甘布的沙滩从北边的市镇沿着酒店一条街一直延伸，直至淹没进一片棕榈树林，狭窄而又绵长。如今，沙滩也整洁了不少，尤其是大酒店跟前，也是相当迷人的。外国游客即使不入住，也可以从各大酒店的门前进入沙滩。喜欢热闹和体验当地多彩的风情，建议在尼甘布沙滩公园加入本地人的行列中嬉戏玩耍。尼甘布沙滩的日落和晚霞不可错过。',0,6807,109,4,1,'','','','',99),(3,'Dutch Canal','荷兰运河','','Hamilton Canal, Negombo','步行或骑自行车从尼甘布汽车站到Hamilton Canal，出汽车站，往北大约步行200米后沿着Custom House','','','Dutch style','经典荷兰式生活','','','','',0,6.8,'The Dutch showed their love of canals here like nowhere else in Sri Lanka. Canals extend from Negombo all the way south to Colombo and north to Puttalam, a total distance of over 120km. You can hire a bicycle in Negombo from various hotels and ride the canal-side paths for some distance, enjoying the views and small villages along the way.','荷兰运河（Dutch Canal）也被当地人称为“Hamilton Canal”，修建于1646年。它穿城而过，起点在普特拉姆（Puttlam），蜿蜒流向科伦坡港（Colombo Port）。运河是早期荷兰人修筑的一条向科伦坡运输肉桂香料的运河，如今依然发挥着重要作用，是本地渔民重要的出海通道。现在这条不算太宽的河道值得一游，两侧是五颜六色、高低错落的房子，坐着小船悠然划过，有种小威尼斯的感觉。',0,3455,134,4,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/Dutch%20Canal/Thumb%20Dutch%20Canal.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/Dutch%20Canal/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/Dutch%20Canal/Dutch%20Canal.mp3',99),(4,'St Sebastian\'s Church','圣塞巴斯蒂安教堂','','Sea St, Negombo','','','','Most beautiful church at Negombo','尼甘布最漂亮的教堂','','','#ERROR!','',0,7.9,'The church was designed by Father G. Gannon, parish priest of Sea Street. Although the foundation stone was laid by the Archbishop of Colombo, Pierre-Guillaume Marque, on 2 February 1936, construction was not completed until ten years later.','尼甘布最漂亮的教堂，于1936年2月2日由当时的科伦坡大主教彼得马凯进行了奠基仪式，由神父G.甘农设计，最初是完全模仿法国兰斯大教堂的样子来建造的，后来由于资金不足，只得把高度降低。',0,7852,92,4,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/St%20Sebastian\'s%20Church/Thumb%20St%20Sebastian\'s%20Church.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/St%20Sebastian\'s%20Church/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/St%20Sebastian\'s%20Church/St%20Sebastian\'s%20Church.mp3',99),(5,'Lagoon','泻湖','','Negombo Lagoon，Negombo','可选择搭乘突突车前往','','','Birdwatching','观鸟好去处','','','','',0,7.3,'Negombo Lagoon is a large estuarine lagoon in Negombo, south-west Sri Lanka.The lagoon is fed by a number of small rivers and a canal. It is linked to the sea by a narrow channel to the north, near Negombo city. It is surrounded by a densely populated region containing rice paddies, coconut plantations and grassland. The land is used for fishing and agriculture.','尼甘布泻湖（Negombo Lagoon）是斯里兰卡最著名的泻湖之一。它是Muthurawajawela Marsh-Negombo泻湖以及海边湿地的一部分，有水道与外海相通，渔业资源十分丰富，生产鱼虾和螃蟹。湖泊内有大片红树林沼泽地，吸引了鸬鹚、苍鹭、白鹭、燕鸥等岸禽类在此栖息。它们在这里嬉戏玩水，成为湖边一道美丽的风景线。',0,4896,110,4,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/Lagoon/Thumb%20Lagoon.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/Lagoon/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/Lagoon/Lagoon.html','',99),(6,'Nuwaraeliya Post Office','粉红邮局','','Queen Elizabeth Dr，Nuwara Eliya','','','9:00-18:00','Oldest post office','拍一张美美的照片，寄一封明信片','','','#ERROR!','',0,0,'The Nuwara Eliya Post Office is located in the centre of Nuwara Eliya and is one of the oldest post offices in Sri Lanka.The Tudor-style two-storey red-brick building with a clock spire, was constructed in 1894 by the British.','这座英国都铎王朝复兴时期风格的建筑位于努沃勒埃利耶镇中心，由英国人建于1894年，屋顶上有一座钟楼。因建筑外墙由红砖砌成，加上砖块之间的白色泥灰，远看通体成粉红色，故被称为粉红邮局。在斯里兰卡1990年12月26日为了纪念世界邮政日所出版的邮票上，粉红邮局被印在了10卢比面值的邮票上。如今除了邮局本身的功能外，还成了一处观光点。',0,4925,124,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Nuwaraeliya%20Post%20Office/Thumb%20Nuwaraeliya%20Post%20Office.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Nuwaraeliya%20Post%20Office/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Nuwaraeliya%20Post%20Office/Nuwaraeliya%20Post%20Office.mp3',99),(7,'Lake Gregory','格雷戈里湖','','Gregory Lake, Nuwara Eliya','可乘坐突突车前往','','','','','200LKR','200卢比','','',0,0,'Lake Gregory is a reservoir in heart of the tea country hill city, Nuwara Eliya. Lake Gregory was constructed during the period of British Governor Sir William Gregory in 1873.','格雷戈里湖（Gregory Lake）位于努沃勒埃利耶东南市郊，1874年由当时的锡兰总督格雷戈里主持修建，占地约91公顷。曾经这个景色优美的人工湖几乎荒废，直到近些年才重新开放，修建了环湖路，从而成为当地人周末野餐、散步，享受湖光山色的地方。',0,6933,144,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Lake%20Gregory/Thumb%20Lake%20Gregory.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Lake%20Gregory/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Lake%20Gregory/Lake%20Gregory.mp3',99),(8,'Devon Falls','德文瀑布','','Avissawella-Hatton-Nuwara Eliya Highway, Talawakele, Nuwara Eliya','可选择从努瓦勒埃利耶汽车站搭乘前往塔勒沃凯莱（Talawakele）或哈顿（Hatton）的公共汽车','','','','','','','','',0,0,'Devon Falls is a waterfall in Sri Lanka, situated 6 km west of Talawakele, Nuwara Eliya District on A7 highway. The falls is named after a pioneer English coffee planter called Devon, whose plantation is situated nearby the falls. The Waterfall is 97 metres high and ranked 19th highest in the Island. The Falls formed by Kothmale Oya, a tributary of Mahaweli River. Altitude of Devon falls is 1,140m above sea level.','德文瀑布（Devon Falls）位于努瓦勒埃利耶以西17公里处，努瓦勒埃利耶到哈顿A7公路旁，因英国的咖啡种植者德文而得名。瀑布高97米，在周围茶园的衬托下非常有斯里兰卡韵味。',0,9895,89,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Devon%20Falls/Thumb%20Devon%20Falls.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Devon%20Falls/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Devon%20Falls/Devon%20Falls.mp3',99),(9,'Hakgala Botanical Garden','哈克加拉皇家植物园','','Peradeniya-Badulla-Chenkaladi Highway, Nuwara Eliya','可选择搭乘从努瓦勒埃利耶汽车站前往Hakgala的公共汽车，在Hakgala Botanical Garden下车后步行','','7:30-17:00','The second largest garden in Sri Lanka','斯里兰卡第二大植物园','1100LKR','1100卢比','','',0,0,'Hakgala Botanical Garden is situated on the Nuwara Eliya-Badulla main road, 16 km from Nuwara Eliya. The garden has a cool temperate climate because of altitude is 5,400 feet above the sea level. The mean annual temperature ranges between 16 °C to 30 °C during course of a year. From December to February it has a cold climate, while the warm climate persists from April to August.','哈克高拉皇家拉植物园（Hakgala Botanical Garden）位于努瓦勒埃利耶东南16公里处，在努瓦勒埃利耶到巴杜勒A5公路旁，临近哈克高拉自然保护区，海拔一千七百多米，是斯里兰卡三大植物园之一。',0,4677,67,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Hakgala%20Botanical%20Garden/Thumb%20Hakgala%20Botanical%20Garden.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Hakgala%20Botanical%20Garden/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Hakgala%20Botanical%20Garden/Hakgala%20Botanical%20Garden.mp3',99),(10,'Victoria Park of Nuwara Eliya','维多利亚公园','','Badulla Road，Nuwara Eliya','维多利亚花园位于努瓦勒埃利耶汽车站旁，步行即可到达','','6:30-18:30','One of the nicest, and best maintained, town parks in South Asia','','60LKR','60卢比','','',0,0,'The lovely Victoria Park at the centre of town is one of the nicest, and best maintained, town parks in South Asia, and a stroll around its manicured lawns is a pleasure indeed. The park comes alive with flowers around March to May, and August and September. It’s also home to quite a number of hill-country bird species, including the Kashmir flycatcher, Indian pitta and grey tit.','维多利亚公园（Victoria Park）是努瓦勒埃利耶中心的一个公园，公园原来是哈克高拉植物园（Hakgala）的科研区，后来因德国王子访问而成立公园。1897年后，为了纪念维多利亚女王登基60周年而更名为维多利亚公园。公园非常安静，在这里可以看到很多小动物，尤其是鸟类，例如印度知更鸟、斑鸠、印巴姬鹟等，因此维多利亚花园是当地非常著名的一个观鸟地区。',0,4701,118,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Victoria%20Park%20of%20Nuwara%20Eliya/Thumb%20Victoria%20Park%20of%20Nuwara%20Eliya.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Victoria%20Park%20of%20Nuwara%20Eliya/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Victoria%20Park%20of%20Nuwara%20Eliya/Victoria%20Park%20of%20Nuwara%20Eliya.mp3',99),(11,'Seetha Amman','sita神庙','','Seetha Eliya, Nuwara Eliya','','','','','印度教史诗《罗摩衍那》故事发生地之一','0','0','','',0,0,'The colourful Hindu Seetha Amman Temple at Sita Eliya. It’s said to mark the spot where Sita was held captive by the demon king Rawana, and where she prayed daily for Rama to come and rescue her. On the rock face across the stream are circular depressions said to be the footprints of Rawana’s elephant.','这个神庙就是根据印度两大史诗之一《罗摩衍那》的描述，十首魔王罗波那绑架阿逾陀国王罗摩之妻悉多，囚禁于此，结果引来猴王哈努曼搭救，这个寺庙就是特别为供奉悉多而建，并有供奉神猴哈努曼的神殿。寺庙外就可以观赏到色彩鲜艳的印度教众神。',0,6472,141,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Seetha%20Amman/Thumb%20Seetha%20Amman.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Seetha%20Amman/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Seetha%20Amman/Seetha%20Amman.mp3',99),(12,'Horton Plains National Park','霍顿国家公园','','Horton Plains National Park, Ohiya, Nuwara Eliya','可选择搭乘坐火车或者汽车到达Ambewela、Pattipola或Ohiya，在这些地方转乘突突车前往','','6:00-18:00','World’s End- a stunning escarpment that plunges 880m','世界尽头悬崖','2200LKR','2200卢比','','',0,0,'Horton Plains is a beautiful, silent, strange world with some excellent hikes in the shadows of Sri Lanka’s second- and third-highest mountains, Kirigalpotta (2395m) and Totapola (2357m). The ‘plains’ form an undulating plateau over 2000m high, covered by wild grasslands and interspersed with patches of thick forest, rocky outcrops, filigree waterfalls and misty lakes. The surprising diversity of the landscape is matched by the wide variety of wildlife (although many of the larger animals are very elusive).','霍顿平原国家公园（Horton Plains National Park）是斯里兰卡的重要生态旅游区，海拔在2100到2300米之间，由山地草原和云雾林覆盖，是生物多样性极其丰富的地区。霍尔顿平原是斯里兰卡三大河流的源头，平原上是草原与山地森林相间的植被，包括许多特有木本植物。2010年7月，斯里兰卡中部高原，其中包括霍顿平原国家公园、亚当峰所在的山ࣿ荒野保护区和Knuckles山脉列入“世界遗产名录”。',0,8259,97,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Horton%20Plains%20National%20Park/Thumb%20Horton%20Plains%20National%20Park.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Horton%20Plains%20National%20Park/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Horton%20Plains%20National%20Park/Horton%20Plains%20National%20Park.html','',99),(13,'Ambewela Farm','Ambewela农场','','update later...','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'','',0,4873,111,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Ambewela%20Farm/Thumb%20Ambewela%20Farm.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Ambewela%20Farm/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Ambewela%20Farm/Ambewela%20Farm.mp3',99),(14,'Nanu Oya','火车站','','Nanu Oya, Sri Lanka','Nanu Oya有公交车和突突车前往努瓦勒埃利耶。','','','','','','','','',0,0,'','',0,3595,117,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Nanu%20Oya/Thumb%20Nanu%20Oya.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Nanu%20Oya/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Nanu%20Oya/Nanu%20Oya.mp3',99),(15,'Sigiriya Rock Fortress','狮子岩','','Lion\'s Rock, Entrance Walkway, Sigiriya','从丹布勒公交站乘坐前往狮子岩的公交车至Sigiriya站','','7:00-17:00','The \"Eighth Wonder of the World\"','斯里兰卡的名片，世界第八大奇迹','30USD','30美元','#ERROR!','',0,0,'Sigiriya rock foretress, According to the ancient Sri Lankan chronicle the Culavamsa, this site was selected by King Kasyapa (477 – 495 CE) for his new capital. He built his palace on the top of this rock and decorated its sides with colourful frescoes. On a small plateau about halfway up the side of this rock he built a gateway in the form of an enormous lion. The name of this place is derived from this structure —Sīhāgiri, the Lion Rock. The capital and the royal palace was abandoned after the king\'s death. It was used as a Buddhist monastery until the 14th century.Sigiriya today is a UNESCO listed World Heritage Site. It is one of the best preserved examples of ancient urban planning.','在5世纪后半叶，来自阿努拉德普勒弑父篡位的王子，为了防止流亡印度、同父异母的弟弟的复仇，在锡吉里耶陡峭的岩石上修建易守难攻、动人心魄的宫殿，但仅仅在这里统治11年后，便被弟弟打败而自杀。之后，新的国王把锡吉里耶捐献给僧侣，将首都再次迁回阿努拉德普勒。14世纪之后，锡吉里耶被逐渐荒废，直至19世纪末淹没在丛林中的伟大宫殿才被英国考古学家重新发现。1982年，联合国教科文组织宣布锡吉里耶成为世界文化遗产。',0,7358,111,7,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Sigiriya%20Rock%20Fortress/Thumb%20Sigiriya%20Rock%20Fortress.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Sigiriya%20Rock%20Fortress/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Sigiriya%20Rock%20Fortress/Sigiriya%20Rock%20Fortress.mp3',99),(16,'Polonnaruwa Ancient City','波隆纳鲁沃古城','','Polonnaruwa','骑自行车或者乘坐突突车','','8:00-17:00','Polonnaruwa is ancient bricks and Buddhas','丛林中的伟大王朝遗迹','3250LKR','3250卢比','','',0,0,'Po?onnaruwa is the second most ancient of Sri Lanka\'s kingdoms, Polonnaruwa was first declared the capital city by King Vijayabahu I, who defeated Chola invaders in 1070 to reunite the country once more under a local leader.\nKings ruled the central plains of Sri Lanka from Polonnaruwa 800 years ago, when it was a thriving commercial and religious centre. The glories of that age can be found in the archaeological treasures that still give a pretty good idea of how the city looked in its heyday. You\'ll find the archaeological park a delight to explore, with hundreds of ancient structures – tombs and temples, statues and stupas','波隆纳鲁沃的历史可以追溯到公元前2世纪，由于马哈维利河天然的保护屏障，并且远离南印度侵略者的登陆地带，波隆纳鲁沃一直是保护阿努拉德普勒的前哨和军事基地，也是阿努拉德普勒后期君王们的避难所。在定都波隆纳鲁沃之后，僧伽罗王朝的君王们继续大力发展水利灌溉和修造寺庙。在全盛时期，这里王城的建筑规模宏大，不仅建立了许多佛像和寺庙，吸引泰国和缅甸的僧侣来此求学，同时水利的高度发达使得古斯里兰卡的农业达到顶峰，在短短的200年内，波隆纳鲁沃取得了异常辉煌的成就，在某些方面甚至超越了阿努拉德普勒。不过，波隆纳鲁沃也和阿努拉德普拉的命运一样，受到印度朱罗王朝的侵略，在13世纪后半期，僧伽罗王朝逐步退居到岛屿的中部，波隆纳鲁沃也逐渐荒废，逐渐埋没在丛林之中。',0,8989,118,7,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Polonnaruwa%20Ancient%20City/Thumb%20Polonnaruwa%20Ancient%20City.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Polonnaruwa%20Ancient%20City/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Polonnaruwa%20Ancient%20City/Polonnaruwa%20Ancient%20City.mp3',99),(17,'Dambulla Cave Temple','丹布拉石窟寺','','Dambulla Cave Temple, Dambulla','从丹布勒客运总站往康堤方向步行即可到达','','7:00-18:00','The largest, best-preserved cave-temple complex in Sri Lanka','斯里兰卡著名的佛教朝圣中心','0','0','#ERROR!','http://www.goldentemple.lk/',0,0,'Dambulla is the largest and best-preserved cave temple complex in Sri Lanka. The rock towers 160 m over the surrounding plains.There are more than 80 documented caves in the surrounding area. Major attractions are spread over five caves, which contain statues and paintings. These paintings and statues are related to Gautama Buddha and his life. There are a total of 153 Buddha statues, three statues of Sri Lankan kings and four statues of gods and goddesses. The latter include Vishnu and the Ganesha. The murals cover an area of 2,100 square metres (23,000 sq ft). Depictions on the walls of the caves include the temptation by the demon Mara, and Buddha\'s first sermon.','传说在公元前1世纪，这里是伐多伽摩尼阿巴耶国王的避难所，当他赶走泰米尔人重夺王位后，为了感谢上苍神灵，在这座酷似鲸鱼脊背的岩石上建造寺庙，开凿出拥有5个巨大石窟的建筑群，打造了这个壮观岩石寺院。后来的国王又不断加以修缮，现在寺中有5个独立的石窟，内藏157尊石刻佛像和其他雕像以及2100平方米的壁画，极具宗教艺术价值，是斯里兰卡最大、保存最完整的洞穴石窟庙宇，也是斯里兰卡著名的佛教朝圣中心。',0,5871,102,7,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Dambulla%20Cave%20Temple/Thumb%20Dambulla%20Cave%20Temple.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Dambulla%20Cave%20Temple/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Dambulla%20Cave%20Temple/Dambulla%20Cave%20Temple.mp3',99),(18,'Minneriya National Park','米内瑞亚国家公园','','Habarana-Polonnaruwa Road, Habarana','','','6:00 - 18:00','Mixed evergreen forest and scrub areas and is home to Sri Lanka \'s favourites such as sambar deer, leopards and elephants.','斯里兰卡最重要的大象栖息地','','','#ERROR!','',0,0,'Minneriya National Park is a national park in North Central Province of Sri Lanka. The area was designated as a national park on 12 August 1997. The tank is of historical importance, having been built by King Mahasen in third century AD. The park is a dry season feeding ground for the elephant population dwelling in forests of Matale, Polonnaruwa, and Trincomalee districts.','斯里兰卡全国拥有多达九个国家公园，其中米内日亚国家公园虽属面积较细小的一个，但占地也有九十平方公里，而园内那个玛哈辛国王在三世纪修建的巨大蓄水湖，面积更是该国数一数二的。蓄水湖区在旱季时露出青草，吸引附近生物到来栖息，包括来自马塔拉、波隆纳鲁瓦和亭可马里等地区的象群，也会在这时来到绿草茵茵的湖畔寻找水源和嫩草，有时会多达2-300头。所以米内日亚国家公园是该国其中一个最重要的大象栖息地。',0,6396,123,7,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Minneriya%20National%20Park/Thumb%20Minneriya%20National%20Park.jpg','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Sigiriya%20&%20Dambulla/Sights/Minneriya%20National%20Park/Minneriya%20National%20Park.html','',99),(19,'Malwatu Oya Stone Bridge','Malwatu Oya Stone Bridge','','Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka','','','0:00-24:00','','精美绝伦的古代石桥','','','','',0,0,'The best preserved ancient stone bridge is the Mahakanadarawa stone bridge, built over the Kanadarawa River in the ancient road between Anuradhapura and Gokanna (Trincomalee). The present road connecting the two cities roughly coincides with the ancient road, which is a clear indication of the technological skills of the ancient Sri Lankans.','斯里兰卡保存最完好的古代石桥。横跨在孕育了璀璨文明的kanadarawa河上。它绝妙的建筑结构和精湛了建造技术无不体现了古代斯里兰卡人民的智慧和聪颖。',0,4368,56,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Malwatu%20Oya%20Stone%20Bridge/Thumb%20Malwatu%20Oya%20Stone%20Bridge.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Malwatu%20Oya%20Stone%20Bridge/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Malwatu%20Oya%20Stone%20Bridge/Malwatu%20Oya%20Stone%20Bridge.mp3',99),(20,'Mihintale','米欣特莱','','Mihintale, Sri Lanka','','','8:00-17:00','','','500LKR','500卢比','','',0,0,'','米欣特莱（Mihintale）是阿努拉德普勒东部一个宁静的小村庄，自从1934年在丛林之中发现了大规模的遗迹群，这里便成为斯里兰卡最重要的圣地，吸引无数朝圣者来此膜拜。公元前247年，印度阿育王之子摩哂陀来到斯里兰卡传播佛教，在米欣特莱遇到天爱帝沙国王。国王与摩哂陀交流后，率领臣民皈依佛教。从此佛教才开始在斯里兰卡盛行。米欣特莱是兰卡佛教的发源地，是佛教最初传入斯里兰卡时的地方。现在，米欣特莱的山ࣿ建有寺庙和佛塔。站在山ࣿ极目远眺，一马平川，让人心旷神怡。',0,6654,66,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Mihintale/Thumb%20Mihintale.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Mihintale/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Mihintale/Mihintale.mp3',99),(21,'The Elephant Pond','大象池塘','','Thuparamaya, Watawandana Rd, Anuradhapura','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'Surrounded by forest, this huge body of water is thought to have acted as an ancient water storage tank for the Abhayagiri monastery rather than as a pool for pachyderms. Such is the scale of the tank– 159m long, 53m wide and 10m deep – that six Olympic-sized swimming pools could comfortably fit inside it.','隐藏在森林中的巨型水池，是阿努拉德普勒遗迹的一部分。水池长159米，宽53米，深9米。相传是给大象洗澡冲凉的地方，但是古人为何修了一座相当于6个奥利匹克游泳馆面积的水池，他们是如何修建的，至今都是一个又一个的谜团。',0,3167,111,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/The%20Elephant%20Pond/Thumb%20The%20Elephant%20Pond.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/The%20Elephant%20Pond/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/The%20Elephant%20Pond/The%20Elephant%20Pond.mp3',99),(22,'Twin Pond','双池塘','','Kuttam Pokuna, Watawandana Road, Anuradhapura','从坐佛沿着Watawandana Rd往东300米','','8:30-17:30','','','','','','',0,0,'One of the best specimen of bathing tanks or pools in ancient Sri Lanka is the pair of pools known as Kuttam Pokuna (Twin Ponds/Pools). The said pair of pools were built by the Sinhalese in the ancient kingdom of Anuradhapura. These are considered one of the significant achievements in the field of hydrological engineering and outstanding architectural and artistic creations of the ancient Sinhalese.','在萨玛狄坐佛东北方向，有一大一小两个水池，库坦博库纳（Kuttam Pokuna）是无畏山寺的僧侣洗澡沐浴的地方。据说这两个水池设计精巧，水从稍大池塘的野兽雕像嘴中流入，然后从池塘地下的管道流向小池塘，然后再通过排水系统引到周围水田中用于灌溉。现在这个水利系统不知是否依然可用，池塘中只剩下墨绿色的污水。',0,6859,110,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Twin%20Pond/Thumb%20Twin%20Pond.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Twin%20Pond/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Twin%20Pond/Twin%20Pond.mp3',99),(23,'Isurumuniya Temple','伊苏鲁姆尼亚寺','','Isurumuniya Vihara, Anuradhapura','','','8:30-17:30','','伊苏如摩尼亚寺以摩崖石刻闻名，其中最 著名的是一块公元5世纪的情侣雕像，记录了一位王子和贫民女子之 间的爱恋故事，生动优美，非常浪漫。','200LKR','200卢比','','',0,0,'The temple was built by King Devanampiya Tissa (307 BC to 267 BC) who ruled in the ancient Sri Lankan capital of Anuradhapura. After 500 children of high-caste were ordained, Isurumuniya was built for them to reside. King Kasyapa I (473-491 AD) renovated this viharaya and named it as \"Boupulvan, Kasubgiri Radmaha Vehera\". This name is derived from names of his 2 daughters and his name. Best known of the sculptures is the \"lovers\", Which dates from around the 5th centry AD and is built in the artistic style of the Indian Gupta dynasty of the 4th and 5th centries.','位于帝沙水库边（Tissa Wewa），由天爱帝沙国王建造，俗称“石头寺庙”，犹如在岩石表面雕刻出来的寺庙和建造在岩石上的佛塔，安置有色彩绚烂佛像的正殿和收藏着宝贵出土文物的藏宝馆，这是一个与阿努拉德普勒其他遗迹迥然不同的寺庙，除了公元前3世纪建造的僧院一部分保留下来以外，寺院本身都经过重修。正殿旁边的宝藏殿（博物馆）内收藏的从寺院北侧王宫花园里发现的“恋人像（Isurumu Lover）”和“国王的一家（King’s Family）”石刻，为镇馆之宝。王子与玛拉的恋情因两人身份差距悬殊而不为世俗所容，但是王子没有放弃，甚至不惜抛弃王位也要与拉玛结合。',0,7805,65,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Isurumuniya%20Temple/Thumb%20Isurumuniya%20Temple.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Isurumuniya%20Temple/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Isurumuniya%20Temple/Isurumuniya%20Temple.mp3',99),(24,'Jethawanaramaya Dagoba','杰塔瓦纳拉玛（祗园寺塔）','','Jethawanaramaya Dagoba, B341 Watawandana Rd, Anuradhapura','沿着Watawandana Rd往南前行即可到达','','8:30-17:30','','','','','','',0,0,'The Jethawanaramaya Dagoba\'s massive dome rises from a clearing back towards the Sti Maha Bodhi. Built in the 3rd century by Mahasena, it may have originally stood over 100m high, but today is about 70m, a similar hight to the Abhayagiri, with which it is sometimes confused. At the time it was built it was the third-tallest monument in the world, the first two being Egyptian pyramids. An early British guidebook calculated taht there were engough bricks in the dagoba\'s brick core to make a 3m-high wall stretching from London to Edinburgh.','杰塔瓦纳拉玛舍利塔巨大的圆形屋顶在圣菩提树后方空明的背景中拔地而起。这座寺庙是3世纪由Mahasenna建造的，起初这里有一百米高，然而今天却只有70米——与安博哈亚奇瑞高度相同。在它建造完成的时代，这是世界第三高的纪念碑，而前两名是埃及的金字塔。20世纪初一本英国旅游指南曾计算说，这座舍利塔中心的砖头数量，足够建一堵从伦敦延伸到爱丁堡的三米高墙。',0,8452,150,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Jethawanaramaya%20Dagoba/Thumb%20Jethawanaramaya%20Dagoba.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Jethawanaramaya%20Dagoba/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Jethawanaramaya%20Dagoba/Jethawanaramaya%20Dagoba.mp3',99),(25,'Mirisawetiya Stupa','米瑞萨瓦提亚舍利塔','','Thuparamaya, Old Puttalam Rd, Anuradhapura','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'The Mirisaveti Stupa is situated in the ancient city of Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka.[1] King Dutugamunu (161 BC to 137 BC) built the Mirisaveti Stupa after defeating King Elara. After placing the Buddha relics in the sceptre, he had gone to Tissa Wewa for a bath leaving the sceptre. After the bath he returned to the place where the sceptre was placed, and it is said that it could not be moved. The stupa was built in the place where the sceptre stood. It is also said that he remembered that he partook a chilly curry without offering it to the sangha. In order to punish himself he built the Mirisavetiya Dagaba.','米瑞萨瓦提亚舍利塔是杜图珈摩奴在公元前2世纪占领这座城市之后首先建立的舍利塔。相传杜图珈摩奴到池塘里去洗澡，把他装饰精美的权杖插在岸边。然而当他想要拿回权杖的时候，却发现这个有着佛祖印记的东西却如何也拔不出来了。于是他把这当成了祥瑞，下令建造了这座舍利塔。',0,8821,88,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Mirisawetiya%20Stupa/Thumb%20Mirisawetiya%20Stupa.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Mirisawetiya%20Stupa/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Mirisawetiya%20Stupa/Mirisawetiya%20Stupa.mp3',99),(26,'Fort Frederick','弗雷德里克要塞','','Fort Frederick, Trincomalee','','','0:00-24:00','','','0','0','','',0,0,'The Fort Fredrick was build by Portuguese in 1623. This is located by the Trincomalee town. The famous Koneswaram temple is located inside this fort. This Hindu temple earlier know as temple of thousand Pillars. This fort was captured by Dutch in 1639. Later this was captured by British in 1795.','弗雷德里克要塞（Fort Frederick）是亭可马里城内的标志性建筑，位于亭可马里东部的海岬上，又被称作亭可马里要塞。1622年葡萄牙人占领亭可马里，拆除了原先坐落在海边的科内斯瓦勒姆神庙，并用神庙的石材修建了要塞。1639年，荷兰人赶走葡萄牙人，重新修建城堡，并命名“弗雷德里克要塞”。从1795年开始，这里就成为英国的海军基地，并在第二次世界大战中成为蒙巴顿勋爵的总部。',0,8766,55,11,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/Fort%20Frederick/Thumb%20Fort%20Frederick.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/Fort%20Frederick/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/Fort%20Frederick/Fort%20Frederick.mp3',99),(27,'Swami Rock','斯瓦米岩','','Swami Rock, Trincomalee','','','0:00-24:00','Cityview of Trincomalee, good for diving','俯瞰亭可马里城区','0','0','','',0,0,'Lover\'s Leap is located in close proximity to Koneswaram Temple and gives the viewers a breathtaking and thrilling scenic view. A rock of around 350 feet sheer drop! The Hindus believe this as “Ravana’s Cleft”.','斯瓦米岩（Swami Rock）又名情人崖（Lovers\' Leap），据说因为荷兰军官的女儿在此跳崖殉情而得名。位于要塞的最高处，崖高130米，峭壁下面就是大海，惊涛骇浪拍打着岩石。这里不仅可以看到美丽的海景，还可以俯瞰亭可马里城。',0,7369,141,11,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/Swami%20Rock/Thumb%20Swami%20Rock.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/Swami%20Rock/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/Swami%20Rock/Swami%20Rock.mp3',99),(28,'Bopath Ella Falls','博道瀑布','','Agalawatta, Kuruwita, HiggasHena - Devipahala Road, Kuruwita','','','0:00-24:00','Well known by treasure trove','传说中巨大宝藏的所在地','0','0','','',0,0,'is a waterfall situated in the Ratnapura District of Sri Lanka. It has a shape very similar to the leaf of the Sacred fig or \"Bo\" tree, which has earned it this name. The waterfall is a major tourist attraction in the country. Local myths say that it is haunted and that it hides a treasure trove.','',0,7533,99,5,1,'','','','',99),(29,'Yala National Park','雅拉国家公园','','Yala National Park','乘坐吉普车前往','','6:00-18:00','The world’s biggest concentration of leopards','世界上能观察和拍摄金钱豹的极少数国家公园之一','3000LKR','3000卢比','#ERROR!','http://yalasrilanka.lk/',0,0,'Situated in Sri Lanka’s south-east hugging the panoramic Indian Ocean, Yala was designated a wildlife sanctuary in 1900 and was designated a national park in 1938. Ironically, the park was initially used as a hunting ground for the elite under British rule. Yala is home to 44 varieties of mammal and 215 bird species. Among its more famous residents are the world’s biggest concentration of leopards, majestic elephants, sloth bears, sambars, jackals, spotted dear, peacocks, and crocodiles. The best time to visit Yala is between February and July when the water levels of the park are quite low, bringing animals into the open.','雅拉国家公园（Yala National Park）1900年被认定为自然保护区，1938年与维拉帕图国家公园一起被认定为国家公园。现在国家公园由五片区域组成，但只有1区和2区对公众开放，我们常说的雅拉国家公园又被称为西雅拉，也称卢胡纳国家公园。雅拉国家公园以野生动物多而闻名，它是世界上能观察和拍摄金钱豹的极少数国家公园之一。这里还有大量哺乳动物，如大象、长毛熊、梅花鹿、猫鼬、猴子、野猪、野牛、狐狸、狼、豪猪等，除此之外还有许多的爬行动物和水生动物，如沼泽鳄、河口鳄、蜥蜴、龟、眼镜蛇、青蛇、石蟒等，在雅拉可以近距离观看动物。',0,5569,125,6,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Sights/Yala%20National%20Park/Thumb%20Yala%20National%20Park.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Sights/Yala%20National%20Park/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Sights/Yala%20National%20Park/Yala%20National%20Park.mp3',99),(30,'Tissa wewa - Tissamaharama','蒂瑟默哈拉默湖','','Weerawila-Tissa-Kataragama Rd (Tissa Rd)','步行即可到达','','0:00-24:00','','','0','0','','',0,0,'The centrepiece of the town and its surrounds is the lovely Tissa Wewa (Tissa Tank), a huge man-made lake about 1.5km from the town centre. In the evening, check out the huge flocks of egrets that descend onto the trees around the lake to roost. The road along the southern edge has a wide new Lakeside Walkway for strolling.','蒂瑟默哈拉默镇外有一个巨大的人造湖，蒂瑟默哈拉默湖（TissaWewa）距镇中心1.5公里（步行15分钟左右），建于公元前3世纪，现在依然发挥着重要作用。傍晚在湖周边树木上会有大量的白鹭栖息。',0,9246,79,6,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Sights/Tissa%20wewa%20-%20Tissamaharama/Thumb%20Tissa%20wewa%20-%20Tissamaharama.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Sights/Tissa%20wewa%20-%20Tissamaharama/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Tissamaharama%20&%20Yala/Sights/Tissa%20wewa%20-%20Tissamaharama/Tissa%20wewa%20-%20Tissamaharama.mp3',99),(31,'Ravana Ella Falls','拉瓦纳埃勒瀑布','','Wellawaya-Ella-Kumbalwela Highway','可乘坐公交车或突突车前往，突突车往返大约700卢比，公交车约需花费15卢比','','0:00-24:00','One of the widest falls of the country','斯里兰卡全国最宽的瀑布之一','0','0','','',0,0,'The Ravana Falls (popularly known as Ravana Ella in Sinhala) is a popular sightseeing attraction in Sri Lanka. It currently ranks as one of the widest falls in the country.','拉瓦纳埃勒瀑布（Ravana Ella Falls）是埃勒非常有名的一个小景点，距离埃勒6公里。瀑布从山ࣿ一个椭圆型凹岩中流出，高25米，是斯里兰卡全国最宽的瀑布之一。埃勒瀑布是埃勒野生动物保护区的一部分，周围植被茂盛，十分秀美。',0,5522,71,9,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Ravana%20Ella%20Falls/Thumb%20Ravana%20Ella%20Falls.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Ravana%20Ella%20Falls/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Ravana%20Ella%20Falls/Ravana%20Ella%20Falls.html','',99),(32,'Ella Rock','埃拉岩石','','Wellawaya-Ella-Kumbalwela Highway, Ella','从埃勒步行即可到达，往返大概需要4-5小时','','0:00-24:00','Best place for hiking, stunning view','绝佳登山地和不枉此行的风景','0','0','#ERROR!','',0,0,'Ella Rock is one of the must-sees in Ella, a place which is becoming increasingly touristy and even brands itself as a \'tourist town\' (check out the signboards at the junction!). Offering panoramic views of the Ella Gap and Little Adam\'s Peak, the hike is an arduous upward climb and you\'re guaranteed to lose yourselves among tea estates, hills, and tall shrubs if you\'re without a guide.','埃拉岩石（Ella Rock）位于埃勒南边巨大的岩石峭壁，是埃勒的标志性景观，因为地势高、视野开阔，是徒步爱好者热衷的登山地。其难度比小亚当峰要大，全程需要3-4个小时，最好有向导带领。',0,3871,69,9,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Ella%20Rock/Thumb%20Ella%20Rock.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Ella%20Rock/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Ella%20Rock/Ella%20Rock.mp3',99),(33,'Demodara Nine Arch Bridge','德摩达拉九孔桥','','Demodera - Spring Valley - Badulla Road\nDemodara','','','0:00-24:00','Amazing views of bridge, mountain and trains','高山小火车最佳拍摄地','0','0','','',0,0,'The Demodara nine arch railway bridge is located between Demodara and Ella railway stations. Specialty of this bridge is that, it’s constructed with stones, bricks and cement, but without any steel.','Demodara九孔桥是Ella到Badulla的铁道上一座著名的桥梁，由石块砌成的九座桥拱正好位于一个150度的大弯上，是拍摄斯里兰卡山地火车的有名场所。',0,6792,82,9,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Demodara%20Nine%20Arch%20Bridge/Thumb%20Demodara%20Nine%20Arch%20Bridge.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Demodara%20Nine%20Arch%20Bridge/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Demodara%20Nine%20Arch%20Bridge/Demodara%20Nine%20Arch%20Bridge.mp3',99),(34,'Galle Face Green','加勒菲斯绿地广场','','Galle Face Centre Road, Colombo, Sri lanka','公交车Galle Face站下车','','0:00-24:00','The Galle Face is a 5 ha (12 acres) ocean-side urban park','一条风景宜人的海滨大道，科伦坡来往的必经之地','0','0','','',0,0,'The Galle Face is a 5 ha (12 acres) ocean-side urban park, which stretches for 500 m (1,600 ft) along the coast, in the heart of the financial and business capital of Sri Lanka, Colombo. The promenade was initially laid out in 1859 by Governor Sir Henry George Ward, although the original Galle Face Green extended over a much larger area than is seen today. The Galle Face Green was initially used for horse racing and as a golf course, but was also used for cricket, polo, football, tennis and rugby.','加勒菲斯绿地广场（Galle Face Green）地处科伦坡要塞区黄金地带，濒临大海、景色宜人。荷兰人统治时期，这里被当作防波堤和堡垒，后来于1859年由当时英国驻斯里兰卡总督主持开辟这片绿地，被用作板球场、赛马场和高尔夫球场。现今，这个绵延半公里的带状广场已经成为当地人休闲娱乐的场所，人们在这里慢跑、散步、放风筝，年轻情侣们谈情说爱。由于距离总统府很近，近年来独立纪念日阅兵仪式也在这里举行。',0,5348,57,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Galle%20Face%20Green/Thumb%20Galle%20Face%20Green.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Galle%20Face%20Green/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Galle%20Face%20Green/Galle%20Face%20Green.mp3',99),(35,'Gangaramaya Temple','冈嘎拉马寺','','Sri Jinaratana Rd Slave Island，Colombo 02','从维哈马哈德维公园步行即可到达','','5:30-22:00','Gangaramaya Temple is one of the most important temples in Colombo, Sri Lanka, being a mix of modern architecture and cultural essence.','拥有图书馆、博物馆、宿舍和一座三层的佛学院','400LKR','400卢比','-3187','www.gangaramaya.com',0,0,'The temple\'s architecture demonstrates an eclectic mix of Sri Lankan, Thai, Indian, and Chinese architecture.[1]\n\nThis Buddhist temple includes several imposing buildings and is situated not far from the placid waters of Beira Lake on a plot of land that was originally a small hermitage on a piece of marshy land. It has the main features of a Vihara (temple), the Cetiya (Pagada) the Bodhitree, the Vihara Mandiraya, the Seema malaka (assembly hall for monks) and the Relic Chamber. In addition, a museum, a library, a residential hall, a three storeyed Pirivena, educational halls and an alms hall are also on the premises.\n\nMost notable for tourists is the architecture of the Simamalaka Shrine, which was built with donations from a Muslim sponsor to the design of Geoffrey Bawa.','科伦坡市政厅（Colombo Muncipal Council）位于维哈马哈德维公园东北部，本地人一般直接称之为“Town Hall”，这是一座圆白墙的新古典主义建筑。由于其纯白色外观与美国白宫颇为相似，这里经常被当地人亲切的称作“小白宫”。该建筑建于1927年，现在是科伦地方议会的总部，市长办公室所在地，很多市政部门和城市服务部门也在此办公。',0,3359,77,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Gangaramaya%20Temple/Thumb%20Gangaramaya%20Temple.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Gangaramaya%20Temple/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Gangaramaya%20Temple/Gangaramaya%20Temple.mp3',99),(36,'Independence Square','独立广场（独立纪念厅）','','Independence Ave Cinnamon Gardens，Colombo 07','从维哈马哈德维公园步行即可到达','','0:00-24:00','','纪念斯里兰卡脱离英国殖民统治的纪念厅','0','0','','',0,0,'Independence Memorial Hall (also Independence Commemoration Hall) is a national monument in Sri Lanka built for commemoration of the independence of Sri Lanka from the British rule with the restoration of full governing responsibility[2] to a Ceylonese-elected legislature on February 4, 1948. It is located at the Independence Square (formerly Torrington Square) in the Cinnamon Gardens, Colombo. It also houses the Independence Memorial Museum.','1948年2月4日为纪念斯里兰卡脱离英国殖民统治，斯里兰卡政府在肉桂花园建造了这座独立纪念厅（Independence Hall）。这栋庞大的石头建筑沿袭了斯里兰卡传统的建筑风格，仿照康堤议会大厅（Kandy\'s Audience Hall）而建。纪念厅的正前方矗立着一尊斯里兰卡国父唐·斯蒂芬·森纳那亚克（Don Stephen Senanayake）的雕像，周围有60尊象征僧伽罗人的狮子雕像，厅内的石柱上刻有复杂的佛教图案。在独立纪念厅的地下室设有一座小博物馆，馆内里面陈列着为斯里兰卡摆脱殖民统治、争取独立做出贡献的英雄雕像。',0,4733,63,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Independence%20Square/Thumb%20Independence%20Square.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Independence%20Square/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Independence%20Square/Independence%20Square.mp3',99),(37,'Mount Lavinia Beach','芒特拉维尼亚','','Dehiwala, Mt Lavinia','可选择从要塞区(Fort)搭乘10路、11路汽车(南下的长途汽车)或者火车，在Mt Lavinia站下车。','','','','如果你喜欢海滩，干净的海滩，必须来','0','0','#ERROR!','',0,0,'Mount Lavinia Beach is located just out of the Colombo city. This beach strip has a lot to offer for the locals as well as the tourists visiting Colombo. Along the beach there are many nice restaurants pubs as well as relaxing areas. As a tourist who is visiting Colombo, Mount Lavinia Beach is a must visit. The weekends could be crowded with locals though, during the week it is relaxing and peaceful. If you would relax at a pool overlooking the ocean or the sunset, The Mount Lavinia Hotel terrace is recommended. You can use the Mount Lavinia Hotel pool for an affordable fee.','冈嘎拉马寺（Gangaramaya Temple）融合了斯里兰卡、泰国、印度和中国建筑特点，精雕细琢，是斯里兰卡最重要的寺庙之一。寺庙拥有图书馆、博物馆、宿舍和一座三层的佛学院。博物馆不大，珍藏着数尊高大的佛像和数根巨大的象牙，还有罗汉舍利、珠宝、纯金法器、象牙法器以及一些来自日本、缅甸、泰国、中国等地的佛像。博物馆的后方还有一座仿印尼波罗浮屠的缩小石雕群，一层一层向上排列，供无法亲身前往那里朝圣的信徒膜拜。据称在所有藏品中，最珍贵的是一撮来自佛陀的头发，通常被紧锁于保险箱中，一般人无缘得见。',0,3588,138,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Mount%20Lavinia%20Beach/Thumb%20Mount%20Lavinia%20Beach.jpg','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Mount%20Lavinia%20Beach/Mount%20Lavinia%20Beach.html','',99),(38,'Old Dutch Hospital','旧荷兰医院','','Dutch Hospital Shopping Precinct, Hospital St, Colombo','地处靠近科伦坡Galle Face海滩绿地的Colombo三区。距离Colombo Fort火车站步行15分钟。','','','','科伦坡全部购物中心排名第三的地方','','','#ERROR!','http://www.uda.lk/dutchhospital',0,0,'','旧国会大厦是一栋始建于英国殖民统治时期的新巴洛克风格建筑。大楼面朝印度洋，当年在建造这栋国会大厦（当时称立法会大楼）时， 时任英属锡兰殖民地政府总督的Sir Henry McCallum先生提出在加勒菲斯北段填海兴建的大胆想法。同时为了方便殖民地政府各部门之间的沟通衔接，除了立法会外，数个殖民地政府机构也在大楼附设的裙楼里办公，直至1948年2月4日斯里兰卡正式宣布独立，成为英联邦的自治领土，定国名为锡兰。1972年5月22日锡兰正式改国名为斯里兰卡。',0,7754,54,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Old%20Dutch%20Hospital/Thumb%20Old%20Dutch%20Hospital.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Old%20Dutch%20Hospital/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Old%20Dutch%20Hospital/Old%20Dutch%20Hospital.mp3',99),(39,'17th Century Dutch Church in Galle Fort','荷兰教堂','','Church St.与Middle St.交叉口','从新城门进入后，右转进入Church St','','9:00-17:00','Nice little old church to look at in the town, there is not much to see other than some interesting ancient tombstones','拥有浓厚的历史痕迹的教堂','0','0','','',0,0,'','荷兰教堂（Dutch Church），又称为荷兰归正会教（DutchReformed Church），初建于1640年，由荷兰指挥官Casparus deJong和他的妻子捐赠，用来表达他们对第一个孩子诞生的感谢。教堂建于一座17世纪中叶葡萄牙女修道院的遗址之上，外部以白色为底，轮廓线条优美，内部没有太多华丽的装饰，只有一些图案简单的彩色玻璃拼花窗，以及一个突出于教堂前方左部的讲道坛上方的巨大天蓬。教堂最为特别的是地面及外墙铺满墓碑，他们是昔日荷兰籍驻加勒居民的墓碑，由旧荷兰时期的荷兰墓园被搬迁至此。最古老的源于1662年，而另一块最为吸引人的则是加勒指挥官E.A.H.Abraham的墓碑，该墓碑位于教堂入口处不远，墓碑上方装饰着沙漏和头颅。',0,4000,109,3,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/17th%20Century%20Dutch%20Church%20in%20Galle%20Fort/Thumb%2017th%20Century%20Dutch%20Church%20in%20Galle%20Fort.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/17th%20Century%20Dutch%20Church%20in%20Galle%20Fort/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/17th%20Century%20Dutch%20Church%20in%20Galle%20Fort/17th%20Century%20Dutch%20Church%20in%20Galle%20Fort.mp3',99),(40,'Old Muncipal Council','市政厅','','Cinnamon Gardens，Colombo 07','位于公园东北角，可步行前往','不对外开放，只可在外参观','不对外开放，只可在外参观','The Colombo Municipal Council is the local council for Colombo, the largest city and financial centre in Sri Lanka.','斯里兰卡的“小白宫”','','','-6345','www.cmc.lk',0,0,'The Colombo Municipal Council is the local council for Colombo, the largest city and financial centre in Sri Lanka. The council was formed in 1865 and first met in 1866.[1] The municipal council is the oldest and the largest local government authority in Sri Lanka and, as of 2001, covers a resident population of over 600,000. It has 53 elected representatives and over 12,000 employees.','维哈马哈德维公园（Viharamahadevi Park）是科伦坡最大的公园，曾被称作维多利亚公园，由英国人建造。斯里兰卡独立后，为纪念光复祖国的英雄图杜盖穆努（Dutugemunu）国王的母亲，改名为维哈马哈德维公园。公园东边是科伦坡市政厅，南边是科伦坡国家博物馆和科伦坡艺术馆，北边不远处有著名的冈嘎拉马寺，面积很大，几乎占据了古城地区一半的面积。公园内常年绿树成荫，是当地居民假日和休闲的好去处。到了周末，在公园南侧会有一个艺术集市，本地的艺术家会聚集在此，展示他们的作品。',0,7744,125,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Old%20Muncipal%20Council/Thumb%20Old%20Muncipal%20Council.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Old%20Muncipal%20Council/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Old%20Muncipal%20Council/Old%20Muncipal%20Council.mp3',99),(41,'Old Parliament','旧国会大厦','','Fort,Colombo,Sri Lanka','距离科伦坡市中心30分钟TuTu车程，可以选择乘坐TuTu车前往。','','不对外开放，只可在外参观','The?Old Parliament Building, is the building that houses the?Presidential Secretariat?of?Sri Lanka.','一座非常有特色的兰卡建筑','','','','',0,0,'The Old Parliament Building, is the building that houses the Presidential Secretariat of Sri Lanka. Situated in the Colombo fort facing the sea, it is in close proximity to the President\'s House, Colombo. The building houses the island\'s legislature for 53 years until the New Parliament Complex was opened at Sri Jayawardenepura in 1983. It is next to the General Treasury Building.','芒特拉维尼亚位于科伦坡南郊12公里处，这是一片离科伦坡市中心最近的沙滩度假胜地。蒙特拉维尼亚因那栋前英国总督府改造的海边酒店而闻名，沙滩也被蒙特拉维尼亚酒店分割成两部分，一部分由酒店私有，一部分供当地人玩耍。酒店私有的沙滩，游客也可以进去享用。',0,9705,54,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Old%20Parliament/Thumb%20Old%20Parliament.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Old%20Parliament/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Old%20Parliament/Old%20Parliament.mp3',99),(42,'Viharamahadevi Park','维哈马哈德维公园','','Cinnamon Gardens，Colombo 07','可选择从加勒菲斯绿地搭乘突突车，15分钟可以到达，价格约200卢比','','日出到日落','It is the oldest and largest park of the Port of Colombo.','科伦坡最大的公园','0','0','-7059','',0,0,'The Viharamahadevi Park (formerly Victoria Park) is a public park located in Colombo, next to the National Museum in Sri Lanka. It is the oldest and largest park of the Port of Colombo. Situated in front of the colonial-era Town Hall building, the park is named after Queen Viharamahadevi, the mother of King Dutugamunu. The park was built on land donated to the Colombo city by Charles Henry de Soysa during the British rule of Sri Lanka, and used to be named \"Victoria Park\" after Queen Victoria. During World War II it was occupied by the British Army with Australian 17th Brigade based at Victoria Park. After the war the park was restored and open to the public in 1951.','荷兰医院旧址是荷兰殖民时期（1656-1796）的旧建筑，曾是当地当时首屈一指的医院。如今，充满历史厚重感的医院已经被改造成非常具有现代风格的购物餐饮街区，老式建筑内别有洞天，风格与北京三里屯或者上海新天地非常相似。在这里你可以找到各种时尚品牌、手工艺品，也有各种以西式餐饮为主的餐厅或者咖啡室。购物区有定期的娱乐活动以及美食街，还有街头艺人表演和文化展览。',0,8301,141,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Viharamahadevi%20Park/Thumb%20Viharamahadevi%20Park.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Viharamahadevi%20Park/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Viharamahadevi%20Park/Viharamahadevi%20Park.mp3',99),(43,'Sri Dalada Maligawa','佛牙寺','','Sri Dalada Veediya，Kandy','从汽车站或火车站步行10分钟即可到达','','6:00-20:00礼拜时间5:30、1','Temple of the Sacred Tooth Relic, a World Heritage Site in Kandy','斯里兰卡著名的佛教胜地','1500LKR','1500卢比','','www.sridaladamaligawa.lk',0,0,'Sri Dalada Maligawa or the Temple of the Sacred Tooth Relic is a Buddhist temple in the city of Kandy, Sri Lanka. It is located in the royal palace complex of the former Kingdom of Kandy, which houses the relic of the tooth of the Buddha. Since ancient times, the relic has played an important role in local politics because it is believed that whoever holds the relic holds the governance of the country. Kandy was the last capital of the Sri Lankan kings and is a World Heritage Site mainly due to the temple.','佛牙寺（Temple of the sacred tooth relic / Sri Dalada Maligawa）内供奉着斯里兰卡国宝释迦牟尼牙舍利，这也是康堤成为世界佛教圣地的重要原因。佛牙寺位于康堤湖畔，是一座僧伽罗风格的八角形建筑，像一朵漂浮在湖面的白莲花。寺院有上下两层，厅堂套厅堂，结构复杂，主要有佛殿、鼓殿、长厅、诵经厅、大宝库、内殿等，其中最重要的建筑是中心大殿。大殿天花板上布满了彩绘和黄金的金饰。佛牙供奉在二层的内殿，也是寺中的核心，但有说法称真正的佛牙早已被转移。每天晨、中午、黄昏定时打开三次供人礼拜，即每日5:30、10:15和19:15，每次约半个小时，信徒可以在这段时间瞻仰和祈祷膜拜供奉佛牙的佛牙塔。',0,9394,99,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Sri%20Dalada%20Maligawa/Thumb%20Sri%20Dalada%20Maligawa.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Sri%20Dalada%20Maligawa/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Sri%20Dalada%20Maligawa/Sri%20Dalada%20Maligawa.mp3',99),(44,'Kandy Lake','康提湖','','Sri Dalada Veediya，Kandy','和佛牙寺处于同一位置，从佛牙寺正门出来便是','','','Kiri Muhuda or the Sea of Milk','康提湖，一个坐落于圣城中先的偌大人工湖','','','','',0,0,'Kandy Lake, also known as Kiri Muhuda or the Sea of Milk, is an artificial lake in the heart of the hill city of Kandy, Sri Lanka, built in 1807 by King Sri Wickrama Rajasinghe next to the Temple of the Tooth. Over the years, it was reduced in size. It is a protected lake, with fishing banned. There are many legends and folklore regarding the lake. One such is that the small island at its center was used by the king\'s helm for bathing and was connected to the palace by secret tunnel.','康提湖（又译做康堤湖）位于康堤城市中心，1807年由末代国王Sri Vikrama Rajasinha主持建造，现今湖面面积逐年减小。湖中央有一个漂亮的小岛，上面遍布棕榈树和灌木丛，传说这里是国王与皇后沐浴的地方。深绿色的康堤湖是一个受保护的湖泊，四周种植着各种树木，湖中严禁垂钓。所以这里鱼多且肥，几乎不怕人。湖面上时常可以看到鸬鹚、白鹭、鹈鹕等鸟类。如果天气好，傍晚橘黄色的湖面漂浮着佛牙寺僧人的诵经声，是一种神奇的体验。清晨和傍晚适合摄影。',0,5065,114,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Kandy%20Lake/Thumb%20Kandy%20Lake.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Kandy%20Lake/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Kandy%20Lake/Kandy%20Lake.mp3',99),(45,'Peradeniya Royal Botanical Garden','佩拉尼亚皇家植物园','','Peradeniya road，Kandy','可选择从康堤汽车站搭乘前往佩拉尼亚的公共汽车，在Botanical Garden站下车','全年开放Open all ye','8:00-17:00','It is renowned for its collection of orchids.','亚洲最大的植物园，世界上最好的热带植物园之一，曾经是康堤国王的御花园。','1500LKR','1500卢比','','',0,0,'Royal Botanic Gardens, Peradeniya are about 5.5 km to the west of the city of Kandy in the Central Province of Sri Lanka. It attracts 2 million visitors annually.[1] It is near the Mahaweli River (the longest in Sri Lanka).[2] It is renowned for its collection of orchids. The garden includes more than 4000 species of plants, including orchids, spices, medicinal plants and palm trees.[1] Attached to it is the National Herbarium of Sri Lanka. The total area of the botanical garden is 147 acres (0.59 km2), at 460 meters above sea level, and with a 200-day annual rainfall. It is managed by the Division of National Botanic Gardens of the Department of Agriculture.','佩拉尼亚皇家植物园距离康堤约半小时车程，游览时间在1小时左右比较合适。该园三面环绕马哈维利河，风景绚丽，是亚洲最大的植物园，也是世界上最好的热带植物园之一，曾经是康堤国王的御花园。如今园内种植收藏了超过4000种斯里兰卡本土，以及海外引进种植的植物，不乏一些非常稀有珍贵的热带植物。这里四季如春，植物茂盛，到处鲜花盛开，还有一个专门养殖兰花的漂亮温室。当地人地票价非常便宜，所以这里经常可以看见谈恋爱的本地情侣。斯里兰卡全国最大的综合性大学——佩拉德尼亚大学位于植物园旁，建筑富丽堂皇，同样值得游览。',0,8127,118,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Peradeniya%20Royal%20Botanical%20Garden/Thumb%20Peradeniya%20Royal%20Botanical%20Garden.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Peradeniya%20Royal%20Botanical%20Garden/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Peradeniya%20Royal%20Botanical%20Garden/Peradeniya%20Royal%20Botanical%20Garden.mp3',99),(46,'Lankatilaka Vihara','兰卡提克寺','','Sri Lankathilake Rajamaha Viharaya, Kandy','从尕达拉德尼亚寺往南步行3公里即可到达','','','','','','','','www.kandycity.lk',0,0,'','建于14世纪，是斯里兰卡最壮观的庙宇之一，它建在一块表面并不平整的巨石之上，上下三层，气势恢弘，寺内有三百多年历史的壁画。由于寺庙地势较高，可以俯瞰周围田园风光。',0,8452,96,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Lankatilaka%20Vihara/Thumb%20Lankatilaka%20Vihara.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Lankatilaka%20Vihara/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Lankatilaka%20Vihara/Lankatilaka%20Vihara.mp3',99),(47,'Gadaladeniya Temple','尕达拉德尼亚寺','','Gadaladeniya Temple, Gadaldeniya Rd, Kandy','从康堤乘坐643路，Gadaladeniya站下','','','','','300LKR','300卢比','','',0,0,'','距康堤16公里，建于1344年，由于受达罗毗荼建筑风格影响，主殿为石殿，还拥有一座印度教副楼。寺庙内有一尊坐佛和一座被四座小佛塔环绕的舍利塔，除此之外，色彩鲜艳的庙门尤其值得一看。',0,7881,83,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Gadaladeniya%20Temple/Thumb%20Gadaladeniya%20Temple.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Gadaladeniya%20Temple/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Gadaladeniya%20Temple/Gadaladeniya%20Temple.mp3',99),(48,'Embekka Temple','恩贝卡寺','','Embekka Temple, Embekka Pilimatalawa Road, Kandy','从康堤乘坐643路，到恩?卡村下，步行1公里；或者从兰卡提克寺向后走5公里','','','','','300LKR','300卢比','','',0,0,'','建于14世纪甘姆博尔王朝时期，寺庙面积很小，却容纳了佛教和印度教。不过寺庙最值得关注的是鼓殿长廊中的雕花木柱，上面雕刻了各种虚构的动物，还有各种人物形态，总计514个，栩栩如生，非常有研究价值',0,4049,77,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Embekka%20Temple/Thumb%20Embekka%20Temple.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Embekka%20Temple/vtour/tour.html','','',99),(49,'Pinnawala Elephant Orphanage','大象孤儿院','','Pinnawala，Kegalla，Sri Lanka','可选择从康堤乘坐662路公交车到Kegalla，乘坐681公交车可以到达大象孤儿院；也可以在此处乘坐突突车，花费约150','','8:30-18:00喂食时间9:15、1','','这里是世界上第一所“大象孤儿院”，可以和大象亲密接触的好地方。','2500LKR','2500卢比','-8895','',0,0,'','平纳瓦拉大象孤儿院（Pinnawela Elephant Orphanage）位于科伦坡与康堤之间的平纳瓦拉，距离康堤45公里。从康堤出发约40分钟车程即可到达。大象孤儿院由斯里兰卡野生动物保护部门于1975年建立，专门收养那些无家可归、掉入陷阱、脱离象群，尤其是因战火受伤或身患疾病的幼象，是世界上第一所“大象孤儿院”。',0,7605,88,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Pinnawala%20Elephant%20Orphanage/Thumb%20Pinnawala%20Elephant%20Orphanage.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Pinnawala%20Elephant%20Orphanage/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Pinnawala%20Elephant%20Orphanage/Pinnawala%20Elephant%20Orphanage.html','',99),(50,'Kandy Garrison Cemetery','英国驻军公墓','','7/11, Anagarika Dharmapala Mawatha, Kandy','从佛牙寺往国家博物馆方向，路左边有Cemetery Road标志，爬一段坡路即可到达','','8:00-17:00','','见证了英国殖民时期的历史','0','0','','',0,0,'','英国驻军公墓（British Garrison Cemetery）在国家博物馆身后的小山丘上，有195座坟墓。这个令人无比伤感的地方建于1822年，用于埋葬在殖民时期死于疟疾、霍乱等热带疾病的英国公民。曾经这个墓地已经荒废，近些年依靠捐赠才从新开放，并且希望游人捐款捐物',0,8857,133,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Kandy%20Garrison%20Cemetery/Thumb%20Kandy%20Garrison%20Cemetery.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Kandy%20Garrison%20Cemetery/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Kandy%20Garrison%20Cemetery/Kandy%20Garrison%20Cemetery.mp3',99),(51,'Bahiravokanda Vihara Buddha Statue','珈蓝佛像','','Kandy, Sri Lanka','需乘车至Kandy Road Bus Stop，下车后沿Wathhimi Rd向东南方步行约500米即可抵达','','','Hightlight of Kandy','这是康堤市内的一处非常著名的地标性景点，这里有一尊通体白色的释迦摩尼像','0','0','','',0,0,'','珈蓝佛像是建造在山顶的大佛，从远处就可以看到，很壮观，在当地也可算是一个地标的建筑。',0,4484,66,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Bahiravokanda%20Vihara%20Buddha%20Statue/Thumb%20Bahiravokanda%20Vihara%20Buddha%20Statue.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Bahiravokanda%20Vihara%20Buddha%20Statue/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Bahiravokanda%20Vihara%20Buddha%20Statue/Bahiravokanda%20Vihara%20Buddha%20Statue.mp3',99),(52,'Ceylon Tea Museum','锡兰茶博物馆','','Hantana, Kandy 20000, Sri Lanka','需乘车至Kaluwala Bus Stop站，下车后沿山路向东步行约1公里即可抵达','周二至周六、周日','8:30-16:30（周二至周六）8:3','The Ceylon Tea Museum is located in the former Hantane Tea Factory,[1] which was originally constructed in 1925.','可以深入了解该地制茶的历史的地方','','','','http://www.ceylonteamuseum.com/',0,0,'The Ceylon Tea Museum at Hantane, three kilometres from Kandy city is served by a motorable road that circles the museum, provides easy access and adequate parking facilities for cars and tourist coaches. The museum consists of four floors. The ground floor and the second floor exhibit very old items of machinery and the first floor consist of a library and an auditorium with facilities for audio visual presentations. The third floor is allocated to tea sales outlets, where a selection of Sri Lanka\'s fine tea is available. The entire top floor is a tea cafe. A panoramic view of the Kandy town surrounded by the beautiful Hunasgiriya, Knuckles Range and the Matale range of hills can be viewed through a telescope mounted on the fourth floor. The grounds surrounding the Tea Museum are landscap','锡兰茶博物馆坐落于康提市区外三公里处。博物馆共有四层，一、二层展示了当地人民在较早时期加工茶叶的工具，一层有阅览室可以让游客更深入了解该地制茶的历史。三层则是茶叶销售点，四层则是餐厅。博物馆周边地区种满了茶叶，景色宜人。',0,6849,82,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Ceylon%20Tea%20Museum/Thumb%20Ceylon%20Tea%20Museum.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Ceylon%20Tea%20Museum/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Ceylon%20Tea%20Museum/Ceylon%20Tea%20Museum.mp3',99),(53,'Arthur\'s Seat','Arthur\'s Seat','','Kandy, Sri Lanka','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'','',0,3792,66,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Arthur\'s%20Seat/Thumb%20Arthur\'s%20Seat.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Arthur\'s%20Seat/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Arthur\'s%20Seat/Arthur\'s%20Seat.mp3',99),(54,'Kandy World War 2 Cemetery','二战墓地','','Lady Magdalene Drive, Kandy 20000, Sri Lanka','','','','The Kandy War Cemetery is a British military cemetery in Kandy, Sri Lanka, for soldiers of the British Empire who were killed during World War II as well as a soldier who died during World War I.','纪念二战牺牲士兵的墓园','0','0','','',0,0,'The Kandy War Cemetery is a British military cemetery in Kandy, Sri Lanka, for soldiers of the British Empire who were killed during World War II as well as a soldier who died during World War I.\n\nThere are 203 buried consisting of: 107 British, 35 East Africans, 26 Sri Lankans, 23 Indians, 6 Canadians, 3 Italians, 1 Frenchman and 2 unidentified persons,Of the 203 dead, 151 were army, 32 were air force, 16 were navy, 2 were unidentified, 1 was merchant navy and 1 was from the national fire service.','由于亭可马里在二战时期是英军的作战基地以及主要港口，因此大量英军也埋葬于此，二战英军公墓内主要是二战时期(部分是二战后)英军的墓地，维护的很整齐。',0,9417,134,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Kandy%20World%20War%202%20Cemetery/Thumb%20Kandy%20World%20War%202%20Cemetery.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Kandy%20World%20War%202%20Cemetery/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Kandy%20World%20War%202%20Cemetery/Kandy%20World%20War%202%20Cemetery.mp3',99),(55,'National Maritime Museum in Galle Fort','加勒城堡博物馆','','Galle, Sri Lanka','','','','','这是一家国家海洋博物馆','','','','',0,0,'The National Maritime Museum in Galle, Sri Lanka is situated within Galle Fort. It was first opened to the public on 9 May 1992 and is located in a 1671 Dutch Warehouse above the Old Gate of Galle Fort. Whilst the building housing the museum survived the impact of the 26 December 2004 tsunami, the adjoining UNESCO Maritime Archaeology Unit was completely destroyed and all the exhibitions were flood damaged[1] and the majority of maritime archeological artifacts were lost. Under Sri Lanka – Netherlands Cultural Co-operation Program, the Royal Government of Netherlands provided financial assistance for reconstruction of the Maritime Museum. After 3 years period of reconstruction, the Maritime Museum was re-opened to the public.','加勒的国家海事博物馆由要塞仓库改建，陈列着大量海下发掘的文物，如地图、船只、绳索、陶器、酒杯、烟袋、火炮等等，这些文物大都来自南部海岸外海沉船，有的文物有近800年的历史。海事博物馆除了陈列这些文物外，还有一些有关加勒历史、海底生物介绍等。',0,4707,116,3,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/National%20Maritime%20Museum%20in%20Galle%20Fort/Thumb%20National%20Maritime%20Museum%20in%20Galle%20Fort.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/National%20Maritime%20Museum%20in%20Galle%20Fort/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/National%20Maritime%20Museum%20in%20Galle%20Fort/National%20Maritime%20Museum%20in%20Galle%20Fort.mp3',99),(56,'Light House','乌得勒支碉堡与灯塔','','Galle, Sri Lanka','','不对外开放，只能在外围参观。','不对外开放，只能在外围参观。','','加勒的标志性建筑之一的灯塔','','','','',0,0,'This is Sri Lanka\'s oldest light station dating back to 1848, but the original 24.5-metre-high (80 ft) lighthouse built by the British was located about 100 metres (330 ft) from the current site; however, it was destroyed by fire in 1934. The existing 26.5-metre-high (87 ft) lighthouse was erected here in 1939. The original light was furnished with a glass prism lens floating in a bath of mercury (to reduce friction) and was powered by a weight driven machine.','乌德勒支碉堡位于加勒老城的东南角，面向大海，它的上方便是加勒的标志性建筑之一的灯塔。灯塔建于1938年，高18米，关于加勒的各种纪念品上都会有出现这个灯塔。',0,6284,132,3,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/Light%20House/Thumb%20Light%20House.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/Light%20House/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/Light%20House/Light%20House.mp3',99),(57,'Old Gate','老城门','','Galle, Sri Lanka','','','0:00-24:00','','','','','','',0,0,'','',0,7300,65,3,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/Old%20Gate/Thumb%20Old%20Gate.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/Old%20Gate/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/Old%20Gate/Old%20Gate.mp3',99),(58,'New Zealand Farm','新西兰牧场','','New Zealand Farm, Sri Lanka','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'','',0,7650,72,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/New%20Zealand%20Farm/Thumb%20New%20Zealand%20Farm.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/New%20Zealand%20Farm/vtour/tour.html','','',99),(59,'St Clairs Falls','圣凯尔斯大瀑布','','St Clairs Falls, Talawakele, Sri Lanka','','','','Little Niagara of Sri Lanka','斯里兰卡的小尼亚加拉','0','0','','',0,0,'St. Clair\'s Falls is one of the widest waterfalls in Sri Lanka and is commonly known as the \"Little Niagara of Sri Lanka\". It is one of six waterfalls affected by the Upper Kotmale Hydropower Project.','圣凯尔斯大瀑布坐落于努瓦勒埃利耶大区内，是斯里兰卡最宽最大的瀑布之一，素有“斯里兰卡的尼亚加拉”之称。',0,6348,114,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/St%20Clairs%20Falls/Thumb%20St%20Clairs%20Falls.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/St%20Clairs%20Falls/vtour/tour.html','','',99),(60,'Lunuganga','巴瓦花园','','Dedduwa, Haburugala, Bentota 32350, Sri Lanka','距离科伦坡一个半小时车程','','9:00-11:30, 2:00-3:0','Geoffrey Bawa\'s Garden','斯里兰卡国宝级建筑师巴瓦的花园','1500LKR','1500卢比','','http://www.geoffreybawa.com/lunuganga-country-esta',0,0,'Lunuganga Estate was the country home of the renowned Sri Lankan architect Geoffrey Bawa. Started in 1947, the garden led Bawa, a lawyer called to the Bar at the Inner Temple in 1940, to decide to become an architect. As he went on to become Sri Lanka\'s and one of Asia\'s most prolific and influential architects, the garden at the Lunuganga estate remained his first muse and experimental laboratory for new ideas. He continued to change and experiment with its spaces and structures throughout his life until his final illness in 1998. Left to the Lunuganga Trust on his demise in 2003, the gardens are now open to the public and the buildings on the estate are run as a country house hotel.','Lunuganga最初是巴瓦年轻时买下的一片废弃的橡胶园，39岁从AA建筑联盟学成归国，便开始改造设计他买下橡胶园，并将其称为lunuganga。1948年，这里是一栋不起眼的小房子，四周种有25英亩的橡胶树。从那时起，在巴瓦长久而美妙的设计中，人们移动了山丘，平整了台地，将森林重新种植，使远景视野变得开放。直到1992年最后一次改建完成。巴瓦在书中写到：多年来，花园已经逐渐变成一个充斥着许多情绪的地方，它是想象力的成果，为我提供了一个休息的寓所，可以独处或者和朋友们共度时光。观察这个场所令人感到愉悦，正如朋友的评论说道：“若能有一个花园，这将是一个可爱的地方!”那位卡车司机在花园里漫步，卸下他的砖，然后对我说:“这是一个受到了很多很多祝福的地方!”',0,5793,109,8,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Sights/Lunuganga/Thumb%20Lunuganga.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Sights/Lunuganga/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Bentota%20&%20Hikkaduwa/Sights/Lunuganga/Lunuganga.mp3',99),(61,'Wolfendhal Dutch Church','荷兰教堂','','Wolfendhal Ln, Colombo 01300, Sri Lanka','','','','One of the oldest Protestant churches still in use in the country','斯里兰卡境内仍在使用的最古老的教堂','','','#ERROR!','',0,0,'Wolvendaal Church (Wolvendaalse Kerk) is located in Pettah, a neighbourhood of Colombo. It is one of the most important Dutch Colonial era buildings in Sri Lanka, and is one of the oldest Protestant churches still in use in the country.','荷兰教堂坐落在斯里兰卡首都科伦坡的Pettah区，是斯里兰卡现存最重要的荷兰殖民时期建筑之一，也时斯里兰卡国内仍旧在使用的最古老的教堂。',0,6919,50,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Wolfendhal%20Dutch%20Church/Thumb%20Wolfendhal%20Dutch%20church.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Wolfendhal%20Dutch%20Church/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Wolfendhal%20Dutch%20Church/Wolfendhal%20Dutch%20Church.mp3',99),(62,'Demodara Station','Demodara Station','','Demodara, Sri Lanka','','','0:00-24:00','The third last station on the Main Line','高山小火车九孔桥所在的火车站','0','0','','',0,0,'Demodara railway station is the third last station on the Main Line, and is 277.71 km (172.56 mi) away from Colombo. It is located 912.5 m (2,994 ft) above mean sea level and 8 km (5.0 mi) from Badulla, the capital city of Uva Province. All the trains that run on the Main Line, including the Podi Menike and Udarata Menike express trains stop at the station.','Demodara 火车站是斯里兰卡铁路主干道上的第三个火车站，距离首都科伦坡277.71公里，海拔912.5米，是斯里兰卡高山小火车最美的路段。',0,7216,75,9,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Demodara%20Station/Thumb%20Demodara%20Station.jpg','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/video_utovr/video/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Demodara%20Station/Demodara%20Station.html','',99),(63,'Elle Pass','埃拉公路','','Ella, Sri Lanka','','','0:00-24:00','The road that leads from Elle town to Wellaway','中部山区到南部海滨的必经之道','0','0','','',0,0,'Elle pass is the road that leads from Elle town to Wellawaya, which is a low country area towards the south. Its called Elle pass because the road has a steep descent between 2 mountain ridge and offers a breathtaking and panoramic unique view as the road heads towards Wellawaya.','Elle pass连接着 Elle 和 Wellawaya，是斯里兰卡的交通要道，是中部山区到南部海滨的必经之道，途中风景优美秀丽。',0,5325,75,9,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Elle%20Pass/Thumb%20Elle%20Pass.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Elle%20Pass/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Ella%20&%20Hatton/Sights/Elle%20Pass/Elle%20Pass.mp3',99),(64,'Hanthana Hills','Hanthana Hills','','Hanthana, Sri Lanka','','','','National Environment Act','国家自然保护区','','','','',0,0,'The Hanthana Mountain Range lies in central Sri Lanka, south-west of the city of Kandy. It was declared as an environmental protection area in February 2010 under the National Environment Act.The maximum height of the range is 3800 ft. The mountain range consists of seven peaks. The highest one being the Uura Kanda. The range is a favourite destination among the mountain hikers in Sri Lanka. University of Peradeniya is situated adjacent to the Hanthana mountain range.','',0,8976,100,2,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Hanthana%20Hills/Thumb%20Hanthana%20Hills.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Hanthana%20Hills/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Kandy/Sights/Hanthana%20Hills/Hanthana%20Hills.mp3',99),(65,'Fishing Area','尼甘布鱼市','','Negombo, Sri Lanka','','','06:00','The large open air fish market is the second largest in the country','体验当地渔民生活与风俗的鱼市','0','0','','',0,0,'The large open air fish market is the second largest in the country. It gives you an unpretentious insight into the local fisher community. The market is loud, vibrant and smells like fish! You will be able to witness the fishermen in hundreds of boats bringing in their days catch. See how the wholesalers and restaurateurs trade and watch the packing and loading of fish for distribution across the country as well as for export – worldwide. The retail area is a bustling hive of activity – with customers negotiating prices with mom and pop fish vendors.','尼甘布是个著名的鱼村，一共有两个鱼市，一个在中心城区，另外一个在外围。菜市场附近的鱼市可以观察到尼干布居民日常生活的状态。外围的鱼市场则规模更大更开放，能够拍到渔民归航的场面。',0,4907,125,4,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/Fishing%20Area/Thumb%20Fishing%20Area.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/Fishing%20Area/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Negombo/Sights/Fishing%20Area/Fishing%20Area.mp3',99),(66,'Kanniya Hot Water Spring','Kanniya Hot Water Spring','','Kanniya, Trincomalee 31000, Sri Lanka','','','0:00-24:00','Kanniya Hot Springs is famous hot well in Sri Lanka from the past','五千年历史的温泉','','','','',0,0,'Kanniya Hot Springs is famous hot well in Sri Lanka from the past.Over 5000 years ago. There are seven wells in a square shape. Wells are only 3–4 feet deep and you can clearly see the bottom. The temperature is considerably high but vary from one spring to another. Wells run out of water, when 10-15 buckets of water are taken out.','斯里兰卡最古老的温泉，有大约五千多年的历史了。说是温泉其实只是几口原始的温泉井，只能用水桶提水冲洗。有许多朝圣者',0,8608,75,11,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/Kanniya%20Hot%20Water%20Spring/Thumb%20Kanniya%20Hot%20Water%20Spring.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/Kanniya%20Hot%20Water%20Spring/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/Kanniya%20Hot%20Water%20Spring/Kanniya%20Hot%20Water%20Spring.mp3',99),(67,'koneswaram Kovil','湿婆神庙','','Koneswaram, Trincomalee, Sri Lanka','','','','Konesvaram is revered as one the Pancha Ishwarams of Sri Lanka for long time','北部印度教圣地','10LKR','10卢比','#ERROR!','',0,0,'Koneswaram temple, is a classical-medieval Hindu temple dedicated to Lord Shiva in Trincomalee, Eastern Sri Lanka. The temple is situated atop Konesar Malai, a promontory from where overlooking of large body of Indian Ocean, nearby eastern coast, as well as Gokarna bay. Konesvaram is revered as one the Pancha Ishwarams of Sri Lanka for long time. Being a major place for Hindu pilgrimage, it was labelled \"Rome of the Gentiles/Pagans of the Orient\" in some records. Konesvaram holds a significant role in the religious and cultural history of Sri Lanka, as it was likely built during the reign of the early Cholas and the Five Dravidians of the Early Pandyan Kingdom.','Koneswaram 寺庙是一座古老的印度教寺庙，供奉着湿婆神，是斯里兰卡东部主要的朝拜圣地',0,4319,50,11,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/koneswaram%20Kovil/Thumb%20koneswaram%20Kovil.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/koneswaram%20Kovil/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1503024527/Sri%20Lanka/Trincomalee/Sights/koneswaram%20Kovil/koneswaram%20Kovil.mp3',99),(68,'Galle Fort','加勒城堡','','Galle Fort, Galle, Sri Lanka','','','0:00-24:00','An urban ensemble which illustrates the interaction of European architecture and South Asian traditions from the 16th to the 19th centuries','殖民亚洲风格的完美融合','0','0','#ERROR!','http://gallefortguide.com/',0,0,'Basking on the southern coast of Sri Lanka in the bay of Galle, the Fort was first built by the Portuguese in 1588 before being extensively fortified by the Dutch in the mid 1600s. Recognized by UNESCO for its cultural heritage value, the Fort was declared a World Heritage Site in 1988 as a unique exposition of \"an urban ensemble which illustrates the interaction of European architecture and South Asian traditions from the 16th to the 19th centuries.\"','在荷兰殖民时期，荷兰人为了显示在斯里兰卡统治坚不可摧，在加勒建立了一座占地36万平方米的城堡，标准的欧洲风格。除了城堡之外，加勒还有其他殖民时代的遗迹，或许是小路，或许是小洋房，甚至可能只是一道门或一面墙，都能看到他们流着欧洲的血。 除了城堡，加勒便是一个小小的东南亚海滨城市，也有沙滩，也有碧海。但是当这里有了那些欧洲建筑，这不是简单的叠加，而是一种勾兑，全如曼特宁咖啡和苏格兰威士忌，所谓异国情调，就是不明所属的美好。',0,6771,79,3,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/Galle%20Fort/Thumb%20Galle%20Fort.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/Galle%20Fort/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Galle%20&%20Merissa/Sights/Galle%20Fort/Galle%20Fort.mp3',99),(69,'BMICH','班达拉奈克国际展览中心','','BMICH, Colombo. Sri Lanka','','','','The best of professional conference facilities','中斯友谊的象征','','','#ERROR!','http://www.bmich.lk/',0,0,'The Bandaranaike Memorial International Conference Hall being the very first purpose built convention center in Asia combines the best of professional conference facilities with the once in a life time opportunity to visit an island known as the paradise on earth - Sri Lanka! The Hall is an outright gift from the Government and People of the People\'s Republic of China as a mark of their esteem for the late Prime Minister and as a symbol of the ideals to which he was dedicated.','班达拉奈克国际会议大厦（Bandaranaike Memorial International Convention Hall）位于科伦坡贝塔区中心地带，建筑宏伟，精美壮观，是该市标志性建筑之一。大厦是由中国政府无偿援助斯里兰卡的，于1973年5月竣工，建成并投入使用30多年来，在斯里兰卡社会生活中发挥着重要作用。后由中国政府援建的纪念西丽玛沃·班达拉奈克展览中心和班达拉奈克国际研究中心分别于2003年1月和4月落成，与大厦构成统一的整体，被誉为“中斯友谊的象征”。',0,3898,87,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/BMICH/Thumb%20BMICH.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/BMICH/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/BMICH/BMICH.mp3',99),(70,'Colombo Museum','科伦坡博物馆','','Colombo Museum, Colombo, Sri Lanka','','','','The oldest museum of Sri Lanka','斯里兰卡最古老的博物馆，藏有“郑和碑”等大量中国文物','600LKR(250LKR for photo)','600卢比(相机票250了卢比）','#ERROR!','http://www.museum.gov.lk/web/index.php?option=com_',0,0,'The Colombo Museum as it was called at the beginning was established on 1st January 1877. It founder was Sir William Henry Gregory, the British Governor of Ceylon (Sri Lanka) at the time. The Royal Asiatic Society (CB) was instrumental in bringing to the notice of Gregory on his appointment as Governor in 1872 the need for a public museum with much difficulty the approval of the legislative council was obtained within a year. The Architect of the Public Works Department, J.G. Smither was able to prepare the plans for new structure on Italian architectural style. The construction was completed in 1876 and the Museum commenced it functions in the following year.','科伦坡国立博物馆Colombo National Museum是斯里兰卡最古老的博物馆。在科伦坡市。1877年建立，1980年建成新馆。馆内收藏斯里兰卡各个历史时期的珍贵文物，有各种石雕像、铜雕像、宝石、武器以及康提王朝时期的各种编织品、金属制品、手工艺品，最后一代康提国王的铠甲等。还有从康提运来的狮子王座，各地出土的中国瓷器。',0,3174,55,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Colombo%20Museum/Thumb%20Colombo%20Museum.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Colombo%20Museum/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Colombo%20Museum/Colombo%20Museum.mp3',99),(71,'New Parliment','新国会大厦','','New Parliment, Colombo, Sri Lanaka','','','','Symble of Sri Lanka','四面环水，大师之作','','','','',0,0,'Sri Lanka\'s original Parliament building dated from 1929 and had been built to accommodate a legislative assembly of fifty members. Occupying a long strip of land running between the southern edge of the Colombo Fort and the Beira Lake, it had been designed in the Anglo-Palladian style by Austin Woodeson, chief architect of the PWD, with highly modelled façades embodying a continuous double-height Ionic order above a rusticated podium. The Assembly was placed with its entrance portico facing towards the Indian Ocean, while the debating chamber occupied a double-height volume above a piano nobile and was arranged as a hemicycle with its seats focusing on the Speaker\'s chair. Behind the Assembly the Secretariat was housed in a separate block with its own entrances, connected to the Assembly ','国会大厦也称国会新大厦，位于科伦坡城新规划区中一个四面环水的岛上，距离科伦坡东部16公里。周围水清草绿，各种花卉灿烂开放，争奇斗艳，景色秀美，除了政治功能以外，也是科伦坡最著名的旅游景点之一。该大厦共有五层，周围的附属建筑为三层或四层，之间用平顶廊链接，占地约6.7公顷，建筑面积48100平方米',0,8181,63,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/New%20Parliment/Thumb%20New%20Parliment.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/New%20Parliment/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/New%20Parliment/New%20Parliment.mp3',99),(72,'Nelum Pokuna','Nelum Pokuna歌剧院','','110 Ananda Coomaraswamy Mawatha, Colombo 00700, Sri Lanka','','','','The Nelum Pokuna (Lotus Pond) – Mahinda Rajapakse Theatre is a fully equipped sate of the art performance centre','斯里兰卡最高级的视听盛宴','','','','http://lotuspond.lk/',0,0,'The Nelum Pokuna (Lotus Pond) – Mahinda Rajapakse Theatre is a fully equipped sate of the art performance centre, meant for large scale theatrical productions. The theatre consists of two venues for performances, which includes the main auditorium and an Open Air Amphitheater.\nSituated in the heart of Colombo city, this modern architectural masterpiece facilitates easy access for both local and foreign producers. The Theatre is also surrounded by several five Star Hotels and other commercial establishments.','',0,7383,100,1,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Nelum%20Pokuna/Thumb%20Nelum%20Pokuna.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Nelum%20Pokuna/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Colombo/Sights/Nelum%20Pokuna/Nelum%20Pokuna.mp3',99),(73,'Ramboda Falls','Ramboda Falls','','Ramboda Pass, Pussellawa, Sri Lanka','','','0:00-24:00','11th highest waterfall in Sri Lanka and 729th highest waterfall in the world','斯里兰卡第11大瀑布','','','','',0,0,'Ramboda Falls is 109 m high and 11th highest waterfall in Sri Lanka and 729th highest waterfall in the world.It is situated in Pussellawa area, on the A5 highway at Ramboda Pass.It formed by Panna Oya which is a tributary of Kothmale Oya. Altitude of the falls is 945 m above sea level.','马伯达瀑布海拔954米，瀑布高109米，是斯里兰卡第11高的瀑布，也是世界第729高的瀑布。瀑布旁有一家高六层的酒店，是专为观景设计。',0,9370,61,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Ramboda%20Falls/Thumb%20Ramboda%20Falls.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Ramboda%20Falls/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Ramboda%20Falls/Ramboda%20Falls.mp3',99),(74,'Tea Planation','茶园','','Nuwara Eliya, Sri Lanka','','','0:00-24:00','Little Rngland','如梦似幻的小英格兰','','','','',0,0,'The Nuwara Eliya region of Sri Lanka, often called \"Hill Tea Country\" is the scene of numerous tea estates such as Pedro, St. Claire and Blue Fields who, altogether, produce much of the premium Ceylon tea for the world market.','从康堤到努瓦勒埃利耶的盘山公路，海拔逐渐升高近千米，路两边则是如宝石般翠绿的茶叶种植园，不时间中还有如水晶般闪烁的大小水库瀑布。在这条公路上行驶不仅是视觉上的享受，间中还可以让车稍停片刻，欣赏下泰米尔采茶女如蝴蝶般穿梭于一排排的茶树丛中采摘茶叶和嫩芽的娴熟手法。',0,7703,56,5,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Tea%20Planation/Thumb%20Tea%20Planation.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Tea%20Planation/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502959672/Sri%20Lanka/Nuwara%20Eliya/Sights/Tea%20Planation/Tea%20Planation.mp3',99),(75,'The Grand Palace&Wat Phra Kaew','大皇宮','','Na Phra Lan Rd, Phra Nakhon, Bangkok','公交船至The Chang(N9)码头;公交车1,3, 25,44,47,53,60,82,91等多路车可到达附近','','8:30-15:30','The city\'s most famous landmark','最著名的地标性建筑','500Baht','500铢通票含玉佛寺、大皇宫、柚木宫的门票','','',0,0,'If there is one must-see sight that no visit to Bangkok would be complete without, it\'s the dazzling, spectacular Grand Palace, undoubtedly the city\'s most famous landmark. Built in 1782 - and for 150 years the home of the Thai King, the Royal court and the administrative seat of government - the Grand Palace of Bangkok is a grand old dame indeed, that continues to have visitors in awe with its beautiful architecture and intricate detail, all of which is a proud salute to the creativity and craftsmanship of Thai people. Within its walls were also the Thai war ministry, state departments, and even the mint. Today, the complex remains the spiritual heart of the Thai Kingdom.','大皇宫(The Grand Palace)紧邻湄南河，是曼谷中心内一处大规模古建筑群(计28座)，总面积二十一万八千四百平方米。大皇宫是仿照故都大城的旧皇宫建造的，经历代君王不断扩建，终于建成现在这座规模宏大的大皇宫建筑群。大皇宫是泰国诸多王宫之一，是历代王宫保存最完美、规模最大、最有民族特色的王宫。曼谷王朝从拉玛一世到拉玛八世，均居于大皇宫内。1946年拉玛八世在宫中被刺之后，拉玛九世便搬至大皇宫东面新建的集拉达宫居住。现在，大皇宫除了用于举行加冕典礼、宫廷庆祝等仪式和活动外，平时对外开放，成为泰国著名的游览场所。',0,7431,149,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/The%20Grand%20Palace&Wat%20Phra%20Kaew/Thumb%20The%20Grand%20Palace&Wat%20Phra%20Kaew.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/The%20Grand%20Palace&Wat%20Phra%20Kaew/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/The%20Grand%20Palace&Wat%20Phra%20Kaew/The%20Grand%20Palace&Wat%20Phra%20Kaew.mp3',99),(76,'Erawan Shrine','四面佛廟','','Hindu shrine in Bangkok, Thailand','位于世贸中心的斜对面，西隆商业区内。离暹罗广场（暹罗商业区）走路也就10分钟左右。空调巴士4、5路，普通巴士13、14路','','7:00-23:00','A popular worship attraction','来这里可以感受到神的权威','free','免费','','',0,0,'The Erawan Shrine, formally the Thao Maha Phrom Shrine, is a Hindu shrine in Bangkok, Thailand, that houses a statue of Phra Phrom, the Thai representation of the Hindu god of creation Lord Brahma. A popular worship attraction, it often features performances by resident Thai dance troupes, who are hired by worshippers in return for seeing their prayers at the shrine answered.','四面佛位于伊拉旺神祠中，供奉的神像高约4米，前后左右有四副面孔，分别代表慈、悲、喜、舍四种梵心，凡是祈求升天者必须勤修这四种功德。神像摆放在工艺精细的花岗岩神龛内，正襟危坐，全身金碧辉煌，四面都是同一面孔、同一姿态。这尊佛像原是印度婆罗门教主神之一梵天，乃是创造世界的神，法力无边。泰国各地包括住家庭院内多有设置。而以此处香火最为旺盛，从早到晚周围摆满了鲜花和香烛等贡品，还可以聘请穿传统服装的少女起舞歌唱。该四面佛2006年曾经被毁过，现已重新修缮。',0,3927,114,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Erawan%20Shrine/Thumb%20Erawan%20Shrine.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Erawan%20Shrine/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/video_utovr/video/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Erawan%20Shrine/Erawan%20Shrine.html','',99),(77,'Wat Pho','臥佛寺','','2 Sanamchai Road, Phra Nakhon in Bangkok, Thailand','位于玛哈叻路(MahaRatRoad)，紧邻大王宫的南面，可与大王宫、玉佛寺一起参观。','','8:00-17:00',' It houses a school of Thai medicine, and is also known as the birthplace of traditional Thai massage which is still taught and practiced at the temple.','它有一所泰国医学院，也被称为传统的泰式按摩的发源地','','100泰铢','','http://www.watpomassage.com/',0,8.7,'The temple is first on the list of six temples in Thailand classed as the highest grade of the first-class royal temples.It is associated with King Rama I who rebuilt the temple complex on an earlier temple site, and became his main temple where some of his ashes are enshrined.The temple was later expanded and extensively renovated by Rama III. The temple complex houses the largest collection of Buddha images in Thailand, including a 46 m long reclining Buddha. The temple is considered the earliest centre for public education in Thailand, and the marble illustrations and inscriptions placed in the temple for public instructions has been recognised by UNESCO in its Memory of the World Programme. It houses a school of Thai medicine, and is also known as the birthplace of traditional Thai mas','卧佛寺坐落在曼谷玉佛寺的旁边，拥有二百二十多年历史，始建于第一世皇建都时期，与玉佛寺一样具有重要意义，而该佛寺内传授的泰国传统按摩医术，堪称传统按摩之正宗。',0,8411,81,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Wat%20Pho/Thumb%20Wat%20Pho.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Wat%20Pho/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Wat%20Pho/Wat%20Pho.mp3',99),(78,'Khao San Road','考山路','','Khao San Road in Bangkok, Thailand','公交船至The Chang(N9)码头;公交车1,3, 25,44,47,53,60,82,91等多路车可到达附近','','','backpacker ghetto','背包客聚集地','','','-2596204','',0,8,'Khaosan Road or Khao San Road is a short street in central Bangkok, Thailand constructed in 1892 during the reign of Rama V. It is in the Banglamphu area of about 1 kilometre north of the Grand Palace and Wat Phra Kaew.\"Khaosan\" translates as \"milled rice\", a reminder that in former times the street was a major Bangkok rice market. In the last 20 years, however, Khaosan Road has developed into a world-famous \"backpacker ghetto\". It offers cheap accommodation, ranging from \"mattress in a box\" style hotels to reasonably priced 3-star hotels. In an essay on the backpacker culture of Khaosan Road, Susan Orlean called it \"the place to disappear\".','考山路夜市是曼谷最大、最受喜爱的夜市。 ·所有泰国小吃在这都能吃到，米粉汤、炒面、炸春卷、芒果饭、烤串等各种美食，好吃又实惠。街边随处可见各类纪念品小店、SPA和酒吧，即使到了深夜，依然灯火通明。这里住宿便宜又便利，是背包客聚集的地方。',0,6272,110,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Khao%20San%20Road/Thumb%20Khao%20San%20Road.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Khao%20San%20Road/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Restaurants/Khao%20San%20Road/Khao%20San%20Road.mp3',99),(79,'Jim Thompson Art Center','吉姆湯普森之家','',' 6 Soi Kasem San 2, Th Phra Ram I, Siam Sq Jim Thompson House,  Bangkok，Thailand','','','','The unique and famous Jim Thompson House Museum.','传奇人物之家','','','','http://www.jimthompsonartcenter.org/',0,0,'Located in the heart of Bangkok, The Jim Thompson Art Center is situated in the same compound as the unique and famous Jim Thompson House Museum. Serving as a haven for Bangkok’s local and international arts and cultural communities, the Center’s reputation as a place to mingle, interact and exchange dialogues is rapidly spreading. In conjunction with its exhibitions, the Center’s activities include parties, events, seminars, lectures and workshops.','作为振兴泰丝业的传奇人物James H.W. Thompson的故居，Jim Thompson博物馆由6栋传统柚木泰式建筑组成。被一座绿意浓浓的花园环绕，里面陈设有众多东南亚古董、画作、雕塑。通过参观这座泰式建筑，可以加深对泰丝和泰国历史的了解。这里出售很多小巧的丝绸制品，比如领带，丝巾等。故居内还有一座咖啡馆。作为一个私人的文化艺术馆，这里不定期的会有一些世界著名的先锋派艺人作品展出。',0,3131,63,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Jim%20Thompson%20Art%20Center/Thumb%20Jim%20Thompson%20Art%20Center.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Jim%20Thompson%20Art%20Center/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Jim%20Thompson%20Art%20Center/Jim%20Thompson%20Art%20Center.mp3',99),(80,'China Town','唐人街','','update later...','地铁华南蓬站（Hualamphong）;公交船Saphan Plut(N6)码头。\n由华南蓬火车总站步行10分钟可达，或','Wednesday - Sun','9:00-16:00 ','','小香港既视感','free','免费','','',0,0,'Bangkok’s Chinatown is a popular tourist attraction and a food haven for new generation gourmands who flock here after sunset to explore the vibrant street-side cuisine. At day time, it’s no less busy, as hordes of shoppers descend upon this 1-km strip and adjacent Charoenkrung Road to get a day’s worth of staple, trade gold, or pay a visit to one of the Chinese temples.','曼谷唐人街位于曼谷中心西南部，是城区最繁华的商业区之一，由三聘街、耀华力路、石龙军路三条大街以及许多街巷连接而成，以耀花力路为中轴。曼谷唐人街有很多餐馆，经营的燕窝、鱼翅很便宜，不妨去尝一下。这里夜间会变成海鲜夜排档，价廉物美。',0,7839,131,12,3,'','','','',99),(81,'National Museum Bangkok','泰國國家博物館','','4 Th Na Phra That','轮渡至Tha Chang(N9)码头，在大皇宫附近，步行可至。','周一、周二不开放，周三至周日','9:00-15:30','','泰国国内最大的博物馆','200Baht','200泰铢','','',0,0,'In the former grounds of the 18th Century Wang Na Palace, The Bangkok National Museum houses the largest collection of Thai art and artifacts in the country. It\'s definitely worth a visit, especially if visiting nearby Wat Phra Kaew or the Grand Palace.\n\nOpened by King Rama V to exhibit the antiques and gifts bestowed to him by his father, it once held a reputation for being an ill-organised gathering of dusty relics. That has now changed, with exhibits now arranged into three areas consistent with Thai history, and good English-language descriptions available. ','泰国国内最大的博物馆，陈列着从史前时代到近代的各种艺术品，面积巨大，展品丰富。',0,5803,122,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/National%20Museum%20Bangkok/Thumb%20National%20Museum%20Bangkok.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/National%20Museum%20Bangkok/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/National%20Museum%20Bangkok/National%20Museum%20Bangkok.mp3',99),(82,'Siam Ocean World','暹羅海洋世界','','B1-B2 fl. Siam Paragon, 991 Rama 1 Rd. Pathumwan Bangkok 10330','搭空铁BTS到SIAM站，走到SIAM PARAGON百貨公司的B1樓 \n','','10:00-21:00','','全东南亚最大的水族馆','250Baht 150Baht','成人票价统一250B，小孩票价150B','','',0,0,'SEA LIFE Bangkok Ocean World (formerly Siam Ocean World) is located two storeys underneath the glitzy Siam Paragon shopping mall. It is an aquatic wonderland the size of three Olympic swimming pools full of interesting animals from the ocean deep. This underground aquarium, one of the largest in Southeast Asia, will dazzle you with innovative world-class exhibits and over 30,000 curious looking creatures from various depths and aquatic regions across the globe.','全东南亚最大的水族馆，面积达一万平方米。水族馆分为深海区和浅水区、南北雨极和热带雨林等多个区域，管内更有室内观光鱼池。',0,9567,57,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Siam%20Ocean%20World/Thumb%20Siam%20Ocean%20World.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Siam%20Ocean%20World/vtour/tour.html','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/video_utovr/video/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Siam%20Ocean%20World/Siam%20Ocean%20World.html','',99),(83,'Tha Maharaj Market','马哈拉文青市场','','Trok Mahathat, Maharaj Road, Phranakorn','','','7:00-11:00','Tha Maharaj Night Bike Market','一个露天聚会场所','','','','http://www.thamaharaj.com/what_on_detail.php?nid=1',0,0,'Tha Maharaj, 100plus and Ideo O2 by Ananda present The 4th \"Tha Maharaj Night Bike Market\".\nThis time, we have organised many fun and exciting activities for all cyclists!','玛哈拉码头文青市集由河畔旧店屋群修葺而成，共包含了七个建筑。目前这个区域已经复苏成为了一个露天聚会场所。这里有着丰富的业态规划，各式餐厅及商店无不激励着顾客来此欣赏河景，并在滨江大道和社区花园散步流连。人们可以花整个下午的时间在这个院落里放松休憩——也许可以在上午晚些的时候在其中的一间咖啡馆喝杯咖啡，接着到艺术书店逛一逛，最后在河边彻底放松之前再享用一份日式拉面作为午餐',0,6079,58,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Tha%20Maharaj%20Market/Thumb%20Tha%20Maharaj%20Market.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Tha%20Maharaj%20Market/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Tha%20Maharaj%20Market/Tha%20Maharaj%20Market.mp3',99),(84,'Ananta Samakhom Throne Hall','皇室博物馆','','U-Thong Nai Road, Bangkok, Thailand','Taxi','','9:30-16:00 Tues-Sun ','Bangkok Palaces and Mansions','很漂亮的博物馆，整座建筑都很壮观','50Baht','','','',0,0,'The centerpiece of Bangkok\'s own Champs Elysees, this impressive two-storey white marble palace sits at the end of Dusit\'s long, wide Royal Plaza, a leafy ceremonial boulevard that\'s often the focus of regal pomp and ceremony during royal celebrations.\n\nOrdered by King Rama V in 1907 and finished in the reign of King Rama VI, its neo-classical Renaissance architecture - particularly its central dome - dominate the scene just as Italian architects Mario Tamango and Annibale Rigotti intended. Following the 1932 coup it housed the first Thai parliament, but today its ornate interiors serve as a prestigious locale in which to court visiting dignitaries, hold state council meetings and royal occasions.','很漂亮的博物馆，整座建筑都很壮观。博物馆的展出品都是艺术品。注意到这里有着装要求，而且禁止拍照录像。所有的相关设备都要放在储物柜里，博物馆为所有游客提供音频导游。',0,5897,83,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Ananta%20Samakhom%20Throne%20Hall/Thumb%20Ananta%20Samakhom%20Throne%20Hall.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Ananta%20Samakhom%20Throne%20Hall/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Ananta%20Samakhom%20Throne%20Hall/Ananta%20Samakhom%20Throne%20Hall.mp3',99),(85,'Siam Paragon','暹罗百丽宫','','Siam Paragon, 991/1 1st Floor, Rama I Road, Bangkok 10330','','','','Siam Paragon Italian Grand Weekend. Vivere all\'Italiana – Smooth Lifestyle, Urban Glamour, Live Music.','东南亚最大的购物中心','','','','www.siamparagon.co.th',0,0,'Siam Paragon Italian Grand Weekend. Vivere all\'Italiana – Smooth Lifestyle, Urban Glamour, Live Music.','堪称东南亚最大的购物中心——Siam Paragon，斥资150亿泰铢建立的豪华顶级大卖场，占地50万平方公尺，共有250间商店，要整个逛完得要花上数天时间；除了卖场主体以外、可停4,000部车的大型停车场，和宽广的户外广场，入夜后可观赏水舞。 这家姿态高调、城镇规模的商场把自己比作一颗多面体宝石，它位于一个六层楼的中庭大厅背后，大厅里面装饰着垂直花园和流水瀑布。这里甚至不像一个购物中心，倒像一座城市花园。 商场有十层楼，包括各种商店及餐馆共270多间，以及一家有15间放映室的电影院，亦拥有一个号称东南亚最大的名叫曼谷海洋世界的水族馆及一个展览厅和泰国艺术画廊和歌剧院。还拥有大型保龄球场，卡拉OK。五层是泰国最大的英文书店Kinokuniya。',0,8254,85,12,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Siam%20Paragon/Thumb%20Siam%20Paragon.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Siam%20Paragon/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Bangkok/Sights/Siam%20Paragon/Siam%20Paragon.mp3',99),(86,'Floating Market','水上市场','','update later...','','','','Floating market TH(talātnām) EN(floating market) FR(marché flottant) is a marketplace where goods are sold from boats.','在这里，你可以划着船挑选你喜欢的蔬菜水果，很是有趣。','','','','http://www.bangkok.com/magazine/5-floating-markets',0,0,'Floating market TH(talātnām) EN(floating market) FR(marché flottant) is a marketplace where goods are sold from boats. The floating markets are well supported locally and mainly serve as tourist attractions.One of their purposes is to allow domestic visitors and international tourists to be able to experience the culture of riverside shopping.','水上市场一般都是生意兴隆，格外繁荣。每天早上六点过后，就有很多郊区的农户或者商人带着各色各样的热带水果和蔬菜划船来到水上市场，准备交易。由于船只众多，所以场面甚是热闹。在这里，你可以划着船挑选你喜欢的蔬菜水果，很是有趣。泰国政府为了保护本国特有文化，也为了吸引国外游客，在嫩沙多河上建立了集市——丹嫩沙水上市场。这个水上市场不仅历史悠久，更是商业繁荣，是泰国国内最有名的水上市场。沿岸树木枝繁叶茂，水上磷光碎影，一条条载有新鲜果蔬的商船在河中穿梭来去。有的穿上还有小型火炉，现场制作汤面、炸香蕉等各色小吃，真是让游客垂涎三尺。船上的小贩都是用长竹竿把蔬菜和水果递给沿岸的人，交易过程很是奇特。',0,6573,132,20,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1497058603/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Ayuthaya/Sights/Floating%20Market/Thumb%20Floating%20Market.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Ayuthaya/Sights/Floating%20Market/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Ayuthaya/Sights/Floating%20Market/Floating%20Market.mp3',99),(87,'Wat Suwan Dararam','苏旺达寺','','Moo 2 | Ho Rattanachai Subdistrcit, Ayutthaya 13000, Thailand','','','','It\'s very nice and beautiful temple.','此外正殿内还有由拉玛七世下令绘制的壁画，很值得一看。','','','','',9,0,'Wat Suwan Dararam located outside Ayutthaya Historical Park. It\'s a very beautiful, clean, peaceful, old and interesting royal temple.','这座寺庙是曼谷王朝的初代王拉玛一世的父亲建立的寺院，后来拉玛一世将这里进行了重修，并将其定为王室寺院。主殿中美轮美奂的壁画绘于150多年前，描绘的是佛陀的生活。寺庙中的圣职受任大殿一般是不对外开放的，此外正殿内还有由拉玛七世下令绘制的壁画很值得一看。该壁画展现的是纳莱颂恩王统治时期的景象和他一生的伟绩，其中有一幅壁画反映的是爆发于1593年的大城与缅甸之间的依萨瑞战役。',0,5106,53,20,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Ayuthaya/Sights/Wat%20Suwan%20Dararam/Thumb%20Wat%20Suwan%20Dararam.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Ayuthaya/Sights/Wat%20Suwan%20Dararam/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Ayuthaya/Sights/Wat%20Suwan%20Dararam/Wat%20Suwan%20Dararam.mp3',99),(88,'Sukhothai National Historic Park','素可泰国家历史公园','','Mueang Kao, Mueang Sukhothai District','','','','','这是一处被列入世界文化遗产的遗址群，也是泰国最有名的世界遗产之一。','100B','','66 2 168 7734','',0,0,'The Sukhothai Historical Park covers the ruins of Sukhothai, literally \"Dawn of Happiness\", capital of the Sukhothai Kingdom in the 13th and 14th centuries,[1] in what is now Northern Thailand. It is located near the modern city of Sukhothai, capital of the province with the same name.The city walls form a rectangle about 2 km east-west by 1.6 km north-south. There are 193 ruins on 70 square kilometers of land.[1] There is a gate in the centre of each wall. Inside are the remains of the royal palace and twenty-six temples, the largest being Wat Mahathat. The park is maintained by the Fine Arts Department of Thailand with help from UNESCO, which has declared it a World Heritage Site. Each year, the park welcomes thousands of visitors who marvel at the ancient Buddha figures, palace building','素可泰历史公园，位于泰国中部，是泰国文化的集中地，公园内有佛家建筑数处，是泰国重要的旅游区之一。',0,9829,111,13,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Sukhothai/Sights/Sukhothai%20National%20Historic%20Park/Thumb%20Sukhothai%20National%20Historic%20Park.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Sukhothai/Sights/Sukhothai%20National%20Historic%20Park/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502870507/Thailand/Sukhothai/Sights/Sukhothai%20National%20Historic%20Park/Sukhothai%20National%20Historic%20Park.mp3',99),(89,'Jinbaran Beach','金巴兰海滩','','Jimbaran Bay Jimbaran Kuta Selatan Bali, 80361','','','',' Here is the Best of Everything.','酒店别墅就如真正的巴厘岛村舍，像一首首抒情小诗。','','','','http://www.bali-indonesia.com/jimbaran/',0,0,'Jimbaran beach and the famous Jimbaran Bay are located on Bali\'s southwestern coast of the narrow isthmus connecting the Bali mainland and the Bukit Peninsula. The beach and the bay of Jimbaran offers small secluded areas, where tranquility and peace are the perfect antidote to a stressful world.The land gently slopes away from the beach revealing exclusive celebrity haunts hidden under a canopy of leafy tropical forests. Jimbaran Beach is also known as the home of luxury hotels, the likes of the Four Seasons Resort at Jimbaran Bay and the InterContinental Bali Resort & Spa. Find out about all the great Jimbaran hotels, dining spots, attractions and nightlife right here.','海边微风徐徐，在凉亭间奢享露天水疗服务，在美如画卷的云水间，让身心彻底焕然一新；管家随叫随到，酒店吃的很棒！性价比很好，地理位置优越，到哪里都很方便，周边烧烤很赞，还可体验浪漫贴心的双人按摩，共同安享静谧悠然的甜蜜时光。',0,9750,149,21,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/South/Sights/Jinbaran%20Beach/Thumb%20Jinbaran%20Beach.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Sights/Jinbaran%20Beach/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Sights/Jinbaran%20Beach/Jinbaran%20Beach.mp3',99),(90,'Pura Luhur Uluwatu','情人崖','','Temple, Other Great Outdoors, and Scenic Lookout Uluwatu','','','','Uluwatu tour is started in the afternoon time and it will spend about 5 - 6 hours to explore the places of interest that are located especially in the southern part of Bali, Indonesia.','绝对是巴厘岛最值得推荐的景点','','','','http://www.bali-indonesia.com/attractions/uluwatu-',0,0,'Uluwatu Temple Tour is one among the Bali half-day tour packages to visit the famous and the beautiful Balinese Hindu sea temple that is located on the cliff on the southern coast of Bali island with the fabulous sunset background.','Pura Luhur Uluwatu，乌鲁瓦图断崖，也被称为情人崖。一望无际南印度洋的海平面，蓝绿色的海浪冲击拍打着断崖，美到令人惊叹！绝对是巴厘岛最值得推荐的景点.',0,9311,69,21,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/South/Sights/Pura%20Luhur%20Uluwatu/Thumb%20Pura%20Luhur%20Uluwatu.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Sights/Pura%20Luhur%20Uluwatu/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Sights/Pura%20Luhur%20Uluwatu/Pura%20Luhur%20Uluwatu.mp3',99),(91,'PadangPadang Beach','PadangPadang海滩','','Labuan Sait, Pecatu village, Jimbaran','','','','','在这里尽情的享受日光浴吧','','','','',0,0,'Padang Padang Beach, locally referred to as Pantai Labuan Sait, is one of Bali’s most famous surf spots, located on the north-western coast of the island’s Bukit Peninsula, and just a kilometre southwest of the Anantara Bali Uluwatu. This beach features an exotic setting; a simply stunning one hundred meter-long stretch of sand that is accessible down a flight of stairs through a unique hollow rock entrance. The surf has a steady set of barrels during good weather, attracting wave riders from around the world.','',0,7285,137,21,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/South/Sights/PadangPadang%20Beach/Thumb%20PadangPadang%20Beach.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Sights/PadangPadang%20Beach/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Sights/PadangPadang%20Beach/PadangPadang%20Beach.mp3',99),(92,'Dreamland Beach','梦幻海滩','','Bukit Peninsula, Kuta, Indonesia','','','','This beach is beautiful and the views around the coast are spectacular.','一个绝美的梦幻海滩','','','','',0,0,'This beach is beautiful and the views around the coast are spectacular.The surf can be epic and the shore-break fun to mess around in.Turn your dream vacation into reality by embarking on a journey to Camiguin, the \"\"island born of fire,\"\" and revel in the comfortable and convenient accommodations offered only at Dreamland Beach Resort.','Dreamland Beach——梦幻海滩是一个绝美的海滩，位于乌鲁瓦图情人崖附近，海滩上的沙子洁白、柔软、细腻，踩上去十分的舒适，海天一色，感觉静谧自在，非常适合躺在海滩上晒日光浴。150米长的新月形白沙滩，澎湃的海浪拍打着海岸，还有一个个小摊位，可以在你欣赏日落时，提供啤酒。由于梦幻海滩风高浪急，不适合游泳和泛舟，但却是晒太阳与冲浪的好地方，想要在短时间内晒成令人向往的古铜色极其的容易，如果不想被晒黑的话，就可租一个海滩椅，静静的躺在海滩椅上观赏辽阔的大海和形形色色的游人，到了傍晚的时候还可以欣赏梦幻般的落日美景，震撼无比。',0,5509,136,21,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/South/Sights/Dreamland%20Beach/Thumb%20Dreamland%20Beach.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Sights/Dreamland%20Beach/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Sights/Dreamland%20Beach/Dreamland%20Beach.mp3',99),(93,'Keramas Beach','Keramas黑沙滩','','update later...','','','','Keramas beach is the happening beach destination in Bali today especially for surfers.','库塔海滩的海浪成为全球冲浪爱好者聚集的地','','','','http://www.keramasbeach.com/',0,0,'Keramas beach is the happening beach destination in Bali today especially for surfers. There are many surfers coming to this beach as this beach has the fantastic waves suitable for pro surfers and has been the spot for many major events such as recently ASP 2013 and also Oakley World Pro Junior 2012.','众多专业的冲浪比赛都在这个黑沙滩举行，现在还有一家新的海滩俱乐部在这里，有时还会举办夜间冲浪活动。 除了冲浪者外，现在这里也受众多游客的欢迎，在这里住宿，因为这里是发现巴厘岛东部的一个好地点。\n\n',0,9686,117,21,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/South/Sights/Keramas%20Beach/Thumb%20Keramas%20Beach.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Sights/Keramas%20Beach/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/South/Sights/Keramas%20Beach/Keramas%20Beach.mp3',99),(94,'Ubud Traditional Market','乌布传统市场','','Jl. Raya and Monkey Forest Road, Ubud 80571, Indonesia','','','','Bali Traditional Public Market','一处更有巴厘本色的市场','','','','',0,0,'Street Food at the Ubud, Bali Traditional Public Market. Delicious street food, eggs, noodles, rice, and soup can be purchased at the traditional public market in the village of Ubud, Bali, Indonesia.','乌布传统市场是一处更有巴厘本色的市场。如果你是想买一些最能代表巴厘岛的特产，当然是要来乌布传统市场了。这市场真是大有名气，各大旅行图册上都会拿出一定的版面来介绍它。《Eat pray love》里面，男女主角相识后携手惬意相逛的，也正是此地。',0,7903,130,23,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/Ubud/Sights/Ubud%20Traditional%20Market/Thumb%20Ubud%20Traditional%20Market.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Ubud/Sights/Ubud%20Traditional%20Market/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Ubud/Sights/Ubud%20Traditional%20Market/Ubud%20Traditional%20Market.mp3',99),(95,'Tirta Empul Temple','圣泉寺','','Banjar Tampak Siring, Tampaksiring, Bali, Indonesia','圣泉寺在巴厘岛中北部，距离乌布约40分钟车程。','','','famous for its holy spring water','巴厘岛上六大著名庙宇之一','','','','',0,0,'Tirta Empul temple is a Hindu Balinese water temple located near the town of Tampaksiring, Bali, Indonesia. The temple compound consists of a petirtaan or bathing structure, famous for its holy spring water, where Balinese Hindus go to for ritual purification. The temple pond has a spring which gives out fresh water regularly, which Balinese Hindus consider to be holy or amritha.Tirta Empul means Holy Spring in Balinese.','圣泉寺是“千寺之岛”巴厘岛上六大著名庙宇之一，依地下泉眼而建，因此得名。石头圣龛上早是苔痕斑斑，而泉涌依然如当年。圣泉寺建筑规模宏大完整，从此处可以看到巴厘岛庙宇的所有特点。 据说远古时有巫师在水中下毒毒害村民，大神因陀罗以矛刺地涌出泉水，解救了村民。这就是圣泉的来历。 圣泉寺中有十多个出水口，历经千年依然清澈。每个出水口的功效都不同，有的可以消灾解祸，有的可以驱逐病痛，有的可以洗涤心灵，附近居民每天早、中、晚三次来此沐浴祈福。 前来沐浴的游客着装需庄重。',0,7454,147,23,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/Ubud/Sights/Tirta%20Empul%20Temple/Thumb%20Tirta%20Empul%20Temple.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Ubud/Sights/Tirta%20Empul%20Temple/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Ubud/Sights/Tirta%20Empul%20Temple/Tirta%20Empul%20Temple.mp3',99),(96,'Monkey Forest','圣猴森林公园','','Jalan Monkey Forest, Padangtegal, Ubud Bali,80571 Indonesia','','','8：30--18：00','Pura Puncak Penulisan','来这里和猴子亲密接触吧~','','','','',0,0,'Ubud Monkey Forest, also known as the Sacred Monkey Forest of Padangtegal, is one of Ubud’s most popular attractions; a natural forest sanctuary that is home to a horde of grey long-tailed macaques. The site is well preserved thanks to a community-based management program. The forest is also conveniently positioned near Ubud Town Centre, and within easy walking distance from guesthouses and resorts along the main roads of Jalan Hanoman and the namesake Jalan Monkey Forest.','圣猴森林公园是一个自然保护区。园内林木葱郁茂盛，林中生活着巴厘岛特有巴厘猕猴，被视为圣猴。这些猴子在这里无忧无虑的生活，还有专人喂食。园内还种植着大概115种不同种类的植物，是乌布地区的热门景点之一。',0,3561,97,23,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/Ubud/Sights/Monkey%20Forest/Thumb%20Monkey%20Forest.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Ubud/Sights/Monkey%20Forest/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Ubud/Sights/Monkey%20Forest/Monkey%20Forest.mp3',99),(97,'Pura Puncak Penulisan','Pura Puncak Penulisan','','update later...','','','','','巴厘岛最古老的寺庙之一，建筑非常具有年代感','','','','',0,0,'','Pura Puncak Penulisan位于巴杜尔火山附近，是巴厘岛最古老的寺庙之一。比起其他寺庙，这里的游客相对最少，是非常清净和有特色的一个寺庙。另外，Pura Puncak Penulisan沿山而建，寺庙位于山顶，需要攀登300多级台阶，健身力度刚好。爬上去后还可以远眺巴杜尔火山及巴杜尔湖，视野绝佳，景观还是不错的。',0,6442,95,23,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/Ubud/Sights/Pura%20Puncak%20Penulisan/Thumb%20Pura%20Puncak%20Penulisan.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Ubud/Sights/Pura%20Puncak%20Penulisan/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Ubud/Sights/Pura%20Puncak%20Penulisan/Pura%20Puncak%20Penulisan.mp3',99),(98,'Tegallalang Rice Terrace','Tegallalang Rice Terrace','','update later...','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'It is impossible to visit Bali and not come across numerous temples and rice field terrace.Rice, in addition to being a staple food Balinese, is part of the local culture. Cultivation is done according to ancient rituals, inextricably linked to religion and philosophy site.The planting and irrigation system of rice field terrace is known as Subak. The land is cropped out into layers or terraces (rice terrace) for the water begins to be accumulated in certain spots, but it also flow naturally from the hilltop to the lower area.The idea is to cultivate rice, creating a harmonious relationship with the gods, with the ground and with other people. This, indeed, is the basis of all Balinese philosophy – Tri Hita Karana','',0,4528,133,23,4,'','','','',99),(99,'Lake Beratan','贝拉坦湖','','Jl. Bedugul, Candi Kuning, Tabanan 80345, Indonesia','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'Lake Beratan is a beautiful lake that is home to the water temple Ulun Danu Bratan, with the majestic Bedugul mountains in the backdrop. Located at a height of 1200 meters above sea level, the pleasant climate simply enhances the visual treat that the temple complex and its surroundings present.','布拉坦湖和百度库好像是合二为一的景点。这里相对人少，很巴厘岛风情，日落时分，风景很美，寺庙很棒。',0,7316,129,25,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/Middle&North/Sights/Lake%20Beratan/Thumb%20Lake%20Beratan.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Middle&North/Sights/Lake%20Beratan/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Middle&North/Sights/Lake%20Beratan/Lake%20Beratan.mp3',99),(100,'Lake Batur','巴图胡','','update later...','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'Bali as primary destination in the world, offers largely on its tropical destinations with white sand beaches, blue sky, and cultural attractions. Beach resort and hotel have been developed. Many tourist destinations that worth to visit whenever you want, Not only famous for beaches, Bali also has natural mountains are very beautiful and are well-known to foreign. One of them is the nature of mountains in Kintamani Bangli. The natural beauty of Kintamani which is supported by the beauty Batur Lake are very wonderful and unspoiled.','由于火山口积水,形成了巴厘岛境内最大的湖泊巴杜尔湖,而该湖相传是湖水女神 Dewu Ulun Danu 的栖息之地。因此虽然不是排名第一的火山,但巴杜尔火山和巴杜尔湖(Lake Batur)却是巴厘岛的标志之一。',0,5994,99,25,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/Middle&North/Sights/Lake%20Batur/Thumb%20Lake%20Batur.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Middle&North/Sights/Lake%20Batur/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Middle&North/Sights/Lake%20Batur/Lake%20Batur.mp3',99),(101,'Lake Buyan','双子湖','','update later...','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'','布拉坦火山曾是个很大的火山. 火山大约在二万多年前大爆发, 大火山口塌陷后, 形成了一个长约11公里, 宽约6公里的破火山口. 雨水泉水经过万年的累集汇聚, 山谷内出现了三个美丽的火山湖.， 这就是有名的山中湖(布拉坦湖)和双子湖布扬(Buyan)湖和坦布林根(Tamblingan)湖',0,5024,57,25,4,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Thumb%20point%20Bali/Middle&North/Sights/Lake%20Buyan/Thumb%20Lake%20Buyan.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Middle&North/Sights/Lake%20Buyan/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502793186/Bali/Middle&North/Sights/Lake%20Buyan/Lake%20Buyan.mp3',99),(102,'Beach Svjetionik','Beach Svjetionik','','Verudela, Pula, Croatia','Walk, Bike, Vehicle, Off road vehicle, by boat','','0:00-24:00','Perfect for families with small children who can with no worries have fun in the shallow water','周末全家出游娱乐的完美选择','0','0','','',0,0,'Beautiful sunrise in the early morning hours, the sound of the sea breeze, the scent of nature and with that sense of peace and tranquility just can not leave you indifferent. The only thing you can do is dream into reality and enjoy all the charms and comforts offered by Beach Svjetionik.The beach is perfect for families with small children who can with no worries have fun in the shallow water. Beach Svjetionik is an ideal place for those who want to enjoy the beautiful nature, clean water and peace away from the stress and crowds.','Beach Svjetionik是享受最纯真的大自然的完美度假去处。清澈见底的海水和宁静的环境让你远离城市钢筋水泥的烦恼的喧嚣。早晨更有极佳的日出美景，伴随着悦耳迷人的海浪轻轻拍打海滩的声音，顿时让人置身于梦境一般的天堂。',0,4143,119,29,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Istria/Sights/Beach%20Svjetionik/Thumb%20Beach%20Svjetionik.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Beach%20Svjetionik/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Beach%20Svjetionik/Beach%20Svjetionik.mp3',99),(103,'Bol','伯埃尔','','Bol, Brac Island 21420, Croatia','','','0:00-24:00','Bol has many beautiful beaches. Bol is the oldest coastal settlement on Bra?','Bol尖角海滩是亚得里亚海的最大和最美丽的景点。像一个小舌头，它延伸近半公里到清澈的蓝色大海。','','','','http://www.bol.hr/',0,0,'Gathered around a compact marina, the old town of Bol is an attractive place made up of small stone houses and winding streets dotted with pink and purple geraniums. While short on actual sights, many of the buildings are marked with interpretative panels explaining their cultural and historical significance.To the west from Bol lies the beach Zlatni rat (Golden Horn) one of the largest and most beautiful attractions of the Adriatic. Like a small tongue it extends nearly half a kilometre into the clear blue sea.The town\'s major attraction is Zlatni Rat, the seductive pebbly beach that ‘leaks’ into the Adriatic and draws crowds of swimmers and windsurfers in summer. A long coastal promenade, lined with pine trees and gardens, connects the beach with the old town. Bol is a buzzing place in s','博尔有许多美丽的海滩。从Bol位于西边，坐落在亚得里亚海最大和最美丽的景点之一的Zlatni大海（金角）。像一个小舌头，它延伸近半公里到清澈的蓝色大海。',0,9630,86,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Bol/Thumb%20Bol.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Bol/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Bol/Bol.mp3',99),(104,'Krka National Park','克尔卡国家公园','','Lozovac, Croatia','从希贝尼克小镇码头坐轮渡','','','It\'s a magical place of waterfalls and gorges, with the river gushing through a karstic canyon 200m deep','瀑布与峡谷的碰撞','Jan-Mar/Nov-Dec 30,00kn;Apr-Jun/Sep-Oct 110,00kn; ','一月-五月/十一月-十二月 30,00库钠；四月-六月/九月-十月 110,00库钠；七月-八月 1','385(0)22 201 777','http://www.np-krka.hr/en/',0,0,'Krka National Park lies within ?ibenik-Knin County, and covers a total area of 109 km2 of the loveliest sections of the Krka River, and the lower course of the ?ikola River. Including the submerged part of the river at the mouth, the Krka River is 72.5 km long, making it the 22nd longest river in Croatia. It springs in the foothills of the Dinara mountain range, 2.5 km northeast of Knin. With its seven waterfalls and a total drop in altitude of 242 m, the Krka is a natural and karst phenomenon. The travertine waterfalls of the Krka River are the fundamental phenomenon of this river.','克尔卡国家公园又被称作卡尔卡或科卡国家公园。我们按克罗地亚官方旅游组织的称谓将其称作克尔卡国家公园。国家公园面积109平方公里。克尔卡盘地与克罗地亚喀斯特地区中间形成一条深近200米的峡谷，美丽的克尔卡河从其间流过，通过一层层石灰岩切割形成的钙化坝台阶层层下落，成为一道道美丽壮观的瀑布。',0,4728,123,28,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Krka%20National%20Park/Thumb%20Krka%20National%20Park.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Krka%20National%20Park/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Krka%20National%20Park/Krka%20National%20Park.mp3',99),(105,'Rab Town','拉布老城区','','Rab, Croatia','','','0:00-24:00','Rab Town is among the northern Adriatic’s most spectacular sights','拉布岛是克罗地亚的一个岛屿，位于亚德里亚海北部，风景秀丽、气候宜人，是个不可多得的度假胜地。','0','0','','http://www.rab-visit.com/',0,0,'Rab Town is among the northern Adriatic’s most spectacular sights. Crowded on to a narrow peninsula, its four instantly recognisable bell towers rise like exclamation marks from a red-roofed huddle of stone buildings. A maze of streets leads to the upper town, where there are ancient churches and dramatic lookout points. It’s quite a scene, the glinting azure waters of Rab’s pocket-sized harbour set against the island’s backbone of hills that shelter the bay from cool bura (cold northeasterly) winds. Once you’ve soaked up the town vibe, there are excursion and taxi boats waiting to whisk you off to lovely beaches scattered around the island.','拉布岛是克罗地亚的一个岛屿，位于亚德里亚海北部，风景秀丽、气候宜人，是个不可多得的度假胜地。岛上有一座十三世纪的罗马风格大教堂，其独立钟楼被认为是亚得里亚海沿岸罗马式建筑最杰出的代表，它与另外三座钟楼依次成排，坐落在山脊之上，俯瞰整个岛屿，当地有几幢威尼斯贵族所建的历史上有名的宅邸，岛上6个小村以渔业、农业、旅游业及成衣业为生，以所产水果和葡萄酒闻名。',0,5734,101,30,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Rab%20Town/Thumb%20Rab%20Town.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Rab%20Town/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Rab%20Town/Rab%20Town.mp3',99),(106,'Dubrovnik Old Town','杜布罗夫尼克古城','','Dubrovnik, Croatia','','','0:00-24:00','Pearl of the Adriatic','亚得里亚海的明珠','0','0','385(0)91 560 3810','https://www.dubrovnikcity.com/dubrovnik/old_town.h',0,0,'The \'Pearl of the Adriatic\', situated on the Dalmatian coast, became an important Mediterranean sea power from the 13th century onwards. Although severely damaged by an earthquake in 1667, Dubrovnik managed to preserve its beautiful Gothic, Renaissance and Baroque churches, monasteries, palaces and fountains. Damaged again in the 1990s by armed conflict, it is now the focus of a major restoration programme co-ordinated by UNESCO.','位于克罗地亚南部的杜布罗夫尼克建于公元7世纪。杜布罗夫尼克依山傍海，风景优美，是欧洲中世纪建筑保存比较完好的一座城市，有“城市博物馆”的美称，1979年被联合国教科文组织列入世界文化遗产名录。城区分为旧城和新城两部分，旧城至今仍保存着14至16世纪建的古城堡，分别体现罗马式、哥特式、文艺复兴式和巴洛克式等不同的建筑风格。这里已经成为欧洲乃至全球游客理想的旅游和疗养胜地。',0,4499,92,26,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Dubrovnik%20Old%20Town/Thumb%20Dubrovnik%20Old%20Town.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Dubrovnik%20Old%20Town/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Dubrovnik%20Old%20Town/Dubrovnik%20Old%20Town.mp3',99),(107,'Split Fish Market','斯普利特鱼市','','Osmih mediteranskih igara 8,21000, Split','','Opened daily','6.30 am till 2 pm','The most popular fish are picarels, sprats, mackerels, sardines and anchovies','丰盛的海鲜，实惠的价格','0','0','','',0,0,'From around 12 a clock they reduce the prices on almost half, so it there is any fish left you can make a bargain at that time of the day.\nThe most popular fish are picarels, sprats, mackerels, sardines and anchovies.\nAt the fish market (inside the market building) you find a man with a sharp knife, for about 10 kuna he will clean your fish and cut it into fillets if you don’t like the hassle your selves.','从大约中午12点钟起，所有鱼的价格打折将近快一半，所以这一天剩下的鱼就可以在每天的中午12点后讨价还价。\n大部分最受欢迎的鱼是野餐，鲱鱼，鲭鱼，沙丁鱼和凤尾鱼。',0,9284,106,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Split%20Fish%20Market/Thumb%20Split%20Fish%20Market.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Split%20Fish%20Market/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Split%20Fish%20Market/Split%20Fish%20Market.mp3',99),(108,'The Greeting to the Sun','霓虹夜舞','','The Greeting to the Sun, Zadar 23000, Croatia','步行即可到达','Opened daily','All','Stunning sunset','绚丽的落日','0','0','','http://www.zadar.travel/en/city-guide/attractions/',0,0,'The Greeting to the Sun consists of three hundred multi-layered glass plates placed on the same level with the stone-paved waterfront in the shape of a 22-meter diameter circle. Under the glass conduction plates there are photo-voltage solar modules through which symbolic communication with nature is made, with the aim to communicate with light, just like the Sea Organs do with sound.','Greeting to the Sun( 夜舞霓虹 )是建筑师Nikola Basic的设计。圆圆的玻璃面倒映着蓝天和白云，它的直径有22米，内部嵌有300块太阳能电池板。白天的时候依靠太阳能储存能量，夜晚来临时霓虹便开始舞动，似真似幻。',0,8930,107,28,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/The%20Greeting%20to%20the%20Sun/Thumb%20The%20Greeting%20to%20the%20Sun.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/The%20Greeting%20to%20the%20Sun/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/The%20Greeting%20to%20the%20Sun/The%20Greeting%20to%20the%20Sun.mp3',99),(109,'Hawaiian Beach Verudela','Hawaiian Beach Verudela','','Verudela 23, 52100, Pula,Croatia','','','0:00-24:00','One of the most popular beaches in Pula, especially among younger population','普拉岛最火的海滩','0','0','','http://www.pulacroatia.net/item/hawaiian-cove-beac',0,0,'Hawaii Beach is one of the most popular beaches in Pula, especially among younger population. Name Hawaii was given to it probably because of the high waves during Jugo in the cove, which reminds of Hawaii.Hawaiian Cove Beach is located in Principina Cove at Verudela Peninsula in Pula. Central part of the beach is pebble with rocky boulders. Sides are rocky and medium height, suitable for water jumps. Entrance is very soft, suitable for families with kids.','夏威夷海滩是普拉最受欢迎的海滩之一，特别是年轻人口中。夏威夷海湾位于普拉岛的Verudela半岛的Principina湾。海滩的中央部分是石块与岩石巨石。侧面是中等高度的岩石，适合跳水。适合带孩子的家庭入住。',0,6799,67,29,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Istria/Sights/Hawaiian%20Beach%20Verudela/Thumb%20Hawaiian%20Beach%20Verudela.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Hawaiian%20Beach%20Verudela/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Hawaiian%20Beach%20Verudela/Hawaiian%20Beach%20Verudela.mp3',99),(110,'Kanjon Verudela','Kanjon Verudela','','Verudela 23, 52100, Pula, Croatia','','','0:00-24:00','','绝佳跳崖地','0','0','','',0,0,'','',0,4206,65,29,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Istria/Sights/Kanjon%20Verudela/Thumb%20Kanjon%20Verudela.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Kanjon%20Verudela/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Kanjon%20Verudela/Kanjon%20Verudela.mp3',99),(111,'Lokrum','洛克鲁姆岛','','?iroka ul. 4, 20000, Dubrovnik,Croatia','老城区海港坐船上岛','','0:00-24:00','Nudist beach and swimming pool','裸晒悬崖和跳潭','0','0','385 20 413 345','https://www.gastronaut.hr/restorani/dubrovacko-ner',0,0,'Lush Lokrum is a beautiful, forested island full of holm oaks, black ash, pines and olive trees, and an ideal escape from urban Dubrovnik. It\'s a popular swimming spot, although the beaches are rocky. To reach the nudist beach, head left from the ferry and follow the signs marked FKK; the rocks at the far end are Dubrovnik\'s de facto gay beach. Also popular is the small saltwater lake known as the Dead Sea.','Lokrum岛位于亚得里亚海中，是世界十大最绚丽悬崖之一，是热门的旅游胜地，主要以有很多的半野生孔雀著名，Lokrum岛的裸体海滩吸引了来自欧洲各地的游客。悬崖下面的水比较深，因此对悬崖跳水者是比较安全的。',0,4635,74,26,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Lokrum/Thumb%20Lokrum.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Lokrum/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Lokrum/Lokrum.mp3',99),(112,'Fort Lovrijenac','Lovrijenac堡垒','','Ul. od Tabakarije 29, 20000, Dubrovnik, Croatia','','Opened daily','9:00-18:00,Apr-Oct;1','Game of Thrones','权利的游戏-君临城','','','385 20 638 800','',0,0,'Fort Lovrijenac or St. Lawrence Fortress, often called \"Dubrovnik\'s Gibraltar\", is a fortress and theater outside the western wall of the city of Dubrovnik in Croatia, 37 metres (121 ft) above sea level.Famous for its plays and importance in resisting Venetian rule, it overshadows the two entrances to the city, from the sea and by land. Early in the 11th century the Venetians attempted to build a fort on the same spot where Fort Lovrijenac currently stands. If they had succeeded, they would have kept Dubrovnik under their power, but the people of the city beat them to it. The \"Chronicles of Ragusa\" reveal how the fort was built within just three months time and from then on constantly reconstructed. When the Venetian ships arrived, full of materials for the construction of the fort, they w','Lovrijenac堡垒矗立在老城西面城门外，高出海面37米，有如卫士一般从海陆两方面守卫着杜布罗夫尼克的两个入口。11世纪威尼斯人曾经试图在相同位置建造自己的堡垒，这样便可将杜布罗夫尼克控制在自己的手中，但是杜布罗夫尼克的子民决定捍卫自己的领土。Ragusa编年史详细的记载了当地人民仅用三个月的时间便建起了堡垒，并在之后的时间不短进行加固，当威尼斯人携带建造堡垒所需的全部材料乘船抵达的时候，只好无功而返。Lovrijenac堡垒朝向海面的城墙有12米厚，面向城内的部分只有60厘米。堡垒的城门上用当地语言写着‘用任何珠宝也换不来自由’。如今，堡垒内部也被用作戏台，在这里上演的莎士比亚名剧哈姆雷特已经成为杜布罗夫尼克夏季盛典的标志。',0,7559,127,26,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Fort%20Lovrijenac/Thumb%20Fort%20Lovrijenac.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Fort%20Lovrijenac/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Fort%20Lovrijenac/Fort%20Lovrijenac.mp3',99),(113,'Nacionalni Park Mljet','亚姆列特国家公园','','Pristani?te 2,20226 Gove?ari - Mljet, Hrvatska','','','','Mljet National Park is large area that borders two salt water lakes','克羅地亞最多姿多彩的國家公園。','70/125KN','70/125库纳','385 20 744 041','http://np-mljet.hr/en/',0,0,'The Mljet National Park is the oldest marine protected area in the Mediterranean and it has delighted its numerous visitors for 56 years with the colours and the scent of untouched nature.','姆列特國家公園坐落於克羅地亞屬亞德裏亞海諸島中最南端的姆列特島，占據姆列特島的西北部，是一個環境優雅、景致美麗的公園，因多種多樣的娛樂活動而備受關註，是克羅地亞最多姿多彩的國家公園。公園內有兩條湖泊，這使得公園成為最絕佳的旅遊勝地，多種娛樂活動圍繞著湖泊展開。皮劃艇、獨木舟、遊泳為知名的運動項目。圍繞著湖泊修建了多條小徑，租一輛自行車或者牽手愛人圍繞著湖泊前進，感受到的不僅是視覺上的美麗，更有凈化心靈的作用。在姆列特國家公園遊泳和曬日光浴也備受歡迎。',0,6860,60,26,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Nacionalni%20Park%20Mljet/Thumb%20Nacionalni%20Park%20Mljet.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Nacionalni%20Park%20Mljet/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Nacionalni%20Park%20Mljet/Nacionalni%20Park%20Mljet.mp3',99),(114,'Pancicev Park','Pancicev公园','','Pancicev Park, Rijeka, Croatia','','','','Beautiful park','美丽的花园','0','0','','',0,0,'Pancicev Park is located Ulica Fra Serafina Sch?na in Rijeka (51000) in the region of Primorsko-Goranska Zupanija (Hrvatska).','Pancicev公园坐落于里耶卡的Ulica Fra Serafina Sch?na',0,8644,68,30,5,'','','','',99),(115,'Plitvice Lakes National Park','普利特维采湖群国家公园','','Plitvicka jezera, Plitvice Lakes National Park 53231, Croatia','','','9:00-19:00','One of the oldest national parks in Southeast Europe and the largest national park in Croatia','欧洲九寨沟','Jan-Mar/Nov-Dec 55,00kn;Apr-Jun/Sep-Oct 110,00kn; ','一月-五月/十一月-十二月 55库钠；四月-六月/九月-十月 110库钠；七月-八月 180库钠','385 (0)53 751 015','http://np-plitvicka-jezera.hr/en/',0,0,'Plitvice Lakes National Park is one of the oldest national parks in Southeast Europe and the largest national park in Croatia. In 1979, Plitvice Lakes National Park was added to the UNESCO World Heritage register..Every season has its own unique charm and the Plitvice Lakes with their alternating colors and every new awakening, both trapped in ice or in the shade of the trees, will leave you with a very distinct, unique and invaluable impression.The Plitvice Lakes are constant, yet always different, and they will surely surprise you with a new experience or new revelation.','普利特维采湖群国家公园（Plitvice Lakes National Park），位于克罗地亚中部的喀斯特山区，创立于1949年，1979年被联合国教科文组织列为世界遗产，为东南欧历史最悠久的国家公园，是克罗地亚最大的国家公园。公园由16个大大小小的湖泊组成，所以称为十六湖国家公园。“十六湖”呈带状蜿蜒于山谷中，分为上湖区和下湖区两个部分。聚集了12个湖泊的上湖区湖底是白云石，下湖区则包括位于石灰石的峡谷中的4湖。公园内有许多石灰岩沉积而形成的天然堤坝，这些堤坝又形成出许多的瀑布和湖泊，这些湖泊呈现出翠绿或宝石蓝等迷人色彩，因此被誉为“克罗埃西亚的宝石”。',0,5643,113,28,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Plitvice%20Lakes%20National%20Park/Thumb%20Plitvice%20Lakes%20National%20Park.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Plitvice%20Lakes%20National%20Park/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Plitvice%20Lakes%20National%20Park/Plitvice%20Lakes%20National%20Park.mp3',99),(116,'Povijesni I Pomorski Muzej Istre','伊斯特拉历史博物馆','','Gradinski uspon 6, 52100, Pula, Croatia','','','','Old fortress built by the Venetians, situated on a hill in the center of Pula','普拉的历史建筑，具有军事意义的历史博物馆','','','385 52 211 566','http://www.ppmi.hr/hr/#',0,0,'Povijesni I Pomorski Muzej Istre, a museum collected more than 15000 pieces, more than 75000 items of cultural relics, historical, political, military and ethnographic properties.','伊斯特拉历史博物馆，博物馆收集了超过15000件文物，历史，政治，军事和民族志性质的75000多个物品。',0,6269,111,29,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Istria/Sights/Povijesni%20I%20Pomorski%20Muzej%20Istre/Thumb%20Povijesni%20I%20Pomorski%20Muzej%20Istre.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Povijesni%20I%20Pomorski%20Muzej%20Istre/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Povijesni%20I%20Pomorski%20Muzej%20Istre/Povijesni%20I%20Pomorski%20Muzej%20Istre.mp3',99),(117,'Kastel','普拉Kastel城堡','','Gradinski uspon 6, 52100, Pula, Croatia','','','','Old fortress built by the Venetians, situated on a hill in the center of Pula','普拉的历史建筑，城堡内有历史博物馆','','','385 52 211 566','http://www.ppmi.hr/hr/',0,0,'Pula Castle “Ka?tel” is an old fortress built by the Venetians, situated on a hill in the center of Pula. It is interesting to point out that there are evidence that hill fort of the Histri was once in the same location. Because of its dominating position, the fortress was always used for defense of the city, bay and port. The Castle was built between 1630 and 1633, based on a design from French military engineer Antonio De Villa, so it belongs to the French style. It was always an important defensive point for Venetian control of the Adriatic. The stone from large Roman theater was used for its construction, along with the one from other quarries around Pula.','堡垒的中心是一个矩形的形状，四个额外的五角塔增加了它的安全性。从空中角度看，城堡的形状像是一朵绽开的花朵。城堡曾经升级了好几次。在奥匈帝国时期，这个堡垒叫哈芬·卡斯特尔，它是普拉当时防御外敌制度的一部分。第一次世界大战结束后，城堡就渐渐地失去它原有的意义。 如今在城堡里有伊斯特拉历史博物馆，博物馆收集了超过15000件文物，历史，政治，军事和民族志性质的75000多个物品。以举办表演，聚会，音乐会，表演和电影发布会而闻名，特别是在夏季。除了丰富的历史，登上普拉 Ka?tel城堡可以欣赏普拉全景及其周边地区的迷人景色。',0,4426,65,29,5,'','','','',99),(118,'Pula Arena','普拉竞技场','','Scalierova ul. 30, 52100, Pula, Croatia','','','','Only remaining Roman amphitheater to have four side towers and with all three Roman architectural orders entirely preserved','世界上最大、保存最完好的罗马遗址之一','30/70kn','30/70库纳','385 52 219 028','',0,0,'The Pula Arena is a Roman amphitheater located in Pula, on the southern tip of the Istria peninsula, north-western Croatia. It has been estimated that there are around 230 Roman amphitheaters that are still surviving today. The Pula Arena is unique, as it has often been claimed that this amphitheater is the “only remaining Roman amphitheater to have four side towers and with all three Roman architectural orders entirely preserved”. As a comparison, it has been claimed that the famous Coliseum in Rome has had two-thirds of its original structure destroyed over the millennia.','位于克罗地亚的普拉古罗马竞技场建于公元一世纪罗马皇帝维斯帕先的统治时期。普拉竞技场是世界上最大、保存最完好的罗马遗址之一。起初这里被用作角斗场，如今则被用作举办音乐会和观看电影的场地。',0,7321,142,29,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Istria/Sights/Pula%20Arena/Thumb%20Pula%20Arena.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Pula%20Arena/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Pula%20Arena/Pula%20Arena.mp3',99),(119,'Rajska Plaza','Rajska Plaza','','San Marino,Rab, Croatia','','','','The beach is being supervised by experienced lifeguards from 09:00 to 18:00, so you can relax and enjoy your vacation','克罗地亚的公共海滩','','','','',0,0,'Paradise beach (Rajska pla?a) is 2km long and is located on the northern part of the island of Rab, in a small tourist resort Lopar. It was awarded a Blue flag because of its quality offer and clean waters.The beach is sandy and somewhat shallow which is ideal for children. There is a big sports center in the neighborhood with different playgrounds and tennis, soccer, basketball, volleyball, miniature golf and table tennis courts. You can also try the water slide as well as numerous other activities and water sports. The beach is being supervised by experienced lifeguards from 09:00 to 18:00, so you can relax and enjoy your vacation.','克罗地亚的公共海滩',0,6330,69,30,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Rajska%20Plaza/Thumb%20Rajska%20Plaza.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Rajska%20Plaza/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Rajska%20Plaza/Rajska%20Plaza.mp3',99),(120,'Rijeka City','里耶卡','','Rijeka 51000, Croatia','','','','Croatia\'s third-largest city, Rijeka is a bustling blend of gritty 20th-century port and Italianate Habsburg grandeur','克罗地亚第三大城市和主要的海港城市','','','','',0,0,'Croatia’s third-largest city, Rijeka is a bustling blend of gritty 20th-century port and Italianate Habsburg grandeur. Most people speed through en route to the islands or Dalmatia, but those who pause will discover charm, culture, good nightlife, intriguing festivals and Croatia’s most colourful carnival.\nDespite some regrettable architectural ventures in the outskirts, much of the centre is replete with ornate Austro-Hungarian–style buildings. It’s a surprisingly verdant city once you’ve left its concrete core, which contains Croatia’s largest port, with ships, cargo and cranes lining the waterfront.\nRijeka is a vital transport hub, but as there’s no real beach in the city most people base themselves in nearby Opatija.','里耶卡位于亚得里亚海克瓦内尔湾畔，是克罗地亚第三大城市和主要的海港城市，面积44平方公里，人口144,043。 该城的两个名字，Rijeka和Fiume在各自的语言里都是“河流”的意思。',0,6688,66,30,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Rijeka%20City/Thumb%20Rijeka%20City.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Rijeka%20City/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Rijeka%20City/Rijeka%20City.mp3',99),(121,'The St Vitus Cathedral','里耶卡主教座堂','','Grivica ul. 11, 51000, Rijeka, Croatia','','','Mon-Fri 6:00-17:00, ','Built by the Jesuit order in 1638 on the site of an older church and dedicated to Rijeka’s patron saint','教堂融合了巴洛克式建筑和哥特式建筑的风格。','','','385 51 330 879','http://katedrala-rijeka.eu/',0,0,'North of the Roman Gate is this unusual round cathedral, built by the Jesuit order in 1638 on the site of an older church and dedicated to Rijeka’s patron saint. If it looks familiar, it\'s probably because it features on the reverse of the 100KN note. Massive marble pillars support the central dome under which are housed baroque altars and a 13th-century Gothic crucifix.','里耶卡主教座堂是位于克罗地亚城市里耶卡的一座罗马天主教的教堂。现在的教堂始建于1638年。教堂融合了巴洛克式建筑和哥特式建筑的风格。里耶卡主教座堂被印在1993年和2002年发行的克罗地亚库纳的钞票反面。',0,4451,70,30,5,'','','','',99),(122,'Sea Organ','海洋风琴','','Sea Organ, 23000, Zadar,Croatia','步行即可到达','All','All','Plays music by way of sea waves and tubes','看不到却听得见的巨型建筑','','','385 91 339 2559','',0,0,'Zadar’s incredible Sea Organ, designed by local architect Nikola Ba?i?, is unique. Set within the perforated stone stairs that descend into the sea is a system of pipes and whistles that exudes wistful sighs when the movement of the sea pushes air through it. The effect is hypnotic, the mellifluous tones increasing in volume when a boat or ferry passes by. You can swim from the steps off the promenade while listening to the sounds.','Sea Organ由一组7个分别长10米的延伸入海的台阶组成，这些表面看似平常的台阶，除了是岸边让人们休闲娱乐的散步系统，用石阶引导人们接近大海，更把海洋“拉向”了人们。在7组石阶里面暗藏着精妙安排合理分布的许多聚乙烯管，当里面的空气被海浪推动后，通过直径不一的各条管道，促使设置在共鸣腔中的风琴管发出声音，共鸣管位于散步系统的下面，并通过石头中神秘的开口释放声音。7组石阶代表7个音阶，每个音阶里面通过不同的管道表现出5个音调，由此来达到演奏音乐的效果，这也是源于当地传统的达尔马提亚歌曲的旋律设置。',0,6192,104,28,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Sea%20Organ/Thumb%20Sea%20Organ.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Sea%20Organ/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Sea%20Organ/Sea%20Organ.mp3',99),(123,'Split City','斯普利特市区','','Split 21000, Croatia','','','','The largest city on the Adriatic Coast, seaside delight','克罗地亚第二大城，斯普利特亦是最古老的城市之一','','','','',0,0,'The largest city on the Adriatic Coast, seaside delight 。There is an abundance of restaurants and wine cellars. Sites such as Diocletian\'s Palace and Mausoleum, the Grgur Ninski Statue and the Cathedral and Bell Tower of St. The city\'s coves offer several lovely beaches, including central Bacvice. Ferries link Split to Dalmatian summer resorts.','斯普利特(Split)，是克罗地亚历史名城、克罗地亚第二大城市、斯普利特-达尔马提亚县的首府、达尔马提亚地区第一大海港、造船和航运中心，也是东南欧最著名的旅游胜地之一。 城内有罗马帝国时的皇宫和其他古迹多处，多教堂。疗养和游览胜地。公元7世纪建城，罗马时代名“阿斯帕拉托斯”，后改称“斯帕拉托”和“斯普利特”。城市建筑以罗马皇帝戴克里先夏宫为核心发展起来。戴克里先宫建于公元305年。占地3万平方米，宫墙高达17～21米，宽2米，宫殿正门6根大理石柱是远涉重洋从中东运至，工程浩繁，宏伟壮丽。附近萨洛纳城是罗马达尔马提亚王朝的古都，现在还保存着有价值的历史遗迹。',0,7606,62,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Split%20City/Thumb%20Split%20City.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Split%20City/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Split%20City/Split%20City.mp3',99),(124,'Stina Winery','Stina Winery','','Bracka Cesta 13, Bol, Brac Island 21420, Croatia','by boat','','','Wine in style','品位地道的红酒和置身与浪漫的环境中','','','385 21 306 220','http://www.stina-vino.hr/en/',0,0,'The island of Bra? is unique and famous for its white stone (Stina), but also for numerous artists who lived and created on the island. Many famous Croatian poets, authors, sculptors and painters were born on Bra?. Bra? stone has always been a source of inspiration due to its beauty, but it is also a symbol of hardship when it comes to viticulture and viniculture.','斯蒂娜是布拉奇岛上的葡萄酒，位于博尔中心的大型现代化，功能齐全的酒庄。',0,9456,51,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Stina%20Winery/Thumb%20Stina%20Winery.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Stina%20Winery/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Stina%20Winery/Stina%20Winery.mp3',99),(125,'Stinica Ferry','Stinica客运中心','','D105, 53287, Stinica, Croatia','','','','Where the new ferry terminal and port for travel to Rab Island is located','轮渡客运中心','','','385 51 724 122','',0,0,'Stinica is a small coastal village and bay just few kilometres north from Jablanac and 40 km away from Senj. The bay used to be an important port where large timber warehouse was located. At the time, the timber was delivered by cable car from Velebit mountain. Nowadays, Stinica is bay where the new ferry terminal and port for travel to Rab Island is located.','前往拉布岛的轮渡客运中心',0,7463,115,30,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Stinica%20Ferry/Thumb%20Stinica%20Ferry.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Stinica%20Ferry/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Stinica%20Ferry/Stinica%20Ferry.mp3',99),(126,'Our Lady of Trsat Church','特尔萨特的圣母圣地','','Frankopanski trg, 51000, Rijeka, Croatia','Trsat stairs, bus, city bus routes 1 and 1A, automobile from','','7:00 - 20:00','The largest pilgrimage centre of Western Croatia','水手在出海前往往到这里祈祷圣母庇护，免除疾病与灾祸。','','','385 51 452 900','http://www.kvarner.hr/hodocastiti-svetistima/en/po',0,0,'According to legend, the angels carrying the house of Jesus\' mother from Nazareth rested here in the late 13th century before moving it to Loreto across the Adriatic in Le Marche. Pilgrims started trickling into the chapel erected on the site, and then pouring in when the Pope donated an icon of St Mary in 1367 (located on the main altar, behind a magnificent wrought-iron gate). The church still attracts thousands of pilgrims each year.','特尔萨特的圣母圣地：于中世纪晚期修建在特尔萨特山海拔135米的地方，是游客的保护神所在的地方，尤其是水手在出海前往往到这里祈祷圣母庇护，免除疾病与灾祸。它是里耶卡哥特式建筑物的代表作，但设计者却是巴罗克建筑师塔斯切。',0,5947,76,30,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Our%20Lady%20of%20Trsat%20Church/Thumb%20Our%20Lady%20of%20Trsat%20Church.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Our%20Lady%20of%20Trsat%20Church/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Our%20Lady%20of%20Trsat%20Church/Our%20Lady%20of%20Trsat%20Church.mp3',99),(127,'Peristyle (Peristil)','Peristyle (Peristil)','','21000, Peristil ul. 2, 21000, Split, Croatia','','','0:00-24:00','Centre of Split and the entire world','斯普利特的城市心脏','','','','http://www.visitsplit.com/en/528/peristyle-peristi',0,0,'Peristyle, as the central square of the Palace, intended for the Emperor Diocletian celebrated as the living son of Jupiter, finds its place among many temples. Owing to its unique beauty and unusual acoustics, Peistyle became the ideal theatre scenery, perfect for opera classics and works of ancient literature, but also the stage where abundant urban life continues.','佩里斯特尔是众多宫殿的中心广场。',0,4345,86,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Peristyle%20(Peristil)/Thumb%20Peristyle%20(Peristil).jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Peristyle%20(Peristil)/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Peristyle%20(Peristil)/Peristyle%20(Peristil).mp3',99),(128,'Vidova Gora','Vidova Gora','','Bol, Brac Island, Croatia','drive, hike or cycle','','0:00-24:00','Vidova Gora on the island of Brac is the highest peak of all the Croatian islands','亚得里亚海最高点','','','','',0,0,'Vidova Gora on the island of Brac is the highest peak of all the Croatian islands - It\'s a fantastic view point and apart from being able to see the distant Croatian island of Jabuka (apple) and practically the while of one side of the Island of Hvar, you can apparently see as far as Italy on a clear day! Aswell as these more distant shores, there is also one very famous beach that it is also worth coming up here for and that is to see probably Croatia\'s most famous beach - Zlatni Rat or \"Golden Horn\". The views from the top stretches to the south coast of the island with a green belt around Bol. View particularly attracted to Zlatni Rat, a narrow sandy promontory that cuts like a peak of more than 600 m in blue sky.It\'s spectacular shifting form and turquoise waters are stunning from this','布拉奇岛上的Vidova Gora是所有克罗地亚群岛的最高峰 - 这是一个奇妙的观点，除了能够看到遥远的克罗地亚的Jabuka岛，几乎是Hvar岛一边的同时你可以在天气晴朗的情况下看到意大利！还有一个非常着名的海滩，也值得来这里，那可能是克罗地亚最着名的海滩 - Zlatni Rat或“Golden Horn”。顶部的景色延伸到岛屿的南部海岸，周围有绿色环绕。它是壮观的转变形式，绿松石水域从这个高点惊人，你真的可以看到整个海岸线的美景。',0,7886,150,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Vidova%20Gora/Thumb%20Vidova%20Gora.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Vidova%20Gora/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Vidova%20Gora/Vidova%20Gora.mp3',99),(129,'Dubrovnik City Walls','杜布罗夫尼克城墙','','Gunduli?eva poljana 220000 Dubrovnik, Hrvatska','','','9:00-19:30','Dubrovnik City walls are the most important feature of Dubrovnik','杜布罗夫尼克老城的一部分,被列入世界文化遗产。','30/120kn','30/120库纳','385 20 324641','http://citywallsdubrovnik.hr/bastina/gradske-zidin',0,0,'Dubrovnik city walls today have the girth established in the 13th century and were systematically and continuously perfected over several hundred years, until 1660, when the last of the towers, the St. Stephen’s Bastion, located at the southern part of the walls, was finished. The walls stretch over 1940 m (6365 ft.) and consist of the main wall, sixteen towers, three forts, six bastions (bulwarks), two corner forts (cantonatas), three pre-walls with several turrets, three moats, two barbicans, two drawbridges and one breakwater.','杜布罗夫尼克城墙是围绕在老城周围的防御性石墙，从7世纪起就矗立在克罗地亚南部，被认为是中世纪时期最伟大的防御系统之一，从未被敌军破坏过。1979年，杜布罗夫尼克老城和很大一部分城墙一同被联合国教科文组织列入世界文化遗产名录。最古老的环城防御系统类似木栅栏，现在我们看到的大部分是在12-17世纪修建的，不间断长1940米，几乎绕城一圈，最高处25米，是欧洲最大最完整的复杂结构城墙，保护了杜布罗夫尼克五个世纪的平安与繁荣。漫步在老城的城墙上，可以欣赏到完美的景色。城墙的主要入口在Inner Pile Gates旁边，Minceta堡垒位于城市西北部的城墙内，是杜布罗夫尼克最美丽的文化景点之一。圣卢克塔历史上一直保卫着杜布罗夫尼克海港的入口。圣约翰堡垒建于16世纪，一层是水族馆，二层和三层是海洋博物馆。',0,9409,141,26,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Dubrovnik%20City%20Walls/Thumb%20Dubrovnik%20City%20Walls.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Dubrovnik%20City%20Walls/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Dubrovnik%20&%20Southern%20Dalmatia/Sights/Dubrovnik%20City%20Walls/Dubrovnik%20City%20Walls.mp3',99),(130,'Zadar City','扎达尔','','Zadar, Croatia','','','0:00-24:00','Key transport hub with superb ferry connections to the surrounding islands','扎达尔有独一无二的海景，海风琴和太阳敬礼，日落确实太美，值得坐在海边好好观赏，老城不大，但是有很棒的餐厅','0','0','385 (0)23 316 166','www.zadar.travel',0,0,'Boasting a historic old town of Roman ruins, medieval churches, cosmopolitan cafes and quality museums set on a small peninsula, Zadar is an intriguing city. It’s not too crowded, it’s not overrun with tourists and its two unique attractions – the sound-and-light spectacle of the Sea Organ and the Sun Salutation – need to be seen and heard to be believed.\n\nWhile it’s not a picture-postcard kind of place, the mix of ancient relics, Habsburg elegance, coastal setting and unsightly tower blocks is what gives Zadar so much character. It\'s no Dubrovnik, but it\'s not a museum town either – this is a living, vibrant city, enjoyed by residents and visitors alike.\nZadar is also a key transport hub with superb ferry connections to the surrounding islands.','扎达尔是克罗地亚的第五大城市，位于亚得里亚海沿岸,是扎达尔县和北达尔马提亚地区的行政中心。扎达尔有独一无二的海景，日落确实太美，值得坐在海边好好观赏，老城不大，但是有很棒的餐厅',0,6321,99,28,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Zadar%20City/Thumb%20Zadar%20City.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Zadar%20City/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zadar%20&%20National%20Park/Sights/Zadar%20City/Zadar%20City.mp3',99),(131,'Zlatni Rat Beach','尖角海滩','','Put Zlatnog rata, 21420, Bol,Croatia','by car, by boat,by a 20km walk from Bol,tourist train','','0:00-24:00','Zlatni rat is one of the most beautiful beaches on the Croatian coastline and at the same time the most representative panorama of Bol','深入海中634米的狭长海滩，其形状会随着海浪方向的变化而变化。','0','0','385 1 3844 288','http://www.visitbrac.com/destinations/bol/zlatni-r',0,0,'The paradise beach Zlatni rat is one of the most beautiful beaches on the Croatian coastline and at the same time the most representative panorama of Bol. It was created by deposits of fine pebbles as sediment around the underwater reef, spreading as a small tongue as much as 500 metres into the sea.The very tip of Zlatni rat keeps changing its shape constantly due to the influence of winds, waves and sea currents, making it appear different and repeatedly interesting.','尖角海滩位于克罗地亚南部布拉奇岛南岸，是一个深入海中634米的狭长海滩，其形状会随着海浪方向的变化而变化。是一处著名的旅游胜地。',0,7417,127,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Zlatni%20Rat%20Beach/Thumb%20Zlatni%20Rat%20Beach.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Zlatni%20Rat%20Beach/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Zlatni%20Rat%20Beach/Zlatni%20Rat%20Beach.mp3',99),(132,'Korzo','Korzo','','Near Grad Rijeka, Rijeka 51000, Croatia','','','0:00-24:00','Korzo is the place where people gather and move apart, where they hang out, do business, make acquaintances, but also go shopping','里耶卡逛街、购物的精品步行街','0','0','385 51 335 882','http://www.visitrijeka.eu/What_To_See/Korzo',0,0,'Rijeka is reflected in Korzo, at Korzo you can read Rijeka. Korzo is the place where people gather and move apart, where they hang out, do business, make acquaintances, but also go shopping. The citizens of Rijeka can do whatever they want at Korzo. They can see and be seen. Some would say that Korzo is the place where the live city newspapers are written daily. They are both written and read by the citizens themselves, but also by all those who come to Rijeka from all over the world.','在Korzo你可以读懂里耶卡这座城市。Korzo是人们聚集和分离的地方，在那里闲逛，做生意，或者与老朋友畅谈生活，同时也是去购物的完美地点。人们可以在Korzo做任何他们想要的事情。',0,8122,87,30,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Korzo/Thumb%20Korzo.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Korzo/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Rijeka%20&%20Rab/Sights/Korzo/Korzo.mp3',99),(133,'Bell Tower','戴克里先宫钟楼','','Split, Croatia','步行即可到达','','','City view','极佳观景位','','','385 21 345 602','http://www.diocletianspalace.org/',0,0,'Bell Tower of Diocletian\'s Palace','戴克里先宫钟楼',0,8362,108,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Bell%20Tower/Thumb%20Bell%20Tower.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Bell%20Tower/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Bell%20Tower/Bell%20Tower.mp3',99),(134,'Diocletian\'s Palace','戴克里先宫','','Split, Croatia','步行即可到达','','','Ruins of the Roman','罗马时代遗址','0','0','385 21 345 602','http://www.diocletianspalace.org/',0,0,'The ruins of the Roman Emperor Diocletian\'s palace date back to the late 3rd to early 4th century A.D.','戴克里先宫（Diocletian\'s Palace）罗马帝国宫殿，约公元295年—公元305年建，占地近4公顷。戴克里先退位后即居于此。位于克罗地亚斯普利特市，为一座宏大壮丽的海滨堡垒和豪华巨型乡间别墅。平面呈长方形，宫殿南北长215米，宫墙厚2.1米。前临亚得里亚海，南高22米，北高18米。计16座塔楼和4座宫门。其中心有两条11米宽的拱廊大道。宫殿前部为寝宫，沿海拱廊长160米，宽7.3米，可瞭望海景和达尔马提亚海岸。后部为朝堂，宫殿于阿瓦尔人入侵时被严重破坏，639年阿瓦尔人撤退后，宫殿遗址被萨洛纳城难民改为他用。1979年，该遗址被列为世界文化遗产。',0,7444,128,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Diocletian\'s%20Palace/Thumb%20Diocletian\'s%20Palace.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Diocletian\'s%20Palace/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Diocletian\'s%20Palace/Diocletian\'s%20Palace.mp3',99),(135,'Cattedrale di San Domino','斯普利特主教座堂','','Ul. Kraj Svetog Duje 5, 21000, Split, Croatia','','','','Among the European cathedrals the one in Split finds its seat in the oldest building','世界上所有基督教主教座堂中第二古老的主座教堂','','','385 21 342 589','',0,0,'Split’s octagonal cathedral is one of the best-preserved ancient Roman buildings standing today. It was built as a mausoleum for Diocletian, the last famous persecutor of the Christians, who was interred here in 311 AD. The Christians got the last laugh, destroying the emperor\'s sarcophagus and converting his tomb into a church in the 5th century, dedicated to one of his victims. Note that a ticket for the cathedral includes admission to its crypt, treasury and baptistery (Temple of Jupiter).','斯普利特主教座堂是位于克罗地亚城市斯普利特的一座罗马天主教的教堂，也是天主教斯普利特-马卡尔斯卡总教区的主教座堂。教堂外观为哥特式建筑。教堂的结构本身修建于公元305年，是世界上所有基督教主教座堂中第二古老的。',0,9132,67,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Cattedrale%20di%20San%20Domino/Thumb%20Cattedrale%20di%20San%20Domino.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Cattedrale%20di%20San%20Domino/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Cattedrale%20di%20San%20Domino/Cattedrale%20di%20San%20Domino.mp3',99),(136,'Ethnographic Museum','萨格勒布民族学博物馆','','Trg bra?e Ma?urani? 14, 10000, Zagreb, Croatia','','','10:00-18:00','The ethnographic heritage of Croatia is catalogued in this museum housed in a domed 1903 building','克罗地亚的人种学遗产被编目在这座博物馆内','adult/concession 20/15KN','20/15库纳','01-48 26 220','http://www.emz.hr/',0,0,'The ethnographic heritage of Croatia is catalogued in this museum housed in a domed 1903 building. Out of 70,000 items, about 2750 are on display, including ceramics, jewellery, musical instruments, tools, weapons and folk costumes, such as gold-embroidered scarves from Slavonia and lace from the island of Pag. Thanks to donations from the Croatian explorers Mirko and Stevo Seljan, there are also artefacts from South America, Ethiopia, China, Japan and Australia.','',0,6331,102,31,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Zagreb/Sights/Ethnographic%20Museum/Thumb%20Ethnographic%20Museum.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zagreb/Sights/Ethnographic%20Museum/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Zagreb/Sights/Ethnographic%20Museum/Ethnographic%20Museum.mp3',99),(137,'Temple of Jupiter','朱庇特神庙','','Temple Of Jupiter, Split, Croatia','','','8:00-20:00','One of the most beautiful European monuments','这个寺庙是最美丽的欧洲古迹之一','0','0','','',0,0,'Eminent Scottish architect Robert Adam considered this temple one of the most beautiful European monuments. Rectangular in its floor plan the temple served to celebrate the Jupiter\'s cult. It lies on an elevated podium, with a six column porch in front of it. Embossed images on the portal, as well as the barrel coffered vault influenced the early Renaissance architecture of Andrija Alessi and Nikola Firentinac in Trogir. \n\nThe transformation into a Baptistery happened in the Late Antiquity era, with a construction of a crypt under the building dedicated to St Thomas. In the former temple, at the beginning of the 13th century, a Baptismal Font was made of the altar screen pluteus (11th century), originally seated in the cathedral. One of the posts shows a figure of a Croatian king (Petar Kr','着名的苏格兰建筑师罗伯特·亚当认为这个寺庙是最美丽的欧洲古迹之一。门户上的压纹图像以及桶形拱顶影响了特里格尔的Andrija Alessi和Nikola Firentinac的早期文艺复兴时期的建筑。朱庇特神庙是戴克里皇帝建造的，据说他把自己当做朱庇特，并进行了宗教改革，继而建了这座神庙。守卫在门口的黑色花岗岩无头狮子雕塑，是5世纪时候从埃及进口来的。寺庙下面是个地下室，曾经被用做教堂。',0,8258,59,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Temple%20of%20Jupiter/Thumb%20Temple%20of%20Jupiter.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Temple%20of%20Jupiter/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Temple%20of%20Jupiter/Temple%20of%20Jupiter.mp3',99),(138,'Kašjuni Beach','Kašjuni Beach','','Ka?juni Beach, Split, Croatia','','','0:00-24:00','','','0','0','','',0,0,'Ka?juni Beach is located almost at the westernmost part of Marjan hill, and this is the first beach to the beach Ka?telet westward. \nOn the beach there are two bars where you can freshen up in the breaks between the churning in the sea, but also you can go in the evening for a drink and enjoy some of the parties that are often organized.','',0,5298,138,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Kašjuni%20Beach/Thumb%20Kašjuni%20Beach.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Kašjuni%20Beach/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Kašjuni%20Beach/Kašjuni%20Beach.mp3',99),(139,'Supetar','Supetar','','Supetar，Bol, Brac Island 21420, Croatia','by boat','','0:00-24:00','The biggest settlement on the island Brac','布拉奇岛的中心','0','0','','',0,0,'With its 3500 inhabitants Supetar is the biggest settlement on the island Brac, and the centre of the island.Although it suffers in comparison to its more glitzy sister, Bol, Supetar is a pleasant little town in its own right, with a historic core of old stone streets fanning out from a little harbour dominated by an imposing church. It\'s a popular holiday destination for Croatian families, with pebbly beaches within an easy stroll of the town centre. The views back across the water to Split and the mountains beyond are universally wonderful.','苏佩塔尔是克罗地亚的城镇，位于该国南部布拉奇岛北岸，由斯普利特-达尔马提亚县负责管辖，面积30平方公里，是该岛的经济、文化和旅游中心',0,5716,66,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Supetar/Thumb%20Supetar.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Supetar/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Supetar/Supetar.mp3',99),(140,'Sustipan Park','Sustipan公园','','Sustipanski put, 21000, Split, Croatia','步行即可到达','','0:00-24:00','Ideal spot for contemplation when viewing of Split.','欣赏斯普利特的理想地点','0','0','','',0,0,'Sustipan Park is located above the marina and at the foot of Marjan Hill. In ancient times, this small park was a cemetery. Archeological excavations have lead to the discoveries of Roman stone coffins and Christian basilica from the early Middle Ages. The park is an ideal spot for contemplation when viewing the marvelous city of Split.','Sustipan公园位于Marjan Hill山脚下。在古代，这个小公园是一座公墓。考古发掘发现了中世纪初期罗马石棺和基督教大教堂。同时公园是观赏Split城市的理想地点。',0,9688,65,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Sustipan%20Park/Thumb%20Sustipan%20Park.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Sustipan%20Park/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Sustipan%20Park/Sustipan%20Park.mp3',99),(141,'Prva Vidilica Na Marjanu','Prva Vidilica Na Marjanu','','?etali?te Luke Boti?a 3','步行即可到达','','0:00-24:00','See the old town Split','老城观景点','0','0','','',0,0,'From this view you can see the old town Split above the belvedere prva vidilica. This path leads the way up to the church of Sv. Nikola Putnik.','从这里你可以欣赏斯普利特老城区的绝妙全景',0,7293,77,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Prva%20Vidilica%20Na%20Marjanu/Thumb%20Prva%20Vidilica%20Na%20Marjanu.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Prva%20Vidilica%20Na%20Marjanu/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Prva%20Vidilica%20Na%20Marjanu/Prva%20Vidilica%20Na%20Marjanu.mp3',99),(142,'Port of Split','斯普利特港口','','Split, Croatia','','','0:00-24:00','One of most important port of Croatia','克罗地亚西部主要海港之一','0','0','','',0,0,'The Port of Split is a port in the central Dalmatian city of Split, Croatia. The port was originally a trading post originally established by Greek settlers from the island of Vis and subsequently taken over by the Romans. The port thrived through the Middle Ages, but it suffered a decline in the late 18th and early 19th centuries when the Port of Rijeka took over as the primary trading and shipping outlet of the region. The decline was also attributed to the decline of the Ottoman Empire, a traditional market for the Port of Split, and the growing domination of Austrian Empire.','位于克罗地亚（全称：克罗地亚共和国 THE REPUBLIC OF CROATLA）西南沿海的MARJAN半岛东南岸，在斯普利特（SPLIT）海峡的东北端，濒临亚得里亚（A-DRIATIC）海的西侧，是克罗地亚西部主要海港之一。初建于7世纪，是通往内地的铁路起点。主要工业有造船、水泥、化学、纺织品及食品加工等。有罗马帝国的皇宫、博物馆、艺术画廓及古迹多处，又是疗养和旅游胜地。港口距机场约23km，每天有定期航班飞往罗马、巴黎、伦敦和苏黎世等地。',0,4402,141,27,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Port%20of%20Split/Thumb%20Port%20of%20Split.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Port%20of%20Split/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Split%20&%20Central%20Dalmatia/Sights/Port%20of%20Split/Port%20of%20Split.mp3',99),(143,'Augustov Hram','奥古斯都神庙','','Forum b.b., 52100, Pula, Croatia','','','06:0-23:00','A temple is considered one of the two best complete Roman monuments outside Italy','意大利国土外最棒古罗马时期的神庙之一','','','385 52 351 300','',0,0,'Augustov Hram. Dedicated to the first Roman emperor, Augustus, it was probably built during the emperor\'s lifetime at some point between 2 BC and his death in AD 14. It was built on a podium with a tetrastyle prostyle porch of Corinthian columns and measures about 8 by 17.3 m (26 by 57 ft), and 14 m (46 ft) high. The richly decorated frieze is similar to that of a somewhat larger and older temple, the Maison Carrée in N?mes, France. These two temples are considered the two best complete Roman monuments outside Italy.','奥古斯都神庙是位于克罗地亚西北部伊斯特拉半岛城市普拉的一座古罗马时期的神庙，修建于公元前2年至14年。',0,4129,125,29,5,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Thumb%20point%20Croatia/Istria/Sights/Augustov%20Hram/Thumb%20Augustov%20Hram.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Augustov%20Hram/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1502848605/Croatia/Istria/Sights/Augustov%20Hram/Augustov%20Hram.mp3',99),(144,'Kravica Waterfalls','Kravica Waterfalls','','Neretva valley, Mostar 88300, Bosnia and Herzegovina','By cab or taxi.By rented cars.','Opened daily','0:00-24:00','In spring, this stunning mini-Niagara of 25m cascades pounds itself into a dramatic, steamy fury. ','小型的普利特维策湖群国家公园','0','0','039/832-340','http://www.jpparkovi-ljubuski.com/',0,0,'In spring, this stunning mini-Niagara of 25m cascades pounds itself into a dramatic, steamy fury. In summer the falls are less impressive but surrounding pools become shallow enough for swimming.The falls are a 15-minute walk from a car park that\'s 4km down a dead-end road turning off the M6 (Čapljina–Ljubuški Rd) at Km 42.5. There\'s no public transport, but many Mostar group tours include a visit to the falls along with Blagaj and Počitelj.\nThe waters of the Trebižat River branch out, cascading from the tuff walls from a height of 30 metres, and they form a natural amphitheatre, 150-metre wide, creating spectacular effects that bring to mind, even if in a more modest dimension, the imposing Niagara waterfalls.','如果来黑塞哥维那的Ljubuški或者莫斯塔尔的话，一定要来这个美丽的自然景点。Kravice是波斯尼亚和黑塞哥维那的Trebižat河上的瀑布，位于Ljubuški向南10公里，莫斯塔尔向南40公里。瀑布的高度达到25米，整个湖围绕着瀑布半径为120米。Kravice是一个热门的游泳和野餐的区域，一直有很多来自莫斯塔尔、默主歌耶以及杜布罗夫尼克的游客。',0,4442,70,33,6,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Thumb%20point%20Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Kravica%20Waterfalls/Thumb%20Kravica%20Waterfalls.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Kravica%20Waterfalls/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Kravica%20Waterfalls/Kravica%20Waterfalls.mp3',99),(145,'Mostar Old Town','莫斯塔尔老城','','Mostar, Bosnia and Herzegovina','步行即可到达','Opened daily','0:00-24:00','a beautiful slice of the past','古城内到处都有着浓厚的土耳其色彩，有着几百年历史的古城是世界文化遗产','0','0','','',0,0,'At dusk, the lights of numerous millhouse restaurants twinkle across gushing streamlets. Narrow Kujundžiluk (\'gold alley\') bustles joyously with trinket sellers. And in between, the Balkans\' most celebrated bridge forms a majestic stone arc between reincarnated medieval towers. It\'s an enchanting scene. Do stay into the evening to see it without the summer hordes of day trippers. Indeed, stay longer to enjoy memorable attractions in the surrounding area as well as pondering the city\'s darker side – beyond the cobbled lanes of the attractively restored Ottoman quarter are still-apparent scars of the 1990s conflict, especially around Spanski Trg.\nBetween November and April most tourist facilities go into hibernation while midsummer can get scorchingly hot. Spring and autumn are ideal.','莫斯塔尔十五世纪由奥斯曼帝国建造。和萨拉热窝一样，莫斯塔尔也是一座在山谷里的城市。在波黑战争期间，莫斯塔尔被实际上独立的克罗地亚赫塞哥波斯尼亚共和国定为首都。虽然历经战乱，但仍旧掩盖不了这里迷人的文化与艺术韵味。相反地，却吸引力更多的人前来一探究竟。2005年，古城及古桥全部被收录进世界遗产名录，成为波黑最重要的一项遗产。城市内以古城和古桥为最重要景观和珍贵的遗产，是游客到此必达的景点。除此之外，清真寺、教堂以及旧时保存的土耳其房、奥斯曼房等建筑，也是经典之外的又一亮点。漫步在沧桑的古城中，不由得心生敬意。',0,6820,124,33,6,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Thumb%20point%20Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Mostar%20Old%20Town/Thumb%20Mostar%20Old%20Town.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Mostar%20Old%20Town/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Mostar%20Old%20Town/Mostar%20Old%20Town.mp3',99),(146,'Stari Most','莫斯塔尔古桥','','Stari Most, Mostar 88000波斯尼亚 黑塞哥维那','步行即可到达','Opened daily','0:00-24:00','The historic town of Mostar','有427年历史的石拱桥','0','0','','',0,0,'World-famous Stari Most (Old Bridge) is Mostar\'s indisputable visual focus. Its pale stone magnificently throws back the golden glow of sunset or the tasteful night-time floodlighting. The bridge\'s swooping arch was originally built between 1557 and 1566 on the orders of Suleyman the Magnificent. The current structure is a very convincing 21st-century rebuild following the bridge\'s 1990s bombardment during the civil war. Numerous well-positioned cafes and restaurants tempt you to sit and savour the splendidly restored scene.','莫斯塔尔古桥（塞尔维亚-克罗地亚语：Stari most，又译莫斯塔尔老桥）是波斯尼亚和黑塞哥维那莫斯塔尔的一座16世纪的桥梁，这是一座单孔石桥，横跨内雷特瓦河。古桥矗立了427年后于1993年11月9日波斯尼亚战争期间被摧毁。之后开始重建项目，并于2004年重新开放。桥宽4.55米，桥长27.34，桥拱最高端距水面20米，桥两端各有一个石砌桥头堡。桥面呈圆拱型，镶有高高的防滑条呈浅台阶状，只能供行人步行通过。\n战争爆发前，桥上跳水时小伙子们一展雄姿的年度运动，他们互相竞赛以博取同城姑娘们的青睐。2004年为庆祝大桥重新开通，9名小伙子一起从大桥上一跃而下。美丽的桥充满了过去的战争和历史，莫斯塔尔古桥是这个城市的地标。',0,3771,69,33,6,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Thumb%20point%20Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Stari%20Most/Thumb%20Stari%20Most.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Stari%20Most/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Stari%20Most/Stari%20Most.mp3',99),(147,'Blagaj Tekija','特基雅修道院','','Blagaj village | Localita Blagaj, Mostar, Bosnia and Herzegovina','By Taxi- Moj Taxi\nBy rented car.\nMostar Bus Service','Open all days i','08:00 am - 10:00 pm','Bosnia\'s Beautiful Monastery Under A Cliff','波斯尼亚最漂亮的悬崖下的修道院','4 BAM','4波黑马克','387 36 572-551','http://www.blagajtekija.ba/en/',0,0,'Forming Blagaj\'s signature attraction, the centrepiece of this complex of traditional stone-roofed buildings is a very pretty, half-timbered Dervish House with wobbly kilm-covered floors, offline carved doorways and a series of curious niches. It\'s perched above the cave-mouth from which the Buna River\'s surreally blue-green waters flow out of a cliff-face.\nAccording to one legend, the complex was built in the early 16th century as a thank you to the dervish whose St George–style dragon slaying rescued the daughter of Count Stjepan. The complex is still a venue for Zikr praise-chanting three nights weekly.','Blagaj Tekija 位于莫斯塔尔以南，周围群山环绕，美丽的内雷特瓦河绵延流淌。修道院建于鄂图曼王朝时代，建造者是伊斯兰教神秘主义团体。历年来，这里都是莫斯塔尔地区的伊斯兰教圣地。',0,9406,116,33,6,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Thumb%20point%20Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Blagaj%20Tekija/Thumb%20Blagaj%20Tekija.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Blagaj%20Tekija/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Blagaj%20Tekija/Blagaj%20Tekija.mp3',99),(148,'Koskin-Mehmed Pasha\'s Mosque','Koskin-Mehmed Pasha\'s Mosque','','Mala Tepa 16, Mostar 80807,Bosnia and Herzegovina','By Cab or Taxi.By rented Car.','Should not be v','08:30 am - 07:30 pm ','most beautiful mosque in the region of Herzegovina. ','波黑境内最漂亮的清真寺','mosque 6KM, mosque & minaret 12KM','6/12波黑马克','','',0,0,'Entered from a gated courtyard, the rebuilt 1618 Koski Mehmed Paša Mosque lacks a certain finesse in its interior, but you can climb the claustrophobic minaret for sweeping town views.The most attractive part of the mosque complex is the small courtyard outside with its fountain taps, tea-stall and garden area. Access to that doesn\'t require a ticket unless you want to get close to the parapet for the river view.','莫斯塔尔老城，圆柱尖顶的清真寺和方柱尖顶的教堂遥相对望。老桥架起和平的桥梁，将各民族联结起来。清真寺、教堂、浴室，各种建筑风格的交杂，展现了老城对多种宗教、信仰、文化的包容与接纳。雷纳特瓦河静静的流淌，洗去了尘埃，留下的是个焕发勃勃生机的新城。',0,4688,121,33,6,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Thumb%20point%20Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Koskin-Mehmed%20Pasha\'s%20Mosque/Thumb%20Koskin-Mehmed%20Pasha\'s%20Mosque.jpg','http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Koskin-Mehmed%20Pasha\'s%20Mosque/vtour/tour.html','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1503588978/Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina/Mostar/Sights/Koskin-Mehmed%20Pasha\'s%20Mosque/Koskin-Mehmed%20Pasha\'s%20Mosque.mp3',99),(149,'Brazen Palace','黄铜宫殿','','Brazen palace, Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka','','','8:30-17:30','So called because it once had a bronze-tiled roof','黄铜宫殿，因其曾有一个铜屋顶而得名。','','','','',0,0,'The ruins of the \'Brazen Palace\' stand close to the bodhi tree. The remains of 1600 columns are all that is left of this huge pavilion, said to have had nine storeys and accommodation for 1000 monks and attendants.\n\nIt was originally built by King Dutugemunu more than 2000 years ago, but through the ages was rebuilt many times, each time a little less grandiosely.\n\nThe current stand of pillars (now fenced off) is all that remains from the last rebuild – that of King Parakramabahu I around the 12th century.','黄铜宫殿，因其曾有一个铜屋顶而得名。原为九层建筑，供千余僧侣居住的地方，建有一百多间房屋，如今仅残留1600根石柱。据传，当年这座建筑镶嵌着大量的金银宝石，宫殿底层雕有400头石象，象牙也用玉石镶嵌，但现在只剩下林立的石柱。',0,6242,59,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Brazen%20Palace/Thumb%20Brazen%20Palace.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Brazen%20Palace/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Brazen%20Palace/Brazen%20palace.mp3',99),(150,'Guard Stone','守护石','','Watawandana Rd, Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka','','','8:30-17:30','This is the most artistic guard stone found in Sri Lanka.','最精美的守护石','','','','',0,0,'This is the most artistic guard stone found in Sri Lanka. Two lovers emerge from the dragons mouth above the  cobra king,who has in his hand the pot of aboundance signifying prosperity. This is said to show that fertility generates prosperity indulgence in woridly life is like entering the mouth of the dragon is another interpretation. It belongs to the 7-9 century A.D.','守护石总是和月亮石雕像相邻，它也有着特别的魅力：微带曲线的男性雕像，神态轻松，欢迎着人们，而不是凶神恶煞似的，拒人于千里之外。\n',0,7144,88,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Guard%20Stone/Thumb%20Guard%20Stone.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Guard%20Stone/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Guard%20Stone/Guard%20Stone.mp3',99),(151,'Key Pond','Key Pond','','Key Pond, Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka','','','8:30-17:30','','','','','','',0,0,'','',0,6994,114,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Key%20Pond/Thumb%20Key%20Pond.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Key%20Pond/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Key%20Pond/Key%20Pond.mp3',99),(152,'Moonstone','月亮石','','Moonstone, Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka','','','8:30-17:30','Moon-stone is a unique feature of the Sinhalese architecture of ancient Sri Lanka.','斯里兰卡最漂亮的月亮石','','','','',0,0,'Moon-stone is a unique feature of the Sinhalese architecture of ancient Sri Lanka. It is an elaborately carved semi-circular stone slab, usually placed at the bottom of staircases and entrances. First seen in the latter stage of the Anuradhapura period, the sandakada pahana evolved through the Polonnaruwa, Gampola and Kandy period. According to historians, the sandakada pahana symbolises the cycle of Sa?sāra in Buddhism.','Moonstone（月亮石）位于Abhayagiri Dagoba西北方向一座建于9世纪的僧人学院废墟中，它是整个Anuradhapura乃至整个斯里兰卡雕刻得最精美的月亮石。',0,3539,58,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Moonstone/Thumb%20Moonstone.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Moonstone/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Moonstone/Moonstone.mp3',99),(153,'Ruwanwelisaya','鲁梵维利萨亚佛塔','','Ruwanwelisaya, Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka','','','8:30-17:30','Considered a marvel for its architectural qualities and sacred to many Buddhists all over the world. ','古城里修缮最完好也最有生命力的佛塔。','','','','',0,0,'The Ruwanwelisaya is a stupa in Sri Lanka, considered a marvel for its architectural qualities and sacred to many Buddhists all over the world. It was built by King Dutugemunu c. 140 B.C., who became lord of all Sri Lanka after a war in which the Chola King Elara, was defeated. It is also known as Mahathupa, Swarnamali Chaitya, Suvarnamali Mahaceti (in Pali) and Rathnamali Dagaba.','鲁梵维利萨亚佛塔(Ruwanwelisaya Stupa)是古城里修缮最完好也最有生命力的佛塔，也被称作为“大塔”。这座舍利塔建造于公元前2世纪，公认是由杜图伽摩尼国王建造的最美的建筑物，但可惜的是建筑还未完工他就去世了，由他的儿子萨达帝沙王子继承父志最终完成了大塔的建造。据说刚完工的时候有110米，但是现在只有55米高。鲁梵维利萨亚曾经不只是一座塔的名字，还是一个教派，拥有着一个颇具规模的寺院。这里还有佛殿、藏金阁、菩提树寺、僧人居所、食堂、浴池等待。佛塔的院墙是由许多个肩并肩并排站立的大象雕刻组成。位于佛塔东南侧有一间佛殿，外侧的走廊上矗立着五尊大理石雕刻的佛像，殿内有一尊镀金的卧佛。',0,7715,99,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Ruwanwelisaya/Thumb%20Ruwanwelisaya.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Ruwanwelisaya/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Ruwanwelisaya/Ruwanwelisaya.mp3',99),(154,'Samadhi Buddha','三味佛像','','Samadhi Buddha, Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka','','','8:30-17:30','This 4th-century statue, seated in the samadhi (meditation) pose, is regarded as one of the finest Buddha statues in Sri Lanka.','三昧佛像藏匿于丛林深处，建于4世纪，是阿努拉德普勒最初4尊佛像中唯一被完整保留至今的一尊，被认为是斯里兰卡最精美的佛像之一。','','','','',0,0,'The Samadhi Statue is a statue situated at Mahamevnāwa Park in Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka. The Buddha is depicted in the position of the Dhyana Mudra, the posture of meditation associated with his first Enlightenment. Whether the Buddha\'s Enlightenment was the experience technically called Samadhi, or some other phenomenon, may depend upon the philosophical allegiance of the believer. In the Dhyana Mudra the Buddha sits cross - legged with his upturned palms placed one over the other on his lap. This position is universally known throughout the Buddhist world, and this statue is therefore one of the most typical pieces of Buddhist sculpture. It is not to be confused with the very similar \"Earth-Touching Mudra,\" which depicts the simple action the Buddha took to fend off the illusions projecte','Samadhi Boddha（三昧佛像）藏匿于丛林深处，是斯里兰卡早期佛教雕刻艺术的代表典范，也是Anuradhapura最初4尊佛像中唯一被完整保留至今的一尊。印度独立运动的领袖Pandit Nehru，在被英国人囚禁的岁月，曾经以注视这座佛像照片的方式让自己保持镇定克制。2007年中国与斯里兰卡建交50周年，兰卡总理拉贾帕克萨赠送给中国的，正是这尊佛像的复制品。',0,3956,71,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Samadhi%20Buddha/Thumb%20Samadhi%20Buddha.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Samadhi%20Buddha/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Samadhi%20Buddha/Samadhi%20Buddha.mp3',99),(155,'Sri Mahabodhi','圣菩提树','','Sri Mahabodhi, Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka','','','8:30-17:30','It is said to be a tree grown from a sapling from the famous Bodhi tree under which the first Buddha became enlightened.','佛陀在菩提伽耶悟道的菩提树分枝，现在是全世界最老的一棵菩提树。','','','','',0,0,'The Sri Maha Bodhi is a Sacred Fig tree in Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka. It is said to be a tree grown from a sapling from the famous Bodhi tree under which the first Buddha became enlightened, which was brought down by Mihindu (Mahinda) and Sangamittha Maha Thero. It was planted in 288 BC, and is the oldest living human-planted tree in the world with a known planting date.\n\nIt was planted on a high terrace about 6.5 m (21.3 ft) above the ground and surrounded by railings, and today it is one of the most sacred objects of the Buddhists in Sri Lanka and respected by Buddhists all over the world. This wall was built during the reign of King Kirthi Sri Rajasingha, to protect it from wild elephants which might have attacked the tree.','公元前3世纪，印度阿育王派他的儿子摩哂陀和女儿僧伽蜜多前往斯里兰卡宣传佛教，摩哂陀带来了教义，僧伽蜜多将佛陀在菩提伽耶悟道的菩提树分枝带到了阿努拉德普勒。印度的那颗大菩提树早已消失在历史的洪流中，如今挺立在菩提寺中的菩提树，其实是斯里兰卡菩提树的子孙，而且已经更替到了第六代。佛教在斯里兰卡就此牢牢扎根，像这棵菩提树一样发芽壮大，历经其他宗教统治者的入侵破坏却屹立不倒。更为珍贵的是菩提伽耶的佛陀悟道的菩提树摧毁后，便是从这棵菩提树分枝移植到菩提伽耶的，所以，阿努纳德普勒的菩提树应是全世界最古老的一棵。现在神圣的菩提树被高台和围栏保护起来，前来礼拜祈福的善男信女更是络绎不绝，特别是月圆之日，这个四方平台将被挤的水泄不通。',0,7636,107,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Sri%20Mahabodhi/Thumb%20Sri%20Mahabodhi.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Sri%20Mahabodhi/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Sri%20Mahabodhi/Sri%20Mahabodhi.mp3',99),(156,'Thuparamaya','萨帕拉玛舍利塔','','Thuparama Mawatha, Anuradhapura, Sri Lanka','','','8:30-17:30','The Oldest Stupa In Sri Lanka','全世界已被发现的最古老的舍利塔。','','','','',0,0,'The stupa is built in the shape of a bell. Its dome is 3.5 meters (11’4 inches) tall from the ground and its diameters measures 50.1 meters (164 feet).\n \nIt has been destroyed many times, but always rebuilt by different Kings throughout history. At one point, the stupa was covered by silver and gold until the Pandyans from India robbed plundered it.\n \nCenturies later, Mahinda IV had the stupa covered in gold again but this time, the Colas, from India plundered the it again.','萨帕拉玛舍利塔坐落于Ruvanvelisaya Dagoba以北的森林中，这是斯里兰卡最古老的舍利塔，也有可能也是全世界已被发现的最古老的舍利塔，它是Devanam Piyatissa国王在公元前3世纪时建造的，据说里面存放着佛祖的右锁骨。它原先的一种“稻田般”的外形在1862年翻修时被改造成了更保守的“钟”的形状，高度为19米。',0,9313,72,10,1,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Thumb%20point%20Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Thuparamaya/Thumb%20Thuparamaya.jpg','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Thuparamaya/vtour/tour.html','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1502934150/Sri%20Lanka/Anuradhapura/Sights/Thuparamaya/Thuparamaya.mp3',99),(157,'Wat Chedi Luang','契迪龙寺','','Phra Pok Klao, Sri Phum, Mueang Chiang Mai, Thailand','出租/TukTuk车或步行','Mon-Sat','6:00-18:00','Wat Chedi Luang temple of the big stupa or temple of the royal stupa) is a Buddhist temple in the historic centre of Chiang Mai, Thailand.','又称大佛塔寺，是清迈市内六大寺庙中最为著名也是最大的寺庙。','Audlt：40THB，Child：20THB','成人：40铢，儿童：20铢','+66-53-276140','',0,0,'The construction of the temple started in the 14th century, when King Saen Muang Ma planned to bury the ashes of his father there. After 10 years of building time it was left unfinished, later to be continued after the death of the king by his widow. Probably due to stability problems it took until the mid-15th century to be finished during the reign of king Tilokaraj. It was then 82 m high and had a base diameter of 54 m, at that time the largest building of all Lanna. In 1468, the Emerald Buddha was installed in the eastern niche. In 1545, the upper 30 m of the structure collapsed after an earthquake, and shortly thereafter, in 1551, the Emerald Buddha was moved to Luang Prabang.','寺庙始建于1411年，之后经过数次增建。1545年，清迈发生一次大地震和大风灾，佛塔的尖顶一夜之间塌毁，露出塔内的金身佛像，现在的寺庙是后人重新修复过的形象。\r\n契迪龙寺属于典型兰纳（古泰族王朝）风格建筑，由主殿、小佛殿、僧房组成。寺庙门口点缀着蛇和孔雀的装饰，进入内部则能看到巨大的佛像。 在正殿的后面则是这里最重要的景物大佛塔，塔身高达90米。\r\n大佛塔是寺内最古老的建筑。1545年清迈大地震后，佛塔的尖顶一夜之间塌毁。所以现在所见的佛塔为平顶。\r\n塔身有六座象头雕塑，其中左侧五座是用水泥修复的赝品，最右侧象头才是为砖砌古迹。 ',0,6659,83,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Wat%20Chedi%20Luang/Thumb%20Wat%20Chedi%20Luang.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(158,'Wat Phra Singh','帕辛寺','','Sri Phum, Mueang Chiang Mai, Chiang Mai, Thailand','出租/TukTuk车或步行','','6:00-18:00','Wat Phra Singh is a Buddhist temple in Chiang Mai, Northern Thailand,the older brother of the late King Bhumibol Adulyadej, bestowed on it the status of Royal temple of the first grade in 1935.','帕辛寺是清迈城内规模最大的佛寺，兰纳式建筑的完美典范。','0','0','','',0,0,'Construction on Wat Phra Singh began in 1345 when King Phayu,226.227 the fifth king of the Mangrai dynasty, had a chedi built to house the ashes of his father King Kham Fu. A wihan and several other buildings were added a few years later and the resulting complex was named Wat Lichiang Phra. When, in 1367, the statue of Phra Buddha Singh was brought to the temple, the temple complex received its present name. During restoration works in 1925, three funerary urns were discovered inside a small chedi. It was assumed that these contained royal ashes. The urns have since been lost. From 1578 to 1774 the Burmese ruled Lanna and in this period the temple was abandoned and came under serious disrepair. It was only when King Kawila assumed the throne as King of Chiang Mai in 1782.','帕辛寺，帕辛寺是清迈城内规模最大的佛寺，兰纳式建筑的完美典范。帕辛寺建于14世纪，具有悠久的历史。据说寺院是模仿清迈的普拉新寺院而建的。寺内供奉着Phra Singh的佛像，殿堂里的壁画以当地古代服饰和风俗为内容，被认为是泰国北部传统艺术的代表作。每年4月泼水节期间，是人们庆祝的主要地点之一。\r\n帕辛寺是清迈规模最大、也是建筑雕刻最精美的一座寺庙，和契迪龙寺同为清迈等级最高的寺庙。\r\n寺庙内部的宏大，佛像顶部是一朵金莲，金莲四周一圈是十二生肖。',0,9355,111,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Wat%20Phra%20Singh/Thumb%20Wat%20Phra%20Singh.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(159,'Wat Chiang Man','清曼寺','','Sri Phum, Mueang Chiang Mai, Chiang Mai, Thailand','出租/TukTuk车或步行','','6:00-18:00','Wat Chiang Man was built by Mangrai in 1297 CE as the first temple of Chiang Mai','又称昌挽寺，建于1300年，清迈的第一座寺庙，也是清迈最古老的寺庙。','0','0','+66-53-375368','',0,0,'Chiang Mai\'s oldest temple was established by the city\'s founder, Phaya Mengrai, sometime around 1296. In front of the ubosot (ordination hall), a stone slab, engraved in 1581, bears the earliest-known reference to the city\'s founding. The main wí·hăhn (sanctuary) also contains the oldest-known Buddha image created by the Lanna kingdom, cast in 1465.','寺中最好的建筑是由15只大象承载的塔。清迈建城时，曼格莱王在此扎营，监督整个工程的进行，并在此盖了清曼寺。寺中有两座兰那式僧院，较大的一座僧院在1920年曾重修过，佛坛前有一尊立佛，造于1465年，是到目前为止清迈发现最早的佛像。较小的僧院中有两座非常珍贵的佛像Phra Sila与Phra Sea Tang Khamani，两尊佛像都是具有造雨的神力，每年泼水节庆祝仪式中被信徒抬起参与到游行队伍当中。',0,9800,58,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Wat%20Chiang%20Man/Thumb%20Wat%20Chiang%20Man.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(160,'Wat Phra That Doi Suthep','素贴山双龙寺','','Su Thep, Mueang Chiang Mai, Thailand','出租/TukTuk车或步行','','6:00-18:00','It is a sacred site to many Thai people. The temple is 15 kilometres from the city of Chiang Mai. From the temple, impressive views of Chiang Mai can be seen.','双龙寺(Wat Phra That Doi Suthep)，又称素贴寺，因有两条长龙在两侧台阶坐卧而得名，是泰国著名的佛教避暑胜地。','30THB','30铢','+66-53-295000','',0,0,'The original founding of the temple remains a legend and there are a few varied versions. The temple is said to have been founded in 1383 when the first stupa was built. Over time, the temple has expanded, and been made to look more extravagant with many more holy shrines added. A road to the temple was first built in 1935.According to legend, a monk named Sumanathera from the Sukhothai Kingdom had a dream. In this vision he was told to go to Pang Cha and look for a relic. Sumanathera ventured to Pang Cha and found a bone. Many claim it was Gautama Buddha\'s shoulder bone. The relic displayed magical powers: it glowed, it was able to vanish, it could move and replicate itself. Sumanathera took the relic to King Dhammaraja, who ruled Sukhothai.','据说在14世纪时泰北得到释迦牟尼佛的舍利子，一位高僧将舍利子放在白象的背上，任由白象寻找供奉舍利子的位置，最后白象走到了素贴山上。至今佛寺的金色佛塔中仍供奉着佛祖的舍利子，每年都吸引世界各地的信徒前来朝圣。',0,3936,108,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Wat%20Phra%20That%20Doi%20Suthep/Thumb%20Wat%20Phra%20That%20Doi%20Suthep.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(161,'Wat Buppharam','布帕兰寺','','Tha Phae Road, Chiang Mai, Thailand','出租/TukTuk车或步行','','6:00-18:00','Wat Buppharam just outside the old walled city','电影《泰囧》的取景地之一。','0','0','','',0,0,'One of the oldest remaining structures is the chedi  that was built more than 4 centuries ago in Burmese and Mon style. The white chedi with a golden spire is guarded by four Burmese style lions, called Singha in Thai. The base of the chedi contains a Buddha image on all four sides.The small Lanna style viharn was likely built during the 16th century.','位于塔佩门外的闹市中，公园1496年由King Muang Kaew建造，正值兰纳王朝佛教最兴盛的時候，是座混合缅甸和兰纳两种风格的寺庙。寺中最吸引人的是年代久远的小木造僧院，有超过300年的历史，19世纪末曾经修复过，屋宇还保存原样，风檐上及廊柱上的细致灰泥装饰依旧叫人心动，有点倾斜的前门，让人有种年华老去的感叹。紧邻小木造僧院的是一座较大的僧院，也有200年的历史，走在两座院间的小道上，思古之情油然而生。左边新建造的僧院则是色彩斑斓、 金碧辉煌，与老旧的僧院像是两间不同的寺庙，塑着人形金鸟的山形墙特别值得细看。寺庙的后方有一座大佛塔，白色的外观加上巨大的塔身颇为雄伟。',0,8281,115,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Wat%20Buppharam/Thumb%20Wat%20Buppharam.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(162,'Wat Phan Tao','潘道寺','','Phra Pok Klao, Sri Phum, Mueang Chiang Mai, Thailand','出租/TukTuk车或步行','','6:00-18:00','The temple is a classic teak wood construction especially its roof structure. ','清迈城中一座瑰宝级殿堂','0','0','','',0,0,'Without doubt the most atmospheric in the old city, this teak marvel sits in the shadow of Wat Chedi Luang. Set in a compound full of fluttering orange flags, the monastery is a monument to the teak trade, with an enormous prayer hall supported by 28 gargantuan teak pillars and lined with dark teak panels, enshrining a particularly graceful gold Buddha image. The juxtaposition of the orange monks\' robes against this dark backdrop during evening prayers is particularly sublime.Above the facade is a striking image of a peacock over a dog, representing the astrological year of the former royal resident\'s birth. The monastery is one of the focal points for celebrations during the Visakha Bucha festival in May or June, when monks light hundreds of butter lamps around the pond in the grounds.','盼道寺，又名柚木寺，就在大佛塔寺不远的拐弯处。寺内有一座古老精致全木质大殿，整座都是用柚木建造的，纯泰北兰纳式风格的设计，超过280年的历史，是目前为数不多的木造建筑之一。泰文Phan Tao的意思是1000个火炉，因为这里曾经是铸佛场，为首要的寺庙铸造佛像，因此得名。盼道寺的大殿由模具脱出的柚木板组合而成，底下有28根巨大的柚木柱支撑；大殿中还有印有灵蛇图案的山形屋顶盖板，镶嵌在五颜六色的拼花镜片中。大殿里面陈列着古老的寺钟、一些陶瓷制品、几尊兰纳风格的镀金木质佛像、几个古董柜子、柜子里还堆放着抄在棕榈叶上的古老佛经。',0,5595,103,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Wat%20Phan%20Tao/Thumb%20Wat%20Phan%20Tao.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(163,'Night Bazaar','古城夜市','','104-1 Chang Klan Road | intersection of Tha Pae and Chang Klang Roads','出租/TukTuk车或步行','Opened daily','','Night markets or night bazaars are street markets which operate at night and are generally dedicated to more leisurely strolling, shopping, and eating than more businesslike day markets.','清迈夜市位于长康路，是当地旅游商店的发源地，吃喝玩乐都能在此体验。','','','+66 53 283 250','',0,0,'Chiang Mai Night Bazaar is one of the city\'s main night-time attractions, especially for families, and is the legacy of the original Yunnanese trading caravans that stopped here along the ancient route between Simao  and Mawlamyaing. Today the night bazaar sells the usual tourist souvenirs, similar to what you\'ll find at Bangkok\'s street markets.In true market fashion, vendors.','这里菠萝饭、海鲜、烧烤等各类当地小吃种类丰富，堪称吃货的天堂。大部分当地特产和纪念品都可以在这儿买到，并且价格非常便宜。每晚均会开放，错过周末夜市的不妨在这里逛逛能感受地道的夜市文化。',0,7135,121,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Night%20Bazaar/Thumb%20Night%20Bazaar.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(164,'Wat Suan Dok','松德寺','','Su Thep, Mueang Chiang Mai, Chiang Mai, Thailand','出租/TukTuk车','','6:00-18:00','It is a Royal Temple of the Third Class. ','寺内供有全泰国最大的青铜佛像，其余建筑亦甚宏伟。','0','0','','',0,0,'Built on a former flower garden in 1373, this important monastery enshrines one half of a sacred Buddha relic (the other half was transported by white elephant to Wat Phra That Doi Suthep). The main chedi is a gilded, bell-shaped structure that rises dramatically above a sea of immaculate white memorial chedi honouring members of the Thai royal family, with the misty ridge of Doi Suthep soaring behind.The hanger-like main wí·hăhn (sanctuary) contains a huge standing Buddha statue that almost touches the ceiling. Take some time to wander the memorial garden of whitewashed chedi in front of the monastery, which contain the ashes of generations of Lanna royalty.','松德寺建于14世纪兰纳泰王朝美丽的花园中。寺内供有全泰国最大的青铜佛像，其余建筑亦甚宏伟。正殿的屋顶为三层，殿后又有大小佛塔，塔内藏有泰王的骨坛。寺中巨大的钟形佛塔与素可泰时期颇为相似，是纪念著名的僧人玛哈泰拉苏玛那，他从斯里兰卡来到清迈讲学曾住在这里。松达寺是摄影师们的最爱，尤其是夕阳夕下的时候特别迷人。每年4月13-14日，这里都要举行大型宗教庆典活动。 ',0,8891,147,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Wat%20Suan%20Dok/Thumb%20Wat%20Suan%20Dok.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(165,'Chiang Mai University','清迈大学','','Chiang Mai University, 239 Huay Kaew Road, Muang District, Chiang Mai, Thailand','出租/TukTuk车','','9:00-17:00','Chiang Mai University ranks third in academics and fifth in research according to the Thailand Office of the Higher Education Commission.The international ranks are 67 in Asia','清迈大学是全市唯一一所国立大学，也是泰国北部首屈一指的高等学府','Audlt：60THB，Child：30THB','成人：60铢，儿童：30铢','+66-53-941000','http://www.cmu.ac.th/',0,0,'The main campus of Chiang Mai\'s famous public university occupies a 2.9-sq-km wedge of land about 2km west of the city centre, partly covered by forest and open greenery. It\'s a peaceful place to wander and there are bike lanes throughout the campus and plenty of cafes for pit-stops.The entry fee for tourists – introduced after Chinese tourists started dressing up in school uniforms and sneaking into classes! – is charged at the Information Center near the Th Huay Kaew entrance; this includes a tram ride to the Ang Kaew reservoir in the grounds.','泰国清迈大学（ChiangMaiUniversity）简称CMU，成立于1964年。包含三个校区，总面积约14平方公里，学生人数超过3万人，主校区位于泰国清迈市西郊。清迈大学是全市唯一一所国立大学，也是泰国北部首屈一指的高等学府，于1964年1月由普密蓬国王殿下批准创建。 校园Huay Kaew路的前门有校区观光车可以乘坐，在风景如画的安娇湖Ang Kaew会稍作停留。',0,6050,122,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Chiang%20Mai%20University/Thumb%20Chiang%20Mai%20University.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(166,'The Bhubing Palace','蒲屏皇宫','','Suthep, Mueang Chiang Mai, Chiang Mai','出租/TukTuk车','','','Above Wat Phra That Doi Suthep, the grounds of the royal family\'s winter palace are open to the public when the royals aren\'t visiting.','蒲屏皇宫为泰国皇室的避暑行宫，该行宫完工于1962年。每年1-3月王室人员来此居住。在皇室人员不住在这里的时候，平日宫外花园向游人开放，游客可以参观。','50THB','50铢','+66-53-211750','',0,0,'Above Wat Phra That Doi Suthep, the grounds of the royal family\'s winter palace are open to the public when the royals aren\'t visiting. Thanks to the mountain\'s cool climate, the royal gardeners are able to raise \'exotic\' species such as roses, attracting lots of Thai sightseers. More interesting is the reservoir in the grounds, brought to life by fountains that dance to the king\'s own musical compositions.','整个王宫为泰式建筑，花园内草木葱郁，花木秀丽，种有玫瑰、鼠尾草和各种奇花异草。每年的12月到1月份的冬季，这里异常凉爽，百花盛开，景色美不胜收。王宫白墙黃瓦，建筑格调雅致，坐落在周围的青山之中，自有一分清涼平和之美。',0,7577,121,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/The%20Bhubing%20Palace/Thumb%20The%20Bhubing%20Palace.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(167,'Doi Suthep','素贴山','','Su Thep, Mueang Chiang Mai, Thailand','出租/TukTuk车','Opened daily','0:00-24:00','Doi Suthep is a mountain west of Chiang Mai, Thailand. It is 1,676 metres (5,499 ft) in elevation and is one of the twin peaks of a granite mountain.','步行300级台阶到达山顶的观景台可欣赏到清迈市区全景','0','0','','',0,0,'The park accommodation makes a comfortable base from which to explore and a trail runs for 2km from the campground to the summit of Doi Suthep, though the only view is of eerie mists swirling between the trees.','素贴在泰语中是仙友之意，当地华人又称此山为遇仙山或会仙山。素贴山海拔1667米，不算特别高大，但是山坡上开满五色玫瑰，山顶白云缭绕，风光秀丽，是清迈的天然瞭望台。素贴山上有著名的双龙寺、蒲屏皇宫等景观。',0,9736,87,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Doi%20Suthep/Thumb%20Doi%20Suthep.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(168,'Nimmanahaeminda Road','宁曼路','','Nimmana Haeminda Road, Chiang Mai, Thailand','出租/TukTuk车','Opened daily','0:00-24:00','Nimmana Haeminda Road, a king is the name of the main street that as a source of modern restaurants.','清迈最小资的商业区、艺术区。','','','','',0,0,'As the city grows and the number of expats have grown, this area west of the old city between Huay Kaew Road and Suthep Road is super popular to tourists, expats as well as trendy and hip locals alike. The entire strip of this street is filled with coffee shops (many with free wifi), bars, international restaurants, spas, gift shops and street vendors.','如果说，清迈大学是古城中的一簇小清新存在，那么宁曼路一定是清迈的最小清新。清迈并不只有古老灿烂的寺庙，这里依然也弥漫着现代的活力，这里的年轻人也热爱时尚的文化，有自己的想法，也有一部分热爱清迈的外籍友人停留在了清迈，他们把来自世界的文化带入这个宁静古老的小城，开启了各式各样的富有情调的酒店，客栈，酒吧，餐厅，咖啡馆以及各种时尚精品小店，这些店铺无疑都是玩味混搭的高手，混合着这个小城的古老与现代，清新与厚重，单一与多元，打散重组成新的艺术空间和艺术品：家庭摆件服装服饰珠宝首饰木雕陶艺家具壁画等等，无不独具匠心。\r\n',0,8949,125,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Nimmanahaeminda%20Road/Thumb%20Nimmanahaeminda%20Road.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(169,'Warorot Market','瓦洛洛市场','','Th Chang Moi & Th Praisani，Chiang Mai，Thailand','出租/TukTuk车','Opened daily','0:00-24:00','Chiang Mai\'s oldest public market, Warorot is a great place to connect with the city\'s Thai soul. ','原汁原味体验本地人市井生活的集市，真正的当地市场','','','+66-53-248604','',0,0,'Chiang Mai\'s oldest public market, Warorot is a great place to connect with the city\'s Thai soul. Alongside souvenir vendors you\'ll find numerous stalls selling items for ordinary Thai households: woks, toys, fishermen\'s nets, pickled tea leaves, wigs, sticky-rice steamers.. It\'s easy to spend half a day wandering the covered walkways, watching locals browsing, and haggling for goods that actually have a practical use back home.','瓦洛落市场是清迈的唐人街，建筑风格与曼谷的唐人街类似，多是红黄两色，大招牌上写的是中文。 白天出售地方小吃、服饰、山地部落的手工艺品，价钱比清迈夜市(Chiang Mai Night Bazaar)要低。另外还可以购买到各种水果、香料和可口的小吃。到了晚上，这里则是色彩缤纷的鲜花市场。',0,5539,113,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Warorot%20Market/Thumb%20Warorot%20Market.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(170,'Three Kings Monuments','三王纪念碑','','Mueang Chiang Mai District, Chiang Mai, Thailand','步行','Opened daily','0:00-24:00','According to legend, the three worked together to lay out the city of Chiang Mai. The sculpture has become something of an iconic image representing Chiang Mai. ','著名的三王雕像，为纪念三位对清迈有重大贡献的人物：兰甘亨大帝、孟莱王和南蒙王并立，他们是兰纳历史上最重要的三个北方泰国和老挝国王。','0','0','','',0,0,'The monument features 5.4-metre  tall bronze statues of three dikgosi, or chiefs, who played important roles in Botswana\'s independence: Khama III, Sebele I, and Bathoen I The three chiefs traveled to Great Britain in 1895 to ask Joseph Chamberlain, Secretary of State for the Colonies, and Queen Victoria to separate the Bechuanaland Protectorate from Cecil Rhodes\'s British South Africa Company and Southern Rhodesia. Permission was granted, and meant that the Batswana remained under direct British rule until independence in the 1960s.','位于清迈文化中心的正前方，是著名的三王雕像，为纪念三位对清迈有重大贡献的人物：兰甘亨大帝、孟莱王和南蒙王并立，他们是兰纳历史上最重要的三个北方泰国和老挝国王。塑像也成了当地居民朝圣的地方。当地人在塑像脚下献上鲜花，点燃香烛，祈求三王的英灵能送来福祉。',0,4847,142,14,3,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1498531468/Thumb%20point%20Thailand/Chiengmai/Sights/Three%20Kings%20Monuments/Thumb%20Three%20Kings%20Monuments.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(171,'Leaning Tower of Pisa','比萨斜塔','','Piazza dell\'Arcivescovadl No.8','比萨火车站出来直走大概20分钟可到。或可直接坐橙色线LAM rossa公车往返','全年开放','12月至1月：10:00-17:00；1','one of the most remarkable architectural structures from medieval Europe.','世界著名的景观，也是意大利标志之一。','18EUR','登塔18欧。','39 050 835011','http://www.towerofpisa.org/',0,0,'The Leaning Tower of Pisa is the piazza’s crowning glory.Although only a third as high as the Washington Monument, it was a miracle of medieval engineering, probably the tallest bell towers in Europe.With 207 columns ranged around eight stories, Tower of Pisa looks like a massive wedding cake knocked precariously askew by a clumsy giant guest.The construction of Tower of Pisa began in August 1173 and continued for about 200 years due to the onset of a series of wars. Till today, the name of the architect is a mystery.','比萨斜塔是意大利比萨城大教堂的独立式钟楼，世界著名的景观，也是意大利标志之一。位于比萨大教堂的后面，是奇迹广场的三大建筑之一。 钟楼始建于1173年，设计为垂直建造，但是在工程开始后不久便由于地基不均匀和土层松软而倾斜，1372年完工，塔身倾斜向东南。由于它的倾斜以及建筑特色使得比萨斜塔有着独一无二的美丽。相传在公元1590年，伽利略曾经在比萨斜塔上做了一个自由落体实验，并推翻了亚里士多德的观点。 1987年它和相邻的大教堂、洗礼堂、墓园一起因其对11世纪至14世纪意大利建筑艺术的巨大影响，而被联合国教育科学文化组织评选为世界遗产。近些年来，政府一直在进行斜塔的维护工作。',0,4620,121,37,7,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/Thumb%20point%20Italy/Tuscany/Sights/Leaning%20Tower%20Of%20Pisa/Thumb%20Leaning%20Tower%20Of%20Pisa.jpg','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/video_utovr/video/Italy/Tuscany/Sights/Leaning%20Tower%20Of%20Pisa/Leaning%20Tower%20Of%20Pisa.html','',99),(172,'Ponte Vecchio','佛罗伦萨维琪奥桥','','Ponte Vecchio, 50123 Firenze, italia','乘坐C3、D路公共巴士至Ponte Vecchio站，下车即可抵达','全年开放','24小时开放','one of the most beloved landmarks in Florence. ','佛罗伦萨地标之一，欧洲最古老的石拱桥','Free','免费','','https://www.italyguides.it/en/tuscany/florence/pon',0,0,'Ponte Vecchio Bridge - “Old Bridge” in Italian - is the most famous bridge in Florence and undoubtedly one of the city’s most illustrious landmarks. It is an incredibly breathtaking sight when seen from afar, and even more so when you walk across it!\nIt spans the narrowest point of the Arno River, and doesn’t really look like a bridge at all for the numerous overhanging shops, whose glittering treasures delight the visitors’ gaze as they pass by. The bridge - entrance point to the city of Florence from the Cassia road - is made of wood and stone and probably dates back to the Roman era. But the river continued to prevail, and until the 1300s the bridge underwent at least two reconstructions due to the floods.','老桥，这座阿诺河上最著名最古老的桥梁见证了佛罗伦萨整个城市的强盛和衰落。它始建于中世纪，历尽战火的洗礼和洪水的侵袭始终保持屹立，成为游客来多佛罗伦萨的必经之地。据说起初老桥是当地贩卖猪肉的场所，后来美蒂奇大公觉得臭气熏天，就下令把肉铺都赶走，取而代之的是珠宝店铺。而美蒂奇大公为了不和普通百姓走同样的路， 就在老桥上面就修建了著名的瓦萨里走廊(Corridoio Vasariano)，以连通自己的办公地点旧宫和住宿地点皮蒂宫。如今老桥是佛罗伦萨最著名的黄金珠宝店铺聚集地，而且几乎全部都是前店后厂手工打造。传说老桥还是但丁和他夫人相遇的地点，所以现在仍有许多情侣在桥的栏杆上锁上同心锁以表真爱。',0,5558,130,34,7,'','','','',99),(173,'Gondola','贡多拉','','Venezia，italy','','全年开放','','gondola is a mode of transportation','意大利威尼斯特有的和最具代表性的传统划船','50Min/80EUR','50分钟/80欧元','','http://www.reidsitaly.com/destinations/veneto/veni',0,0,'A gondola ride is the one Venetian tourist trap everyone falls into willingly.Long, sleek, black, slightly crooked, looking like a cross between a canoe and a coffin, the single oar worked by a professional gondoliere.That\'s the Venetian gondola, the primary form of transportation in Venice from the 12th century until speedboats roared into the canals in the late 20th.And touristy or not, your visit to Venice isn\'t complete until you take one of these time-honored water taxis for a spin.\nTechnically the gondola is a mode of transportation, and technically you might find a gondolier willing to ferry you from point A to point B, but in practice these most famous of Venetian boats operate as supremely overpriced tourist mini-cruises, not as a viable means of public transportation.','独具特色的威尼斯尖舟（Gondolieri）有一个独具特色的名字——“贡多拉”，又名“公朵拉”。这种轻盈纤细、造形别致的小舟已有一千多年的历史了。它一直是居住在泻湖上的威尼斯人代步的工具。据说，7世纪时，第一任总督将这种船命名为“贡多拉”.贡多拉实际上就是一只单人摇撸的可以同时乘坐6人的小船，与中国江南的小木船和云南泸沽湖的猪槽船有点类似，她之所以被人们誉为“水上奔驰”、“水上法拉利”，不是因为她有顶级的发动机和变速箱（实际上她是一种无机械动力的小船），也不是因为她在水上速度有多快，而是因为她造型奇特，船体精美，内饰奢华，乘坐舒适，人坐在里边有着坐在豪华轿车里的感觉。当然这种小船的造价也非我们国内的小木船可比，一只贡多拉要2万欧元，相当于20万元人民币，高昂的价格也是被人们称为水上法拉利的原因之一。',0,3932,135,38,7,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/Thumb%20point%20Italy/Venice/Sights/Gondola/Thumb%20Gondola.jpg','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/video_utovr/video/Italy/Venice/Sights/Gondola/Gondola.html','',99),(174,'Arco Di Costantino','君士坦丁凯旋门','','Via di San Gregorio','地铁:B线Colosseo站下车即到。\n公交:60/75/85/87/ 117/271/571/175/186/810/','全年开放','24小时开放','The arch is the last and largest in Rome','罗马现存凯旋门中最新的一座。','Free','免费','','',0,0,'Dedicated by the Senate in AD 315, the tenth anniversary (decennalia) of the emperor\'s reign, the Arch of Constantine (Arcus Constantini) commemorates the victory of Constantine over Maxentius at the Battle of Milvian Bridge in AD 312 for sole control of the Roman empire in the west. The inscription, which is repeated on both sides of the attic, alludes to the \"divine inspiration\" about which Eusebius writes in his Life of Constantine (I.28), although which divinity had helped Constantine deliberately is not specified. The arch is the last and largest in Rome, and the most flamboyant in its use of colored stone.\n','君士坦丁凯旋门位于斗兽场和废墟之间，为纪念君士坦丁一世312年米里维桥战役的胜利而修建，是罗马现存凯旋门中最新的一座。\n凯旋门高21米，宽25.7米，深7.4米，建于312年末到315年。由于时间比较仓促，它的很多装饰部分都是从以往其他皇帝的建筑物上拆卸而来的。比如凯旋门顶端的八块长方形浮雕，它们是从奥理略皇帝纪念碑上拆卸而来，现在原件已被珍藏在罗马首都博物馆。而每根圆柱顶端的达基亚囚犯大理石雕像则很可能来自图拉真广场。只有两个小拱门上方的圆形浮雕描绘了这场战争的场面。',0,6986,138,36,7,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/Thumb%20point%20Italy/Rome/Sights/Arco%20Di%20Costantino/Thumb%20Arco%20Di%20Costantino.jpg','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/video_utovr/video/Italy/Rome/Sights/Arco%20Di%20Costantino/Arco%20Di%20Costantino.html','',99),(175,'Castel Sant’Angelo','圣天使城堡','','Lungotevere Castello, 50, 00193 Roma,italy','公交：30/70/81/87/130F/186/280/492/628/N6/N7于Lungotevere Tor Di',' 1月1日和12月25日闭馆，','9:00-19:30','This Fortress was built as a mausoleum for the Emperor Hadrian','一座华丽的罗马教皇宫殿','10EUR','10欧元','0039-66819111','http://www.castelsantangelo.com/museo.asp',0,0,'This Fortress was built as a mausoleum for the Emperor Hadrian (AD130-139), but it has also been a prison and a papal residence. It was used by former Popes who absconded there for protection in times of danger. There has been a covered passageway which still connects Castel Sant\'Angelo to the Vatican.\nThe National Museum of Castel Sant\'Angelo inside retraces its history. The castle has various exhibits ranging from Renaissance paintings and pottery to antique military weapons. A huge spiral ramp ascends upwards the Castel Sant Angelo for about 400 feet. \nAs in the last act of Tosca, admire the beautiful view from the terrace but don\'t throw yourself off - go for a coffe instead in one of the rampart towers. ','圣天使城堡是意大利罗马的一座城堡，该建筑位于台伯河畔，邻近梵蒂冈教廷，圣天使城堡首先作为阻止西哥特人和东哥德人入侵的要塞，然后被当作监狱使用，最后改建成一座华丽的罗马教皇宫殿。现在圣天使城堡已成为一座博物馆，也成为当地的旅游景点之一。',0,6136,136,36,7,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/Thumb%20point%20Italy/Rome/Sights/Castel%20Sant’Angelo/Thumb%20Castel%20Sant’Angelo.jpg','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/video_utovr/video/Italy/Rome/Sights/Castel%20Sant’Angelo/Castel%20Sant’Angelo.html','',99),(176,'Colosseum','罗马斗兽场','','Piazza del Colosseo, 1, 00184 Roma, italy','地铁：B线，Colosseo站\n公交：60/75/85/87/117/271/571/175/186/810/850/C','全年开放','3月最后一个周日至8月31日：8:30-','Rome’s great gladiatorial arena is the most thrilling of the city\'s ancient sights. ','纵使你看了一万张斗兽场的照片，当你走近它时你还是会深深震撼。','12EUR','套票12欧','39-06-3996-7700','http://www.coopculture.it/en/colosseo-e-shop.cfm',0,0,'Rome’s great gladiatorial arena is the most thrilling of the city\'s ancient sights. Inaugurated in AD 80, the 50,000-seat Colosseum, also known as the Flavian Amphitheatre, was clad in travertine and covered by a huge canvas awning held aloft by 240 masts. Inside, tiered seating encircled the arena, itself built over an underground complex (the hypogeum) where animals were caged and stage sets prepared. Games involved gladiators fighting wild animals or each other.','古罗马斗兽场又称圆形竞技场，位于古罗马广场较低的一头，占地六英亩，像一座由石灰石垒成的顶部凹陷的小山。斗兽场外墙布满大得令人生畏的拱门；内部是裂痕累累的座位席，底部是一个曾经人兽决斗表演的平台，平台下方是关闭野兽和奴隶的隔间。站在底部，可以感受到深深的压迫感袭来！这座庞大的斗兽场在血腥味最浓的鼎盛时期始终是座无虚席的，最狂热的场面比比皆是，但却从未能像今日作为一座废墟那样打动人心。',0,6723,118,36,7,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/Thumb%20point%20Italy/Rome/Sights/Colosseum/Thumb%20Colosseum.jpg','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/video_utovr/video/Italy/Rome/Sights/Colosseum/Colosseum.html','',99),(177,'Piazza Del Duomo','佛罗伦萨主教座堂广场','','Piazza Duomo, 17 - 50122 Florence','地铁(红线M1/黄线M3)Duomo站；公车Duomo站','全年开放','24小时开放','Milan\'s most beautiful square.','佛罗伦萨的地标','Free','免费','39(055)215380','http://www.duomofirenze.it/',0,0,'The Piazza del Duomo is Milan\'s most beautiful square. It is dominated by the magnificent front facade of the Duomo (cathedral). At the center of the square stands a monument honoring the first king of a unified Italy.As early as during the Roman era this area was the heart of Milan. Later, during the Middle Ages, when there were several churches clustered together here, it was the center of religious life in Milan. The churches had to make way for the expansive Piazza del Duomo, a popular meeting place that is constantly crowded with tourists and locals alike.','主教座堂广场（Piazza del Duomo）位于佛罗伦萨市中心，佛罗伦萨主教座堂（圣母白花大教堂、乔托钟楼)和圣乔凡尼洗礼堂都位于广场上。主教座堂广场可以说是佛罗伦萨最出名的景色了，这里有佛罗伦萨的地标——百花大教堂，旁边还有圣乔凡尼礼拜堂（Battistero di San Giovanni）以及乔托钟楼 （Campanile di Giotto）。所有来佛罗伦萨的旅客都会聚集在这里，是佛罗伦萨为数不多会出现拥拥攘攘的景点之一。',0,5205,129,34,7,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/Thumb%20point%20Italy/Firenze/Sights/Piazza%20del%20Duomo/Thumb%20Piazza%20del%20Duomo.jpg','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/video_utovr/video/Italy/Firenze/Sights/Piazza%20del%20Duomo/Piazza%20del%20Duomo.html','',99),(178,'St.Peter\'s Square','圣彼得广场','','Piazza San Pietro, Roma，italy','搭乘去地铁A线（红线）至Ottaviano-S.Pietro站，下车后沿Via Ottaviano向南步行约700米即可','全年开放','24小时开放','is an architectural highlight.','天主教会重要的象征之一。','Free','免费','','http://www.vaticanstate.va/content/vaticanstate/en',0,0,'St. Peter\'s Square is bordered on two sides by semi-circular colonnades which, according to Bernini, symbolize the stretched arms of the church embracing the world. The colonnades were built in 1660 and consist of four rows of columns with in total 284 Doric columns and 88 pilasters. The columns are 20 meters high (66 ft) and 1.6 meters wide (5ft). 140 statues were installed on top of the colonnades, all created by Bernini and his students. They depict popes, martyrs, evangelists and other religious figures.\nTo the left and right of the central obelisk on the square are circular marble plates which indicate the foci of the elliptical square. When you stand on either of these plates and look at the nearest colonnade, it will look as if there is only one row of columns instead of four. Berni','圣彼得广场位于梵蒂冈的最东面，是罗马教廷举行大型宗教活动的地方，可同时容纳50万人。广场的建设工程用了十一年的时间(1656-1667年)，由世界著名建筑大师贝尔尼尼亲自监督工程的建设。广场最具代表性的就是包围它的4列共284根多利安柱式圆柱，圆柱上还矗立有140座圣人像。而广场中央是一根公元40年从埃及运来的巨大的圆柱，使这座广场整体感觉非常雄伟。',0,9859,142,36,7,'','','','',99),(180,'Riomaggiore','里奥马焦雷','','Riomaggiore, Province of La Spezia, Italy','火车、汽车、船、飞机','全年开放','24小时开放','Cinque Terre\'s easternmost village','欣赏五渔村壮丽的海岸线。','Free','免费','','http://www.cinqueterre.eu.com/en/',0,0,'Cinque Terre\'s easternmost village, Riomaggiore is the largest of the five and acts as its unofficial HQ (the main park office is based here). Its peeling pastel buildings march down a steep ravine to a tiny harbour – the region\'s favourite postcard view – and glow romantically at sunset.','五渔村的五镇之一，是最（东）南端也是最大的一个镇。国家公园的办公室就在这镇上。从马纳罗拉到里欧马吉哦雷的沿海步行街被称作“爱之路”Via dell\'Amore，是连通五渔村步道最短最容易的一段，约一公里长，在离地不太高的悬崖上凿出平铺的路面，一侧是山岩，另一侧就是立谷里安海的层层波浪。路上有一尊“现代主义”吻像，周边的护栏上挂满了同心锁。而半路上还有短短的一段隧道，隧道内墙上写满了各种浪漫或肉麻的情话。 从火车站到靠山一侧的镇上要走过一条地下通道，通道的壁画描绘的是五渔村的先人如何赤手空拳一土一木将五渔村建起来的。出了通道，就是镇的陡峭的主街Via C. Colombo，街两旁是各种餐馆，小卖部和纪念品店。火车站的另一侧就是里欧马吉哦雷的小码头，时常有渔船和五渔村海上游的客船在此靠岸。码头两侧的山岩上建满了高矮楼房，表层五颜六色的涂料为码头增添了可爱的气氛。从码头沿着小路往南走一小段，可以到达缶叟拉小海滩 Fossola beach，到这儿可以看看植被与海鸟，到沙滩上玩玩，浮浅或是租独木舟和皮筏艇。',0,9681,75,35,7,'http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/Thumb%20point%20Italy/La%20Spezia/Sights/Riomaggiore/Thumb%20Riomaggiore.jpg','','http://europe.beejeen.com/1500824984/video_utovr/video/Italy/La%20Spezia/Sights/Riomaggiore/Riomaggiore.html','',99),(181,'Arch Of Triumph','平壤凯旋门','','update later...','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'','',0,8826,123,47,12,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1500884101/Thumb%20point%20North%20Korea/Pyongyang/Sights/Arch%20Of%20Triumph/Thumb%20Arch%20Of%20Triumph.jpg','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1500884101/video_utovr/video/North%20Korea/Pyongyang/Sights/Arch%20Of%20Triumph/Arch%20Of%20Triumph.html','',99),(182,'Kim Il Sung Square','金日成广场','','update later...','','','','','','','','','',0,0,'','',0,5087,81,47,12,'http://asia.beejeen.com/1500884101/Thumb%20point%20North%20Korea/Pyongyang/Sights/Kim%20Il%20Sung%20Square/Thumb%20Kim%20Il%20Sung%20Square.jpg','','http://asia.beejeen.com/1500884101/video_utovr/video/North%20Korea/Pyongyang/Sights/Kim%20Il%20Sung%20Square/Kim%20Il%20Sung%20Square.html','